rol.jpg","details":{"size":55275,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"N26_Blog Header_Logo_Petrol.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002FdSl9ry52vRq1OSSmMSbTM\u002F0b19b973fa6a65924021ba2978e5fa73\u002FN26_Blog_Header_Logo_Petrol.jpg","details":{"size":55275,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"N26_Blog Header_Logo_Petrol.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"categoryId":{"en":"technology"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"kaFaEXjWLYmWEIi4wGi2I"}}},"date":{"en":"2020-09-16"},"excerpt":{"de":"N26 ist eine Bank mit Vollbanklizenz. Hier erfährst du mehr über die Sicherheitsmaßnahmen rund um unsere Produkte.","en":"Just because we make banking simple, doesn’t mean it’s insecure. Learn about the security programs we use to protect your balance and personal data."},"copy":{"de":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Dein Bankkonto bei N26 ist 100 % mobil – das bedeutet, dass du komplexe und zeitaufwändige Bankgeschäfte schnell und einfach auf deinem Handy ausführen kannst. Aus diesem Grund setzen wir Technologien ein, um für sichere Bankkonten und eine sichere App zu sorgen.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Die primäre Verantwortung jeder Bank besteht darin, dein Geld zu schützen. Niemand darf in der Lage sein, unbefugt auf dein Konto zuzugreifen, mit betrügerischen Einkäufen in deinem Namen davonzukommen oder deine persönlichen Daten zu stehlen. N26 sorgt für diese grundlegenden Sicherheitsstandards. Als moderne Bank bieten wir ein vollständig mobiles Banking-Erlebnis von deinem Smartphone aus, das ändert jedoch nichts an unserem Sicherheitsversprechen. Lies weiter, um einige unserer Sicherheitsmaßnahmen für dein N26 Konto kennenzulernen:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"{{youtube id=\"gl3RcZmfZPg\" caption=\"Was ist eigentlich eine Banklizenz?\"}}","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Europäische Einlagensicherung und Datenschutz","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Erstens sind die Einlagen eines jeden N26 Kontos bis zu 100.000 € durch das europäische Einlagensicherungssystem gemäß der EU-Richtlinien abgesichert. Unabhängig davon, ob du dein N26 Konto in Deutschland, Frankreich, Irland, Slowenien oder einem unserer anderen Märkte eröffnet hast – deine Einlagen sind bei uns sicher. Dieser Rechtsschutz gilt für Banken in der gesamten EU. Da wir eine voll lizenzierte europäische Bank sind, gilt er auch für uns. Zweitens sind all deine Daten nach deutschem Datenschutzrecht geschützt.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"{{youtube id=\"-alnV4cNTbY\" caption=\"Sicheres Online-Banking\"}}","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Sicheres mobiles Banking","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Beim Eröffnen eines N26 Kontos musst du es mit deinem Smartphone verknüpfen. Solange dein Konto mit deinem Handy verknüpft ist, kann keine andere Person von einem anderen Handy aus auf dein Bankkonto zugreifen. Solltest du dein Smartphone einmal verlieren, können wir dich selbstverständlich durch den Wiederherstellungsprozess deines Kontos führen. Du hast immer und überall die volle Kontrolle über die Sicherheitseinstellungen deines Kontos. So kannst du deine Karte bei Verlust sofort sperren, deine PIN zurücksetzen, Abhebungs- und Zahlungslimits festlegen und Online- oder Auslandstransaktionen ermöglichen – alles mit nur wenigen Klicks in der N26 App. Außerdem erhältst du nach jeder Transaktion eine Push-Nachricht in Echtzeit, sodass du immer über deine Kontobewegungen auf dem Laufenden bist.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"3D-Secure-Technologie für zusätzliche Sicherheit","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"3D Secure (3DS) ist ein zusätzlicher Authentifizierungsschritt, der bei Online-Kartenzahlungen Schutz vor Betrug bietet – unsere 3DS-Technologie heißt Mastercard SecureCode.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Weitere Informationen über unsere Sicherheitsfunktionen findest du auf der ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fsicherheit#:~:text=Deine%20Sicherheit%20hat%20bei%20uns,durch%20die%20nationale%20Einlagensicherung%20gesch%C3%BCtzt."},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"value":"N26 Webseite zum Thema Sicherheit","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Being mobile means quick and simple solutions to tough problems. That’s why we work with technology to keep your bank account, app, and Mastercard safe and secure.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The first responsibility of any bank is to earn your trust. You deposit money into the bank with the firm expectation that it will be protected. Nobody else should be able to access your account unexpectedly, get away with fraudulent purchases, or steal your personal information. All of these fundamental rules apply at N26. We have a modern setup—100% mobile banking from your phone—but our basic promise to you is the same. Here are some of the security features that support this promise.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"EU deposit guarantee and privacy protection","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"First and foremost, the deposits of any N26 bank account are guaranteed up to €100,000 by the Deposit Guarantee Scheme in accordance with EU directives. Whether you opened your N26 bank account in Germany, France, Ireland, Slovenia, or any of our other markets, your deposits are safe. This legal protection applies to banks across the EU, and because we’re a fully licensed European bank, it applies to us, too. The second major point is that all your data is protected under German privacy law. We understand the sensitive nature of financial services and how to handle that kind of information.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Mobile security for safe mobile banking","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"When you open an N26 bank account, you have to pair it to your phone with a pairing code. Your account can’t be accessed by anyone else from any other phone as long as it’s paired to your phone. If you happen to lose your phone, we can obviously guide you through the process of retrieving your account. You also have full control over the particulars of your account on a daily basis—decide whether to immediately lock your card if it gets lost, reset your PIN, set withdrawal and payment limits, and enable online or foreign payments. You’ll also get an instant push notification after all account activity, so you’re up to date at all times.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"3D Secure for advanced fraud protection","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"3D Secure (3DS) is an authentication step that helps prevent fraud when you make online card purchases. Our 3DS initiative is called Mastercard SecureCode, and you’ll see it if you make an online purchase that may be risky.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Bug Bounty Program","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"We believe in working with the security research community around the world to constantly keep our security and our app up to date. The N26 Bug Bounty program offers cash rewards to encourage security researchers to inform us about bugs or vulnerabilities, so that we can fix them long before any damage is done.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"{{youtube id=\"gypk6w60fMk\" caption=\"With digital banking is my money safe?\"}}","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"For even more information about our ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fsecurity"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"state of the art security","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", see the security page on the N26 website.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"}},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"JNjk338u2pUwexYsMeF36"}}}}}]},"to":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"4HroqtiG609WUc9978IC6i","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-11-27T15:31:12.382Z","updatedAt":"2021-05-20T18:43:10.333Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":4,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"blogPost"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"en":"Blogpost: How secure is an N26 bank account? - Magazine Migration"},"countryCodes":{"en":["EU","DE",