ry","createdAt":"2021-01-22T05:01:03.919Z","updatedAt":"2021-01-27T15:09:14.431Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":4,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"blogPost"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"en":"Pandemic insurance coverage launch (ALL)"},"countryCodes":{"en":["DE","AT","FR","IT","ES","EU"]},"title":{"de":"Umfassende Absicherung – auch bei COVID-19-Fällen","en":"Epidemic and pandemic travel coverage—now included with N26 You and Metal","es":"Cobertura de viaje Covid en tiempos de pandemia: incluido con N26 You y N26 Metal","fr":"Couverture des risques liés aux épidémies et pandémies pour vos voyages nécessaires en période de COVID-19","it":"Viaggia protetto con la copertura viaggio Covid"},"slug":{"de":"umfassende-reiseversicherung-auch-bei-covid-19-faellen","en":"stay-protected-with-covid-travel-insurance","es":"seguro-de-viaje-covid-en-tiempos-de-pandemia","fr":"couverture-assurance-voyage-coronavirus","it":"viaggia-protetto-con-l-assicurazione-viaggio-covid"},"previewImage":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Insurance"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"3ZxIDsL0JonhVlvSeEWbbL","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2021-01-21T10:23:53.608Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:31:06.667Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Blog header: Pandemic insurance coverage (ALL)"},"description":{"de":"Reiseversicherung Covid","en":"Pandemic insurance coverage","es":"Seguro de viaje Covid","fr":"Assurance pandémie","it":"Assicurazione viaggio Covid"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ZxIDsL0JonhVlvSeEWbbL\u002Fce7b201493a7caf36889b1fe88a10498\u002FPandemicCoverage_GENERAL_Web1000x700_2x_RGB.jpg","details":{"size":1279560,"image":{"width":2000,"height":1400}},"fileName":"PandemicCoverage_GENERAL_Web1000x700_2x_RGB.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ZxIDsL0JonhVlvSeEWbbL\u002F6abf87ef982c35949db0e9db1b88dc6f\u002FPandemicCoverage_GENERAL_Web1000x700_2x_RGB.jpg","details":{"size":1279560,"image":{"width":2000,"height":1400}},"fileName":"PandemicCoverage_GENERAL_Web1000x700_2x_RGB.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ZxIDsL0JonhVlvSeEWbbL\u002F8e1efecb94aac4ce8cbc38ef61175431\u002FPandemicCoverage_GENERAL_Web1000x700_2x_RGB.jpg","details":{"size":1279560,"image":{"width":2000,"height":1400}},"fileName":"PandemicCoverage_GENERAL_Web1000x700_2x_RGB.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ZxIDsL0JonhVlvSeEWbbL\u002F99762c71ac8c8790b4961fe4b2c46a24\u002FPandemicCoverage_GENERAL_Web1000x700_2x_RGB.jpg","details":{"size":1279560,"image":{"width":2000,"height":1400}},"fileName":"PandemicCoverage_GENERAL_Web1000x700_2x_RGB.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ZxIDsL0JonhVlvSeEWbbL\u002F725c31e580632d2eec9a8561f0194e73\u002FPandemicCoverage_GENERAL_Web1000x700_2x_RGB.jpg","details":{"size":1279560,"image":{"width":2000,"height":1400}},"fileName":"PandemicCoverage_GENERAL_Web1000x700_2x_RGB.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"categoryId":{"en":"product"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5KiVGM6QjC6aOuyciK8cGy"}}},"date":{"en":"2021-01-22"},"excerpt":{"de":"Mit N26 You und Metal bist du immer auf der sicheren Seite. Eröffne dein Bankkonto mit umfassender Reiseversicherung – auch bei Pandemien.","en":"Traveling in times of COVID-19? Be prepared with epidemic and pandemic travel coverage, now available for N26 You and Metal customers.","es":"¿Necesitas viajar en tiempos de pandemia? Si tienes que hacerlo, mejor que sea con el seguro de viaje Covid incluido en las cuentas N26 You y N26 Metal.","fr":"Bénéficiez d’une couverture voyage coronavirus pour vos voyages en période de pandémie du COVID-19 avec le compte N26 You et N26 Metal.\n","it":"Hai organizzato un viaggio a cui non puoi rinunciare? Evita gli imprevisti con la copertura viaggio Covid per i clienti N26 You e N26 Metal."},"copy":{"de":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Mit neuen Situationen und Umständen ändern sich auch unsere Bedürfnisse. Als mobile, innovative Bank gehen wir mit der Zeit, um dich immer bestmöglich unterstützen zu können. Deshalb haben wir unsere Reiseversicherung mit Allianz jetzt ausgeweitet – sie greift jetzt auch in Fällen mit COVID-19-Bezug. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nN26 You, Business You, Metal und Business Metal können jetzt auch Ansprüche mit Covid-Bezug geltend machen – beispielsweise bei Reiseabbrüchen oder medizinischen Notfällen. Hier erfährst du, was alles gedeckt ist und wie du einen Anspruch einreichen kannst.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Reiseabbruch und Stornierung","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wenn deine Reise storniert wird oder du sie aus triftigen Gründen abbrechen musst, erhältst du Schadensersatz – das gilt jetzt auch für Gründe mit Corona-Bezug. Dazu gehören nicht nur für Reisen ins Ausland, sondern auch für Reiseziele innerhalb deines Wohnsitzlandes – solange sie mehr als 100 km von deinem Wohnort entfernt sind. Das gilt für Reisen, die am oder nach dem 22. Januar 2021 beginnen.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Du kannst einen Anspruch geltend machen, wenn du eine Reise abbrechen oder stornieren musst, weil du oder ein\u002Fe Mitreisende\u002Fr sich verletzt oder krank wird. Zu den gedeckten Krankheiten gehören auch ansteckende oder pandemische Krankheiten wie COVID-19.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Außerdem erhältst du bis zu 10.000 €, falls dein Flug abgebrochen, storniert oder das Boarding verweigert wird, weil bei dir oder deinem Familienmitglied Verdacht auf eine ansteckende Krankheit (z. B. COVID-19) besteht. Das gilt nur für Fälle, in denen du oder ein\u002Fe Mitreisende\u002Fr spezifisch aussortiert wird und du dich auf Anweisung der Regierung oder einer offiziellen Behörde in Quarantäne begeben musst.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Die Absicherung greift auch nicht im Fall einer Quarantäne-Anordnung, die für die generelle Bevölkerung, eine ganze Region oder das Land gilt, von, zu oder durch das du reist. Weitere Details zur Allianz Assistance Absicherung findest du in den Allianz AGB.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Absicherung für medizinische Notfälle","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Die Absicherung für N26 You, Business You, Metal und Business Metal Kunden wurde auch im Bereich medizinische Notfälle ausgeweitet und deckt nun auch ansteckende und pandemische Erkrankungen im Ausland.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wenn du dich also während einer Auslandsreise verletzt oder schwer erkrankst – dazu gehört auch die Diagnose einer ansteckenden oder pandemischen Erkrankung wie COVID-19 – kannst du folgende Ansprüche geltend machen: Krankenhausaufenthalt (Notfall), Transport, medizinische Behandlung, Medikamente und Unterstützung bei der Rückreise ins Wohnsitzland.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Dank der 24\u002F7-Notfallhotline von Allianz Assistance kannst du dir jederzeit und von überall her Rat einholen. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Bitte beachte, dass die Absicherung nicht greift, wenn du entgegen der Empfehlung deines Abreise- oder Ziellandes reist. Weitere Details zur Allianz Assistance Absicherung findest du in den Allianz AGB.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Wie kann ich einen Anspruch einreichen?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nÖffne dazu einfach deine N26 App und gehe auf ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Mein Konto. ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Tippe auf ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"N26 You ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"oder ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"N26 Metal","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" und dann auf ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Allianz Versicherung. ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wähle die Art des Anspruchs und tippe dann auf ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Versicherungsanspruch geltend machen. ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Folge danach den Anweisungen in der App und sende die relevanten Dokumente an Allianz Assistance. Es gelten die AGB der Allianz Assistance Absicherung.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\n","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Mit N26 bist du auf der sicheren Seite","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nEgal ob zu Hause oder im Ausland: Mit N26 hast du immer und überall Zugriff auf dein N26 Bankkonto, innovative Features und dein Versicherungspaket.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nNoch kein N26 Kunde? Eröffne dein ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fyou-internationales-konto"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 You","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fbusiness-you-geschaeftskonto"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 Business You","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fmetal"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 Metal","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" oder ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fbusiness-metal"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 Business Metal Konto","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" in nur wenigen Minuten – ganz ohne Papierkram. Profitiere von Premiumvorteilen wie dem umfassenden Versicherungspaket für Reisen, Lifestyle und Mobilität, exklusiven Partnerangeboten, kostenlosen Abhebungen und Zahlungen in Fremdgebühren und vielem mehr!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"5EaQdKZJgsVic9wHayAHrM","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Traveling for necessary reasons during the COVID-19 pandemic, and looking for an extra safety net in case things don’t go according to plan? We’ve got you covered. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"If you’re a premium N26 You, N26 Business You, N26 Metal or N26 Business Metal customer, you’ll be pleased to know that we’ve expanded your Allianz Assistance travel coverage to include epidemic and pandemic coverage for your travels, at no extra cost. Read on below to find out what’s newly included, and how to make a claim. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Travel cancellation and curtailment coverage","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Canceling a fully-booked trip or cutting a trip short can be stressful, especially if you’re stuck having to pay out-of-pocket for your lost journey. If you’re an N26 You, N26 Business You, N26 Metal or N26 Business Metal customer making travel plans, you’ll now have extended travel cancellation and curtailment benefits, including pandemic coverage for claims relating to COVID-19. This trip cancellation and curtailment coverage is valid for all trips abroad, and for trips to destinations farther than 100km from your home in your country of residence, which begin on or after January 22, 2021. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"If you have to cancel an upcoming trip or cut a trip short because you or a travel companion is diagnosed with an epidemic or pandemic disease such as COVID-19, you’ll be able to claim compensation. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"In addition, you’ll now also be covered up to a maximum amount of €10,000 if your trip is interrupted or canceled because you or your travel companion are placed into an individual quarantine due to exposure to a virus. In this case, you must have been specifically singled out as an individual case, and ordered to quarantine by the government or a public authority. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Please note that you must not have traveled against government or public authority advice. This new pandemic coverage will not cover cases where a quarantine applies generally to the wider population or a region, or to the place you are traveling from, through, or to. For the cover details, please refer to the policy Terms and Conditions.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Emergency medical travel assistance","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"If you’re traveling abroad for necessary reasons during a pandemic, it helps to be prepared against the unexpected. For extra peace of mind, N26 You, Business You, Metal and Business Metal memberships now come with extended emergency medical travel assistance that includes pandemic coverage for trips abroad. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"This means that if you develop a sudden, unexpected illness, injury or medical condition that could cause you serious harm while on a trip overseas—","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"including being diagnosed with an epidemic or pandemic disease such as COVID-19","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"—you’ll be covered for emergency hospitalization and medical treatment, along with medicine costs, medical transportation, and repatriation assistance, if necessary. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Plus, with access to the 24\u002F7 medical assistance hotline from Allianz Assistance, we’re always only a dial away if you need to speak to someone, wherever you are in the world.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Please note that you must not have traveled against government or public authority advice. For the cover details, please refer to the policy Terms and Conditions.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"How do I make a claim?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"To make a claim, open your N26 app and go to ‘","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"My Account’","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":". Tap on ‘","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"N26 You’","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" or ‘","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"N26 Metal’","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" under ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"‘Manage","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":",’ and go to ‘","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Allianz coverage","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".’ ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Select the type of claim you’d like to make, and then tap ‘","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Start my claim process","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".’ Please follow the step-by-step guide on how to submit the required documents to Allianz Assistance. The usual Terms and Conditions of your Allianz Assistance coverage apply.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 has you covered","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Whether you’re managing your finances at home or making trips abroad, you can count on N26 to support your everyday—especially during times of uncertainty, such as the COVID-19 pandemic.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"If you’re not an N26 customer yet, you can open an ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fyou-bank-account-with-travel-insurance"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"value":"N26 You","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fyou-business-bank-account-with-travel-insurance"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"value":"N26 Business You","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fmetal"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"value":"N26 Metal","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" or ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fbusiness-metal"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"value":"N26 Business Metal","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" bank account online in minutes, with zero paperwork involved. Sign up now to start tapping into your premium benefits, such as a travel, lifestyle, mobility and mobile phone coverage package from Allianz Assistance, free ATM withdrawals worldwide, no international transaction fees, exclusive partner brand offers, and so much more.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"5EaQdKZJgsVic9wHayAHrM","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si tienes que viajar por necesidad en tiempos de Covid y quieres protegerte contra posibles imprevistos, tenemos la solución para ti. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Hemos extendido la cobertura de viaje de Allianz Assistance que incluyen las cuentas N26 You, N26 Business You, N26 Metal y N26 Business Metal y, ahora, incluye también una cobertura de viaje Covid sin ningún coste adicional. Sigue leyendo para descubrir lo que cubre y cómo dar parte. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Cobertura de cancelación o interrupción de viaje","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Cancelar un viaje o tener que interrumpirlo cuando ya lo tienes todo programado es algo que genera estrés, sobre todo si encima lo tienes que pagar de tu bolsillo. Pero si tienes una cuenta N26 You, N26 Business You, N26 Metal o N26 Business Metal, ahora cuentas con una extensión de la cobertura que cubre los gastos de cancelación o interrupción de un viaje debido al COVID-19. Esta cobertura de viaje Covid se aplica a todos los viajes al extranjero, o a cualquier viaje de más de 100 km desde tu hogar en tu país de residencia, a partir del 22 de enero de 2021. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"La cobertura de viaje Covid te cubre si tienes que cancelar o interrumpir un viaje porque tú o tu acompañante sois diagnosticados de una enfermedad epidémica o pandémica como el COVID-19. En este caso podrás reclamar una indemnización","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Además, tienes una cobertura de hasta 10.000 € si tu viaje se cancela o se interrumpe porque, porque tú o tu acompañante estáis en cuarentena debido a la exposición a un virus. En este caso, necesitaréis demostrar que las autoridades públicas os han indicado expresamente que debéis hacer cuarentena.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ten en cuenta que no debes viajar en contra de las recomendaciones del gobierno o de las autoridades públicas. La cobertura de viaje Covid no cubre casos en los que la cuarentena sea un requisito general para toda la población de una determinada región, ni si el requisito de hacer cuarentena se debe al país desde el que viajas, al que vas o por el que has pasado, por ejemplo, por tratarse de un país de riesgo. Para conocer los detalles de la cobertura, consulta los términos y condiciones de la póliza.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Cobertura de gastos de emergencia médica en el extranjero","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si tienes que viajar por necesidad durante la pandemia, más vale prevenir que curar. Para protegerte aún mejor, las cuentas premium N26 You, Business You, Metal y Business Metal ahora incluyen también una cobertura de viaje Covid cuando viajas al extranjero.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Es decir, que si enfermas de repente, sufres una lesión o te contagias de alguna enfermedad, incluido un diagnóstico positivo de COVID-19, se cubren tus gastos de emergencia médica; incluyendo la hospitalización, asistencia médica, medicinas, transporte médico y, si fuera necesaria, tu repatriación.Además, tienes acceso al servicio de asistencia médica por teléfono de Allianz Assistance las 24 horas, los 7 días de la semana, a tan solo una llamada de distancia desde cualquier lugar del mundo.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ten en cuenta que no debes haber viajado en contra de las recomendaciones del gobierno o de las autoridades públicas. Para conocer los detalles de la cobertura, consulta los términos y condiciones de la póliza.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"¿Cómo dar parte?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Para dar parte, abre tu app N26 y ve a ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Mi cuenta","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" \u003E ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"N26 You","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" o ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"N26 Metal","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" \u003E ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Cobertura del seguro de Allianz","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"; una vez ahí, selecciona el motivo de tu reclamación y pulsa en ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Dar parte al seguro","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Después, solo tienes que seguir los pasos que se indican y aportar la documentación necesaria para dar parte a Allianz Assistance. Se aplican los Términos y Condiciones de tu póliza de Allianz Assistance.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"N26 a tu lado","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Tanto para gestionar tus finanzas desde el sofá como si tienes que viajar al extranjero, puedes contar con la tranquilidad de que N26 estará siempre a tu lado, sobre todo en tiempos de una pandemia como la del COVID-19. Si todavía no eres de N26, puedes abrir tu cuenta bancaria ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fes-es\u002Fyou-tarjeta-para-viajar"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"value":"N26 You","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fes-es\u002Fyou-cuenta-autonomos-seguro-viaje"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"value":"N26 Business You","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fes-es\u002Fmetal"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"value":"N26 Metal","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" o ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fes-es\u002Fbusiness-metal"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"value":"N26 Business Metal","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" directamente desde el móvil, en pocos minutos y sin papeleos. Abre ya tu cuenta y empieza a disfrutar de numerosas ventajas premium; como cobertura de Allianz Assistance para viajes y para tu día a día, retiradas gratis en cajeros de todo el mundo, pagos y transferencias internacionales sin comisiones, ofertas y descuentos de marcas asociadas y mucho más.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"5EaQdKZJgsVic9wHayAHrM","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Vous avez besoin de voyager en période de COVID-19 et vous voulez éviter les déconvenues liées à la pandémie ? Nous avons une couverture pour vous.  ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pour les clients premium N26 You, N26 Business You, N26 Metal et N26 Business Metal, l'ensemble de couvertures voyage d'Allianz Assistance comprend désormais une couverture des risques liés aux épidémies et pandémies pour vos voyages nécessaires en période de pandémie du COVID-19, sans coût supplémentaire. Découvrez ci-dessous de quoi il s'agit et comment lancer une procédure de réclamation.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Couverture en cas d'annulation ou interruption de voyage","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ce n'est jamais agréable de devoir annuler ou couper court à un voyage, surtout lorsqu'il faut payer de sa poche. Si vous avez un compte N26 You, N26 Business You, N26 Metal ou N26 Business Metal, votre ensemble de couvertures inclut désormais les annulations et interruptions de voyage liées à la pandémie de COVID-19. La couverture des risques liés aux épidémies et pandémies s'applique à tous les voyages à l'étranger ainsi qu'à plus de 100 km du domicile dans votre pays de résidence effectués à partir du 22\u002F01\u002F2021.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Vous pouvez prétendre à une compensation lorsque vous devez annuler ou interrompre un voyage parce que vous ou votre compagnon de voyage est déclaré positif à une maladie épidémique ou liée à une pandémie, dont le COVID-19. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"De plus, vous êtes couverts à hauteur de 10 000 € si votre voyage est annulé ou interrompu car vous ou votre compagnon de voyage êtes contraints de vous placer en quarantaine après avoir été exposé à un virus. Dans ce cas précis, vous devez avoir été signalés personnellement et contraints à vous placer en quarantaine par les autorités publiques.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Veuillez noter que vous ne devez pas voyager à l’encontre des recommandations officielles d’un gouvernement ou des autorités publiques. Cette nouvelle couverture des risques liés aux épidémies et pandémies ne couvre pas les situations de quarantaine généralisée qui s'appliquent à l'ensemble de la population ou à l'ensemble d'un territoire de votre lieu de départ, de destination, ou traversé pendant votre voyage. Pour les détails de la couverture, veuillez vous référer aux conditions générales de la police. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Assistance pour les urgences médicales","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si vous avez besoin de voyager durant la pandémie, mieux vaut vous prémunir contre les situations inattendues. Pour vous permettre de voyager plus sereinement, les comptes premium N26 You, N26 Business You, N26 Metal et N26 Business Metal comprennent désormais une couverture des risques liés aux pandémies et épidémies pour vos voyages à l'étranger.C'est à dire que si vous tombez soudainement malades, que vous êtes blessés ou atteints d'un trouble médical en cours de voyage à l'étranger, y compris en cas de diagnostic positif au COVID-19, vous êtes couvert pour vos frais médicaux d'urgence, tels que votre hospitalisation, votre traitement médical, vos transports médicaux ou votre rapatriement si nécessaire.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"De plus, le service d'assistance médicale par téléphone d'Allianz Assistance est accessible 7 jours\u002F7 et 24 heures\u002F24 pour prendre en charge votre urgence, où que vous soyez dans le monde. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Veuillez noter que vous ne devez pas voyager à l’encontre des recommandations officielles d’un gouvernement ou des autorités publiques. Pour les détails de la couverture, veuillez vous référer aux conditions générales de la police. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Comment lancer une procédure de réclamation ?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pour lancer une procédure de réclamation, ouvrez l'application N26, allez sur \"","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Découvrir","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\" et dans la section \"","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Vos assurances","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\", sélectionnez la réclamation que vous souhaitez effectuer puis \"Commencer une procédure de réclamation\". Suivez ensuite les étapes indiquées pour faire parvenir à Allianz Assistance les documents nécessaires à votre procédure de réclamation. Les conditions générales habituelles de votre assurance Allianz Assistance s'appliquent.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"N26 est à vos côtés","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Que vous gériez votre budget depuis votre canapé ou que vous soyez en déplacement à l'étranger, vous pouvez toujours compter sur le soutien de N26, surtout en cette période de pandémie du COVID-19.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si vous n'êtes pas encore client chez N26, vous pouvez ouvrir un compte ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Ffr-fr\u002Fyou-carte-bancaire-sans-frais-etranger"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 You","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Ffr-fr\u002Fcompte-ban