gramme initiative (ALL)","it":"Header: World Food Programme initiative (ALL)"},"description":{"de":"Ein lächelndes kleines Mädchen mit einem Teller mit Essen in der Hand","en":"A smiling little girl with a plate of food in her hands","es":"Una niña sonriente con un plato de comida en la mano","fr":"Une petite fille souriante avec une assiette de nourriture dans sa main","it":"Una bambina sorridente con un piatto di cibo in mano"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002Fxmy5Ek3KIHTppiaKCy94P\u002F594116c54f078dc0aeca63a8cf187fd7\u002F2MC00010_WFP_N26_Banner_CRM_Blog_Header_DE_1200x600.jpg","details":{"size":363442,"image":{"width":1200,"height":600}},"fileName":"2MC00010_WFP_N26_Banner_CRM_Blog_Header_DE_1200x600.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002Fxmy5Ek3KIHTppiaKCy94P\u002Fe81a71b4649692eba68b5f2d01879f18\u002F2MC00010_WFP_N26_Banner_CRM_Blog_Header_EN_1200x600.jpg","details":{"size":363136,"image":{"width":1200,"height":600}},"fileName":"2MC00010_WFP_N26_Banner_CRM_Blog_Header_EN_1200x600.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002Fxmy5Ek3KIHTppiaKCy94P\u002F38f1c23008865326d2bec72a437c13c5\u002F2MC00010_WFP_N26_Banner_CRM_Blog_Header_1200x600_ES.jpg","details":{"size":363430,"image":{"width":1200,"height":600}},"fileName":"2MC00010_WFP_N26_Banner_CRM_Blog_Header_1200x600_ES.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002Fxmy5Ek3KIHTppiaKCy94P\u002Fb70f3dc8b21f5fbd7c77f2f9b7df5a22\u002F2MC00010_WFP_N26_Banner_CRM_Blog_Header_1200x600_FR.jpg","details":{"size":363086,"image":{"width":1200,"height":600}},"fileName":"2MC00010_WFP_N26_Banner_CRM_Blog_Header_1200x600_FR.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002Fxmy5Ek3KIHTppiaKCy94P\u002Fd1381a4a84fc72a69e574ecdde13beaa\u002F2MC00010_WFP_N26_Banner_CRM_Blog_Header_1200x600_IT.jpg","details":{"size":363147,"image":{"width":1200,"height":600}},"fileName":"2MC00010_WFP_N26_Banner_CRM_Blog_Header_1200x600_IT.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"categoryId":{"en":"company"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"27jlDrE1cQuQWOKooYAwYw"}}},"date":{"en":"2020-12-01"},"excerpt":{"de":"Hilf uns dabei, diese Kampagne zu verbreiten! Für jeden Online-Einkauf, den du bis 24. Dezember mit deiner Mastercard tätigst, spenden wir eine Mahlzeit an das World Food Programme.","en":"Please help us spread the word. For every online purchase made with your N26 Mastercard® before December 25, a meal will be donated to the United Nations World Food Programme.","es":"Corre la voz: por cada compra online realizada con tu Mastercard® N26 antes del 24 de diciembre, se donará un plato de comida al Programa Mundial de Alimentos.","fr":"Aidez-nous à passer le mot : pour tout achat en ligne effectué avant le 24 décembre avec votre Mastercard® N26, un repas sera offert au Programme Alimentaire Mondial.","it":"Spargi la voce: per ogni acquisto online effettuato con la tua Mastercard® N26 prima del 25 dicembre, verrà donato un pasto al World Food Programme delle Nazioni Unite."},"copy":{"de":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Je mehr wir teilen, desto mehr können wir erreichen. Nutze deine N26 Mastercard® oder melde dich noch heute an, um mitzumachen!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wir freuen uns, unsere Unterstützung der Initiative von Mastercard und dem World Food Programme bekanntzugeben! Für jeden Einkauf, den Kunden in Europa bis zum 24. Dezember online tätigen, spenden wir eine Mahlzeit für bedürftige Kinder an das World Food Programme.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Warum N26 mitmacht","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"2020 war kein einfaches Jahr. Wir sind uns unserer Rolle als Unternehmen, das wirklich etwas verändern kann, zunehmend bewusst. Wir haben uns aus einem Berliner Startup in eine weltweit agierende Bank mit Millionen Kunden entwickelt. Damit kommt Verantwortung einher – und die möchten wir wahrnehmen.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Aus diesem Grund haben wir uns entschieden, die Kampagne von Mastercard und dem World Food Programme der Vereinten Nationen im Dezember zu unterstützen.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Was ist das World Food Programme?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Das World Food Programme der Vereinten Nationen ist die größte humanitäre Hilfsorganisation der Welt und setzt sich für die Rettung von Leben in Notsituationen ein. Mit der Nahrungsmittelhilfe stellt sie die Weichen für Frieden, Stabilität und Wohlstand in Krisenländern und hilft Menschen dabei, Folgen von Krieg, Katastrophen und Klimawandel zu überwinden.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Welche Rolle spielt Mastercard dabei?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Mastercard und das World Food Programme arbeiten bereits seit 2012 zusammen. Dabei beschäftigen sie sich mit Themen wie Ernährung, Gesundheit, kognitive Entwicklung, Zugang zu Bildung und zukünftiges Einkommen. Wir bei N26 freuen uns sehr, diese Initiative unterstützen zu können.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wie funktioniert es?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Für jeden Einkauf, den du vom 1. bis einschließlich 24. Dezember online mit deiner N26 Mastercard® tätigst, spenden wir einen Betrag im Wert einer Mahlzeit für ein bedürftiges Kind an das World Food Programme*.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Warum uns das wichtig ist","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Dieses Jahr hat eines ganz klar gezeigt: Unsere Welt kann schnell aus den Fugen geraten. Mehr denn je ist uns bewusst, dass wir uns um unsere Mitmenschen und unsere Umwelt kümmern müssen. Wir stehen noch ganz am Anfang, aber heute tun wir den ersten Schritt in eine neue Richtung.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Spende noch mehr!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Du kannst – wenn du magst – noch mehr tun. Klicke auf den neuen \"Spenden\" Button in deiner N26 App, um eine zusätzliche Spende an das WFP zu senden!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1AppFull"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2AppMainAccount"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-12-10T10:15:06.606Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:27:17.356Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"de":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","en":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","es":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","fr":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","it":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)"},"description":{"de":"Der \"Spenden\" Button in der N26 App","en":"The \"Donate\" button in the N26 app","es":"El botón «Donar» en la app N26.","fr":"Le bouton \"Don\" dans l'application N26","it":"Il pulsante \"Dona\" nell'app N26"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F9b8ae187c632a2ffa34237eeef304f2f\u002F1_1_DE.png","details":{"size":809306,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_DE.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002Fc3182e3cb6302ecc6ba6240a771dd302\u002F1_1_EN.png","details":{"size":804939,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_EN.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F2f6d01e8b87574c17673ebf17aaf72ec\u002F1_1_ES.png","details":{"size":809605,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_ES.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F383e25c5b44f7da4227005ca87cc0c25\u002F1_1_FR.png","details":{"size":809472,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_FR.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F2e3ed6c69dbd38e056d78b9783f09827\u002F1_1_it.png","details":{"size":806032,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_it.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"*Was steht im Kleingedruckten?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Für jede Online-Transaktion, die vom 1. bis einschließlich 24. Dezember mit der N26 Mastercard in Europa getätigt wird, spendet N26 den Durchschnittswert einer Mahlzeit für ein bedürftiges Kind (0,20 €) an das World Food Programme. Der maximale Spendenbetrag beträgt 800.000 €. 100 % der durch N26 getätigten Spenden werden via Worldcoo überwiesen. 100 % aller Spenden durch Karteninhaber fließen direkt an das WFP. Auf den Bildern sind Schauspieler zu sehen, keine Hilfsempfänger des WFP. Die mit dem Fotografen-Vermerk WFP gekennzeichneten Fotos bilden Hilfsempfänger des WFP ab. Das WFP unterstützt keine unserer Produkte oder Dienstleistungen. Weitere Informationen über das WFP findest du auf wfp.org.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The more we share, the more impact we can have. Use your N26 Mastercard® or sign up today to take part.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"We’re excited to announce that we support the partnership between Mastercard and the World Food Programme in the month of December. For every online purchase our European customers make before 25 December, a meal will be donated to vulnerable children via the World Food Programme.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Why is N26 doing this?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"2020 hasn’t been easy. We are increasingly conscious of the role that a company like ours can play in supporting social topics. We’ve moved from being a Berlin start up to a truly global bank with millions of customers around the world and we want to take more of a stance—investing in, and supporting, organizations that are working to do the right thing.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"That’s why we have decided to support the partnership of Mastercard with the United Nations World Food Programme in the month of December.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"What is The World Food Programme?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The United Nations World Food Programme is the world’s largest humanitarian organization, saving lives in emergencies and using food assistance to build a pathway to peace, stability and prosperity for people recovering from conflict, disasters and the impact of climate change.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"How is Mastercard involved?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Mastercard and the World Food Programme have been working together since 2012 with a partnership focused on the transformational power of school meals, which can help improve children’s health, cognitive development, access to education, and future lifetime earnings. N26 is excited to support this initiative.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"How does it work?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"For every online purchase made with your N26 Mastercard® between December 1 and December 24, the value of one meal for a vulnerable child will be donated via the World Food Programme*.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Why is this important to us?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"This year has proven—beyond doubt—that our world is fragile, and taking care of those around us matters. It matters to our customers, to our employees and to us. Yes, we may be at the very beginning of this journey, but we want to make a start today.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Make an additional donation","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"You can provide additional support on top! If you want to make a donation to the WFP, please tap the new “donate” button in the N26 app.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1AppFull"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2AppMainAccount"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-12-10T10:15:06.606Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:27:17.356Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"de":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","en":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","es":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","fr":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","it":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)"},"description":{"de":"Der \"Spenden\" Button in der N26 App","en":"The \"Donate\" button in the N26 app","es":"El botón «Donar» en la app N26.","fr":"Le bouton \"Don\" dans l'application N26","it":"Il pulsante \"Dona\" nell'app N26"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F9b8ae187c632a2ffa34237eeef304f2f\u002F1_1_DE.png","details":{"size":809306,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_DE.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002Fc3182e3cb6302ecc6ba6240a771dd302\u002F1_1_EN.png","details":{"size":804939,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_EN.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F2f6d01e8b87574c17673ebf17aaf72ec\u002F1_1_ES.png","details":{"size":809605,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_ES.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F383e25c5b44f7da4227005ca87cc0c25\u002F1_1_FR.png","details":{"size":809472,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_FR.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F2e3ed6c69dbd38e056d78b9783f09827\u002F1_1_it.png","details":{"size":806032,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_it.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"*Is there any small print?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"For each N26 Mastercard transaction made online in Europe from 1 December – 24 December 2020, the average value of one meal for a vulnerable child (€0.20) will be donated to the World Food Programme up to a maximum donation of €800,000. 100% of the donation made by N26 will be transferred via Worldcoo and 100% of cardholder donations will be transferred to WFP directly. Images are of actors, not of WFP beneficiaries. Those photos marked with WFP photographer credit are of WFP beneficiaries. WFP does not endorse any product or service. For more information about WFP, visit wfp.org.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"nodeType":"document","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Cuanto más lo compartamos, mayor impacto conseguiremos. Usa tu Mastercard® N26 o únete hoy para participar.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Nos alegra anunciar que apoyamos la colaboración entre Mastercard y el Programa Mundial de Alimentos durante el mes de diciembre. Por cada compra online que realicen nuestros clientes europeos antes del 24 de diciembre, donaremos un plato de comida a niños desfavorecidos a través del Programa Mundial de Alimentos.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"¿Por qué hace esto N26?","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Como ya sabes, el 2020 no ha sido un año fácil. Cada vez somos más conscientes del papel que una empresa como la nuestra puede jugar a la hora de mejorar la realidad social. Hemos pasado de ser una startup en Berlín a convertirnos en un banco internacional con millones de clientes en todo el mundo, y queremos tener una actitud activa invirtiendo y apoyando a organizaciones que luchan por hacer lo correcto.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Por eso hemos decidido apoyar la colaboración de Mastercard con el Programa Internacional de Alimentos de las Naciones Unidas durante el mes de diciembre.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"¿Qué es el Programa Mundial de Alimentos?","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"El Programa Mundial de Alimentos de las Naciones Unidas es la organización humanitaria más grande del mundo, brindando asistencia alimentaria en situaciones de emergencia para crear vías de paz, estabilidad y prosperidad para las personas que se recuperan de conflictos bélicos, desastres naturales y del impacto del cambio climático.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"¿Cómo participa Mastercard?","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Mastercard y el Programa Mundial de Alimentos llevan trabajando juntos desde 2012 con una asociación centrada en el poder transformador de los menús escolares para mejorar la salud de los niños, así como su desarrollo cognitivo, su acceso a la educación y sus futuros salarios. En N26 nos complace apoyar esta iniciativa.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"¿Cómo funciona?","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Por cada transacción online que realicen nuestros clientes con su Mastercard® N26 entre el 1 y el 24 de diciembre, se donará un plato de comida al Programa Mundial de Alimentos (WFP)* para ayudar a niños en situación de vulnerabilidad en todo el mundo.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"¿Por qué nos parece importante?","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"No cabe duda de que este año ha servido para demostrar que el mundo es frágil y que debemos cuidar de los demás. Es importante para nuestros clientes, para nuestros empleados y para nosotros. Sabemos que esto solo es el comienzo de una aventura, y tenemos muchas ganas de iniciarla contigo.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Donar más","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Tú también puedes ayudar. Si quieres hacer una donación al WFP, pulsa en el nuevo botón «donar» en la app N26.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block","content":[],"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1AppFull"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2AppMainAccount"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-12-10T10:15:06.606Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:27:17.356Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"de":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","en":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","es":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","fr":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","it":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)"},"description":{"de":"Der \"Spenden\" Button in der N26 App","en":"The \"Donate\" button in the N26 app","es":"El botón «Donar» en la app N26.","fr":"Le bouton \"Don\" dans l'application N26","it":"Il pulsante \"Dona\" nell'app N26"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F9b8ae187c632a2ffa34237eeef304f2f\u002F1_1_DE.png","details":{"size":809306,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_DE.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002Fc3182e3cb6302ecc6ba6240a771dd302\u002F1_1_EN.png","details":{"size":804939,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_EN.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F2f6d01e8b87574c17673ebf17aaf72ec\u002F1_1_ES.png","details":{"size":809605,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_ES.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F383e25c5b44f7da4227005ca87cc0c25\u002F1_1_FR.png","details":{"size":809472,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_FR.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F2e3ed6c69dbd38e056d78b9783f09827\u002F1_1_it.png","details":{"size":806032,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_it.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"*¿Hay letra pequeña?","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Desde hoy, 1 de diciembre a las 12:00 (CET), hasta el 24 de diciembre a las 00:00 (CET), por cada transacción online realizada con la Mastercard® de N26 en Europa, se donará el valor medio de un menú escolar (0,20 €) al Programa Mundial de Alimentos hasta un máximo de 800.000 €. El 100 % de las donaciones realizadas por N26 se transferirán a través de Worldcoo y el 100 % de las donaciones realizadas por los clientes de N26 se transferirán directamente al Programa Mundial de Alimentos. En las imágenes aparecen actores, no usuarios del programa del WFP. Las imágenes firmadas por un fotógrafo del WFP son de usuarios del WFP.","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"text","value":" ","marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"text","value":"El WFP no promociona ningún producto o servicio. Para más información sobre el WFP, visita WFP.org.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}]},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Plus nous partagerons l’information, plus grand sera notre impact. Utilisez votre Mastercard® N26 ou ouvrez votre compte pour participer dès maintenant.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nous sommes ravis de vous annoncer le partenariat entre Mastercard et le Programme Alimentaire Mondial en décembre. Pour tout achat effectué en ligne par nos clients européens avant le 24 décembre, un repas sera offert aux enfants vulnérables dans le cadre du Programme Alimentaire Mondial.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pourquoi cette initiative de N26 ?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"2020 a été difficile. Une entreprise comme la nôtre devient de plus en plus consciente du rôle qu’elle peut jouer dans la société. Nous nous sommes beaucoup développés en quelques années et nous comptons désormais des millions de clients dans le monde. Nous souhaitons aujourd'hui prendre davantage position en soutenant des organisations et initiatives qui s’engagent pour des causes justes. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"C’est pour cette raison que nous avons décidé d’appuyer le partenariat de Mastercard avec le Programme Alimentaire Mondial des Nations Unies en décembre.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Qu’est-ce que le Programme alimentaire mondial ?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Le Programme Alimentaire Mondial des Nations Unies est la plus grande organisation humanitaire du monde, sauvant des vies dans les situations d’urgence et utilisant l’aide alimentaire pour ouvrir la voie à la paix, à la stabilité et à la prospérité pour les personnes qui sont exposées à un conflit, des catastrophes ou aux effets liés aux changements climatiques.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Quelle est l’implication de Mastercard ?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Mastercard et le Programme Alimentaire Mondial collaborent depuis 2012 dans le cadre d’un partenariat axé sur le pouvoir de transformation de l’école, qui permet d’améliorer la santé des enfants, le développement cognitif, l’accès à l’éducation et les revenus futurs. N26 est heureuse de soutenir cette initiative.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Comment cela fonctionne-t-il ?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pour toute transaction en ligne effectuée par nos clients avec leur N26 Mastercard® entre le 1er et le 24 décembre*, un repas sera offert au Programme alimentaire mondial* pour aider les enfants vulnérables dans le monde.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pourquoi est-ce important pour nous ?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nous avons constaté cette année que le monde était fragile et que prendre soin de ceux qui nous entourent était essentiel. C’est essentiel pour nos clients, nos employés, et pour nous. Ce n’est que le début, mais nous sommes déterminés à nous engager pour de justes causes dès aujourd’hui.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Donner plus","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Vous pouvez aussi contribuer davantage. Si vous souhaitez faire un don au PAM, vous pouvez cliquer sur le nouveau bouton « Don » dans l’application N26.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1AppFull"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2AppMainAccount"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2020-12-10T10:15:06.606Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:27:17.356Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"de":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","en":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","es":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","fr":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)","it":"WFP Initiative - Donation button (ALL)"},"description":{"de":"Der \"Spenden\" Button in der N26 App","en":"The \"Donate\" button in the N26 app","es":"El botón «Donar» en la app N26.","fr":"Le bouton \"Don\" dans l'application N26","it":"Il pulsante \"Dona\" nell'app N26"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F9b8ae187c632a2ffa34237eeef304f2f\u002F1_1_DE.png","details":{"size":809306,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_DE.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002Fc3182e3cb6302ecc6ba6240a771dd302\u002F1_1_EN.png","details":{"size":804939,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_EN.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F2f6d01e8b87574c17673ebf17aaf72ec\u002F1_1_ES.png","details":{"size":809605,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_ES.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F383e25c5b44f7da4227005ca87cc0c25\u002F1_1_FR.png","details":{"size":809472,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_FR.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F4YOq2Apl3ZVSEqWAne3vYq\u002F2e3ed6c69dbd38e056d78b9783f09827\u002F1_1_it.png","details":{"size":806032,"image":{"width":1200,"height":1200}},"fileName":"1_1_it.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"*Y a-t-il des petits caractères ?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pour chaque transaction N26 Mastercard effectuée en ligne en Europe du 1er au 24 décembre 2020, la valeur moyenne d'un repas pour un enfant vulnérable (0,20 €) sera reversée au Programme Alimentaire Mondial jusqu'à un don maximum de 800 000 €. 100 % du don effectué par N26 sera transféré via Worldcoo et 100 % des dons des titulaires de carte seront transférés directement au PAM. Les images sont celles d'acteurs et non de bénéficiaires du PAM. Les photos portant le crédit photographique du PAM sont des photos des bénéficiaires du PAM. Le PAM ne cautionne aucun produit ou service. Pour plus d'informations sur le PAM, visitez wfp.org.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Più condividiamo, maggiore è l'impatto che possiamo avere. Utilizza la tua Mastercard® N26 o apri oggi un conto per partecipare.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Siamo felici di annunciare il nostro sostegno alla collaborazione di Mastercard con il World Food Programme nel mese di dicembre. Per ogni acquisto online effettuato dai nostri clienti europei prima del 25 dicembre, doneremo un pasto ai bambini meno fortunati tramite il World Food Programme.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Perché N26 sostiene questa iniziativa?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Come sai, il 2020 non è stato un anno facile. Noi di N26 siamo sempre più consapevoli del ruolo che un'azienda come la nostra può ricoprire sostenendo questioni sociali. Siamo passati da essere una startup nata a Berlino a diventare una banca globale a tutti gli effetti, con milioni di clienti in tutto il mondo. Ecco perché vogliamo sostenere una causa ancora più grande, supportando le organizzazioni che cercano di fare la cosa giusta.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Per questo motivo, abbiamo deciso di sostenere la collaborazione di Mastercard con il World Food Programme delle Nazioni Unite nel mese di dicembre.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Cos'è il World Food Programme?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Il World Food Programme (Programma Alimentare Mondiale) delle Nazioni Unite è l'organizzazione umanitaria più grande al mondo. Il suo obiettivo è salvare vite durante le crisi e fornire assistenza alimentare per aiutare a portare pace, stabilità e prosperità alle vittime di conflitti, catastrofi naturali e conseguenze del cambiamento climatico.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"In che modo è coinvolta Mastercard?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Mastercard e il World Food Programme collaborano dal 2012 in una partnership concentrata sul potere trasformazionale dei pasti scolastici che possono contribuire a migliorare la salute, lo sviluppo cognitivo, l'accesso dei bambini all'istruzione e quindi a una retribuzione futura stabile. Noi di N26 siamo fieri di sostenere questa iniziativa.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Come funziona?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Per ogni transazione effettuata online utilizzando una Mastercard® N26 tra l'1 e il 24 dicembre, N26 donerà un pasto al World Food Programme* a sostegno dei bambini meno fortunati in tutto il mondo.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Perché è importante per noi?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Quest'anno ha rivelato senza ombra di dubbio quanto il nostro mondo sia fragile e che prendersi cura di chi ci sta attorno è importante. È importante per i nostri clienti, per i nostri collaboratori e per noi stessi. Sì, siamo solo all'inizio di questo viaggio, ma oggi vogliamo fare il primo passo.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Dona di più","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Anche il tuo contributo è prezioso. Se vuoi fare una donazione aggiuntiva a favore del WFP, clicca sul pulsante “Dona” nell'app N26.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1AppFull"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","l