:1958012,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"2002_Booking_BlogHeader.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F6kldODlJ2LVos4yGh2G3sa\u002F6a4bf11e9391b28031622a3df23477f9\u002F2002_Booking_BlogHeader.png","details":{"size":1958012,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"2002_Booking_BlogHeader.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F6kldODlJ2LVos4yGh2G3sa\u002F3f1d4138f551e5a4726500acf87dc986\u002F2002_Booking_BlogHeader.png","details":{"size":1958012,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"2002_Booking_BlogHeader.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F6kldODlJ2LVos4yGh2G3sa\u002Fde149bc96bceb10eaf71949d39911754\u002F2002_Booking_BlogHeader.png","details":{"size":1958012,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"2002_Booking_BlogHeader.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"categoryId":{"en":"company"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"27jlDrE1cQuQWOKooYAwYw"}}},"date":{"en":"2020-02-11"},"excerpt":{"de":"Entdecke mit Booking.com eine neue Art zu Reisen und erhalte bis zu 10 % Cashback, wenn du einen Aufenthalt mit deiner N26 Mastercard buchst.","en":"Travel smarter with Booking.com—get up to 10% cashback when you book a stay with your N26 Mastercard, and more.","es":"Viaja adonde quieras con Booking.com y aprovecha esta oferta exclusiva: hasta un 10% de reembolso al reservar tu estancia con tu Mastercard N26.","fr":"Déplacez-vous où vous voulez avec Booking.com, et profitez d’une offre exclusive : jusqu’à 10 % de cashback lorsque vous réservez votre séjour avec votre Mastercard N26.","it":"Preparati all’arrivo delle vacanze con un’offerta per le tue prenotazioni su Booking.com."},"copy":{"de":{"nodeType":"document","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Hast du schon deine Reisepläne für 2020 gemacht? Wir haben uns vor dem Beginn der Ferienzeit mit einer der weltweit führenden Reiseplattformen zusammengetan und unsere Partnerschaft ausgebaut – damit du bei der Buchung deiner nächsten Unterkunft sparen kannst.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Egal, wo es dich hinverschlägt und welche Abenteuer du planst, mit Booking.com erhältst du als N26 Kunde bis zu 10 % Cashback auf die Buchung einer Unterkunft. Außerdem profitierst du von mindestens 20 % Rabatt auf ausgewählte Unterkünfte – so kannst du nochmal ordentlich sparen und dein Geld für Wichtigeres ausgeben, wie spannende Tagesausflüge oder Aktivitäten an deinem Reiseziel. Du bist Mitglied des Booking.com Genius-Treueprogramms? Noch besser! Als Genius-Mitglied kannst du durch dieses Angebot Treuepunkte sammeln und noch mehr Reiseprämien abräumen!","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block","content":[],"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"7928Jdry4mzvHHUJJhtghz","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Falls du schon N26 Kunde bist, kannst du das N26 x Booking.com-Angebot einfach auf der Seite ","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"hyperlink","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"www.booking.com\u002Fn26offer","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.booking.com\u002Fn26offer"}},{"nodeType":"text","value":" einlösen. Achte darauf, deine N26 Mastercard als Zahlungsmittel zu verwenden. Das Angebot läuft vom 11. Februar bis zum 31. Mai 2020, du hast also noch genug Zeit, deine nächste Reise zu planen. Du erhältst dein Cashback von Booking.com mindestens 64 Tage nach dem Ende deines Aufenthaltes. So einfach kann es sein.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Du hast noch kein N26 Bankkonto? Keine Sorge! Du brauchst nur wenige Minuten, um ein Konto zu eröffnen und vom N26 x Booking.com-Deal zu profitieren. Mit N26 bist du optimal auf deine Reise vorbereitet: keine versteckten Gebühren, kostenlose Zahlungen weltweit – in jeder Währung – und vieles mehr. Wir streben immer danach, das Leben einfacher zu machen und mehr Flexibilität bieten zu können – für Reisen, Finanzen und mehr. ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"hyperlink","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Hier erfährst du mehr.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fbooking"}},{"nodeType":"text","value":"\nEntdecke die Welt mit N26 und Booking.com!","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}]},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"With 2020 finally in full swing, it’s time to consider planning your next adventure. Ahead of the upcoming travel season, we’ve expanded our partnership with one of the world’s leading travel platforms to help you save more when booking a place to stay. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Whatever your interests and wherever in the world you choose to go, Booking.com is giving N26 customers up to 10% cashback when you book a place to stay through their website. Alongside this, also benefit from at least 20% off selected accommodation for even greater savings, meaning you can spend your hard-earned cash on the things that really matter once you get to your destination. Part of Booking.com’s Genius loyalty program? Even better! As a Genius member, tap into this opportunity to level up and unlock even more travel rewards.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"To enjoy this N26 x Booking.com offer as an existing customer, just head over to ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fbooking.com\u002Fn26offer"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"www.booking.com\u002Fn26offer","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" and pay for your chosen accommodation with your N26 Mastercard—with this deal being available from February 11 through to May 31, 2020, there’s plenty of time to plan your perfect getaway. After you complete your stay and check-out, you’ll receive your cashback from Booking.com in at least 64 days. It’s as simple as that.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"If you don’t have a N26 bank account—no worries! You can sign up for one in a matter of minutes to benefit from this N26 x Booking.com deal, and enjoy other travel perks such as free payments in any currency worldwide, no hidden fees abroad, and much more. It’s just another way that we’re constantly striving to streamline your life by giving you more flexibility while traveling, and helping you save more on-the-go.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"To learn more, ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fbooking"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"visit this page.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Go anywhere with Booking.com and N26.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ahora que acabamos de estrenar 2020, es hora de empezar a pensar en tu próxima aventura. Y para que puedas planificar tus vacaciones con tiempo, hemos ampliado nuestra colaboración con la plataforma de viajes líder para que ahorres aún más al reservar tus alojamientos. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Da igual si eres más de playa que de montaña o si te gusta más Asia que América; sea cual sea tu destino, Booking.com ofrece a los clientes de N26 ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"hasta un 10% de reembolso","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" al reservar tu estancia en su web. Y para que ahorres aún más, te ofrecemos un 20% de descuento extra en una selección de alojamientos. ¿Eres parte del programa Genius de Booking.com? ¡Mejor aún! Como miembro Genius puedes aprovechar esta oportunidad para subir de nivel y desbloquear más ventajas y descuentos en tus viajes. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si ya eres cliente de N26, para disfrutar de esta oferta solo tienes que ir a www.booking.com\u002Fn26offer y reservar el alojamiento elegido con tu Mastercard N26 entre el 11 de febrero y el 31 de mayo de 2020. ¡Tienes tiempo de sobra para planificar la escapada perfecta! Una vez finalices tu estancia y realices el check-out, recibirás tu reembolso de Booking.com en los siguientes 64 días. ¡Así de fácil! ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si todavía no eres cliente de N26, ¡no te preocupes! Puedes abrir tu cuenta en  cuestión de minutos y beneficiarte de esta oferta de N26 y Booking.com, así como de otras ventajas como pagar sin comisiones en cualquier moneda del mundo y con el tipo de cambio oficial de Mastercard. Esta es solo otra forma de ayudarte a ahorrar y  de darte más ventajas y flexibilidad en tus viajes. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Para más información, visita ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fes-es\u002Fbooking"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"esta página","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Descubre el mundo con Booking.com y N26.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"L’année 2020 a commencé, et vous pensez peut-être déjà à planifier vos prochaines vacances. Pour vous permettre d’économiser en organisant votre prochain séjour, nous avons prolongé notre partenariat avec Booking.com, l’une des plus grandes plateformes de réservation de séjours en ligne.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Quelle que soit votre destination, Booking.com vous propose un cashback allant jusqu’à 10 % lorsque vous réservez votre séjour depuis leur site internet. Vous bénéficiez également d’au moins 20 % de réduction sur une sélection de destinations, pour vous permettre de profiter encore plus de vos vacances. Vous faites partie du programme de fidélité Booking.com “Genius” ? Cette offre vous permet aussi de cumuler des points et donc de recevoir de nouvelles récompenses pour vos futurs voyages.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pour profiter de cette offre si vous êtes déjà client N26, rendez-vous directement sur ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.booking.com\u002Fn26offer"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"www.booking.com\u002Fn26offer","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":". Il vous suffira alors de choisir vos dates de séjour et votre hébergement, puis de régler votre réservation avec votre Mastercard N26. Vous recevrez ensuite le montant de votre cashback de Booking.com au plus tôt 64 jours après la fin de votre séjour. C’est aussi simple que cela. L’offre est valable pour la réservation d'un séjour entre avant le 31 mai 2020*.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si vous n’avez pas encore de compte bancaire N26, c’est sûrement le moment pour vous de découvrir une nouvelle expérience bancaire, sans paperasse ni frais cachés et 100 % Mobile.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"L’ouverture d’un compte N26 est gratuite et ne prend que 8 minutes. Votre Mastercard vous permet notamment de régler vos achats par carte bancaire partout dans le monde, sans aucuns frais de change. Les comptes premium N26 proposent également les retraits en devises sans frais de change, un ensemble d’assurances pour le quotidien, les déplacements et les voyages, et bien d’autres avantages…","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"*Pour en savoir plus et prendre connaissance des conditions générales, ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Ffr-fr\u002Fbooking"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"rendez-vous sur cette page","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nous espérons que ce partenariat vous offrira plus de flexibilité lors de vos séjours et nous vous souhaitons de beaux voyages.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ora che ci siamo lasciati gennaio alle spalle e la primavera non sembra più così lontana, è il momento perfetto per iniziare a organizzare la tua prossima avventura!\nPer l’occasione, abbiamo ampliato la nostra collaborazione con una delle piattaforme digitali leader nel settore dei viaggi per aiutarti a risparmiare quando prenoti le tue vacanze.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Non importa la tua destinazione: che si tratti di un weekend lungo in una capitale europea o del viaggio della vita in Giappone, Booking.com offre fino al 10% di cashback a tutti i clienti N26 che prenotano un soggiorno tramite il loro sito. In più, puoi approfittare di un ulteriore sconto minimo del 20% su destinazioni selezionate: perfetto per regalarti una vacanza e godertela senza pensieri!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ma le buone notizie non finiscono qui. Hai aderito al programma fedeltà Genius di Booking.com? In questo caso, puoi accumulare bonus di viaggio e ottenere ancora più sconti. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Sei già cliente N26? Per approfittare di questa offerta, visita la pagina ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.booking.com\u002Fn26offer"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"www.booking.com\u002Fn26offer","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" e prenota un soggiorno a tua scelta con la tua Mastercard N26. La promozione è valida dall’11 febbraio al 31 maggio 2020, così hai tutto il tempo per organizzare la vacanza perfetta. Al termine del tuo soggiorno, riceverai il tuo cashback da Booking.com dopo un minimo di 64 giorni. Semplice, no?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Se non hai ancora un conto N26, non preoccuparti! Puoi aprire il tuo in pochi minuti e approfittare subito dell’offerta di N26 e Booking.com e di tanti altri vantaggi per i tuoi viaggi, come pagamenti gratuiti in qualsiasi valuta, zero commissioni nascoste all’estero e pieno controllo del tuo conto da smartphone, ovunque tu sia. Apri un conto N26 e inizia a viaggiare risparmiando!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Vuoi saperne di più? ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fit-it\u002Fbooking"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Visita questa pagina.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Esplora il mondo con N26 e Booking.com!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"pt":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"}},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2JUja2o7P30wSfZIDFGBkG"}}]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"Xox6DHY8uqYKuWbranop2"}}}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"P3GS7bcL76LMlJpzB2FZs","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-10-26T13:49:59.725Z","updatedAt":"2020-10-27T15:55:31.694Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"redirect"}}},"fields":{"from":{"en":"\u002Fen-eu\u002Fopen-n26-account"},"to":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"3zUyLAIGliAUiqoG0C20qO","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2017-09-25T10:05:40.666Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-11T10:16:38.492Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":23,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"page"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"en":"Standard Bank Account Page (EU)"},"countryCodes":{"en":["EU"]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7uCTUnv69iosicSg24yIcO"}}},"trackingName":{"en":"accountPage"},"productPreference":{"en":"n26Card"},"ctaLink":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4Ulnjvp5kfSlz7L3LIy1rt"}}},"seaPage":{"en":false},"headerFooterMode":{"en":"DEFAULT"},"isIndexed":{"en":true},"title":{"en":"Free Bank Account"},"slug":{"en":"free-bank-account"},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"DQSeZKV9CNnUydu6xSJyj"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","