:"ContentType","id":"blogPost"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"de":"Bekanntgabe unserer $160 Millionen Series C Finanzierungsrunde und 850k+ Kunden.","en":"Blog: Announcing our $160 million Series C funding round and 850k+ customers (ALL, UK, US)","es":"Nueva ronda de financiación: 160 millones de dólares en Serie C. ¡Y más de 850.000 clientes!","fr":"N26 lève 160 millions de dollars en Série C et compte désormais plus de 850 000 utilisateurs.","it":"Annunciamo $160 milioni di Serie C funding e 850.000 clienti"},"countryCodes":{"en":["DE","AT","FR","IT","ES","EU","CH"]},"title":{"de":"Bekanntgabe unserer $160 Millionen Series C Finanzierungsrunde und 850k+ Kunden.","en":"Announcing our $160 million Series C funding round and 850k+ customers","es":"Nueva ronda de financiación: 160 millones de dólares en Serie C. ¡Y más de 850.000 clientes!","fr":"N26 lève 160 millions de dollars en Série C et compte désormais plus de 850 000 utilisateurs.","it":"Annunciamo $160 milioni di Serie C funding e 850.000 clienti"},"slug":{"de":"bekanntgabe-unserer-160-millionen-series-c-finanzierungsrunde-und-850k-kunden","en":"160-million-series-c-funding-round-and-850k-customers","es":"nueva-ronda-de-financiacion-160-millones-de-dolares-en-serie-c-y-mas-de-850-000-clientes","fr":"n26-leve-160-millions-de-dollars-en-serie-c-et-plus-de-850-000-utilisateurs","it":"annunciamo-160-milioni-di-serie-c-funding-e-850-000-clienti"},"previewImage":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1AppFull"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2AppMainAccount"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"3ivlngSmHmg0Ocw2o6U6AM","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-04-27T11:52:11.717Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:32:58.904Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Bekanntgabe unserer $160 Millionen Series C Finanzierungsrunde und 850k+ Kunden.","en":"Announcing our $160 million Series C funding round and 850k+ customers","es":"Nueva ronda de financiación: 160 millones de dólares en Serie C. ¡Y más de 850.000 clientes!","fr":"N26 lève 160 millions de dollars en Série C et compte désormais plus de 850 000 utilisateurs.","it":"Annunciamo $160 milioni di Serie C funding e 850.000 clienti"},"description":{"de":"iPhone X und eine N26-Karte auf einem Tisch","en":"iPhone X and an N26 card on a table","es":"El iPhone X y una tarjeta N26 sobre una mesa","fr":"iPhone X et une carte N26 sur une table","it":"iPhone X e una carta N26 su un tavolo"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ivlngSmHmg0Ocw2o6U6AM\u002Fb83067449287d3a0f89c59ba8e2d83f2\u002F1803-funding-announcement--og-de.jpg","details":{"size":192165,"image":{"width":1200,"height":630}},"fileName":"1803-funding-announcement--og-de.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ivlngSmHmg0Ocw2o6U6AM\u002Fb7c784ce7b09625eb6f2ef21234226ed\u002F1803-funding-announcement--og-en-.jpg","details":{"size":914195,"image":{"width":1200,"height":630}},"fileName":"1803-funding-announcement--og-en-.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ivlngSmHmg0Ocw2o6U6AM\u002F0d1a99682fbdc0f73c9e463b820ebfc0\u002F1803-funding-announcement--og-es.jpg","details":{"size":189491,"image":{"width":1200,"height":630}},"fileName":"1803-funding-announcement--og-es.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ivlngSmHmg0Ocw2o6U6AM\u002F93232e588faaab74525f0486de39fa8d\u002F1803-funding-announcement--og-fr.jpg","details":{"size":194021,"image":{"width":1200,"height":630}},"fileName":"1803-funding-announcement--og-fr.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ivlngSmHmg0Ocw2o6U6AM\u002F83ae802d10ac3ff71e6ae4025a866210\u002F1803-funding-announcement--og-it.jpg","details":{"size":191451,"image":{"width":1200,"height":630}},"fileName":"1803-funding-announcement--og-it.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"categoryId":{"en":"company"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"27jlDrE1cQuQWOKooYAwYw"}}},"date":{"en":"2018-03-20"},"excerpt":{"de":"Mit viel Freude geben wir den Abschluss unserer Series C Finanzierungsrunde bekannt. Angeführt von Allianz X und Tencent wurden in dieser Runde $160 Millionen investiert.","en":"We're thrilled to announce that we have just closed our Series C round, with additional funding of USD 160 million led by Allianz X and Tencent.","es":"Estamos encantados de anunciar que hemos cerrado nuestra ronda de financiación de Serie C, con una cantidad de 160 millones de dólares y liderada por Allianz X y Tencent. ","fr":"Nous sommes très heureux de vous annoncer que nous venons de clore une levée de fonds en Série C d’un montant de 160 millions de dollars. ","it":"Siamo orgogliosi di annunciare che abbiamo appena chiuso la Serie C di finanziamento, con un ulteriore ammontare pari a 160 milioni di dollari USA, guidata da Allianz X e Tencent."},"copy":{"de":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"10.01.2019 - Update: N26 verkündet Series D Finanzierungsrunde in Höhe von 300 Millionen US-Dollar. ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fblog\u002Fn26-series-d-finanzierungsrunde-2019"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Jetzt mehr erfahren.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Es gibt aufregende Neuigkeiten.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Mit viel Freude geben wir den Abschluss unserer Series C Finanzierungsrunde bekannt. Angeführt von Allianz X und Tencent wurden in dieser Runde $160 Millionen investiert. Das stellt eine Rekordsumme für die deutsche Fintech-Szene dar und ist eine der höchsten Equity Funding Runden in Europa. Damit beträgt das gesamte Funding unseres Unternehmens nun $215 Millionen. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Investition in die Zukunft: Unsere $160 Millionen Series C Finanzierungsrunde","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wir sind davon überzeugt, dass Allianz X und Tencent die idealen Partner sind, um N26 als Marktführer im Mobile Banking zu etablieren. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wir freuen uns sehr, Allianz und Tencent als Investoren an Bord zu haben. Allianz X ist die strategische Investmentgesellschaft der Allianz Gruppe, Marktführer bei Versicherungsdienstleistungen und im Asset Management. Wir wissen die langjährige Erfahrung und das große öffentliche Vertrauen von Allianz sehr zu schätzen. Tencent ist mit Produkten wie WeChat und QQ ein Pionier im Bereich der sozialen Medien und Online-Zahlungen und ist bis zum Weltmarktführer aufgestiegen. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Doch das ist noch nicht alles: Unsere Kundenzahl ist seit der letzten Bekanntgabe im August 2017 von 500.000 auf über 850.000 angestiegen. Hierzu mehr in unserer Pressemitteilung. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Unsere neueste Finanzierungsrunde stellt aber mehr als nur einen finanziellen Erfolg dar. Sie ist gleichzeitig eine klare Validierung unserer Vision, eine Bank zu schaffen, die jeder liebt.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Für unsere Kunden bedeutet die Finanzierungsrunde ein direktes Investment in unser Produkt. Wir arbeiten an neuen Features, die Banking noch smarter und einfacher machen. Mit Hilfe von künstlicher Intelligenz schaffen wir eine personalisierte Banking-Erfahrung für unsere Kunden, die genau auf die Bedürfnisse des Einzelnen zugeschnitten ist.  ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Auch geht es mit der internationalen Expansion rasant weiter voran. Im Laufe dieses Jahres werden wir mit N26 auch in den USA und in Großbritannien an den Start gehen. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wir können es kaum erwarten euch zu zeigen, was wir noch alles geplant haben und versprechen, dass das Beste noch kommt. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"10\u002F01\u002F2019 - Update: N26 closes Series D funding round with an incredible $300 million. Read more about it ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-de\u002Fblog\u002Fn26-series-d-funding-round-2019"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"here","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Today is a big day.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"We're thrilled to announce that we have just closed our Series C round, with additional funding of USD 160 million led by Allianz X and Tencent. This is a record for this type of funding in the German fintech industry—and one of the biggest across Europe—bringing our total funding to date to $215 million. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Investing in the future: our $160 million Series C funding","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"We believe that both Allianz X and Tencent are the perfect choice to help make N26 a market leader in mobile banking.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Allianz and Tencent joining our family of existing investors is an incredible achievement that we’re very proud of. Allianz is one of the world’s largest asset management and leading insurance firms and is considered one of the most trusted brands in the financial services industry. Tencent has gone from a pioneer to market leader in social media, gaming, e-commerce, and mobile payments in China. Its flagship product WeChat now has over one billion active monthly users. It recently even surpassed Facebook in market value. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The good news doesn’t stop there, though. We now have over 850.000 customers! \nThat’s a big jump from our 500.000 announcement in August 2017. You can read more about it in the press release here.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Looking ahead, we’re very excited about what this latest funding round represents. It’s not just the amount of money we raised. To us, it’s a confirmation of our vision and our mission to build a bank the world loves to use. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"For customers, this is a direct investment in our product. With it, we’ll be able to invest in making  banking even more intelligent and simpler. We will go a step further by making banking even smarter and more personalized for all of our customers through the use of artificial intelligence. \nWe’re pushing ahead with our international expansion to the UK and US, where we are launching later this year. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"We can't wait to show you what's coming next. And promise that the best is yet to come. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"10\u002F01\u002F2019 - N26 cierra su ronda de financiación Serie D con 300 millones de dólares. Descubre más ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fes-es\u002Fblog\u002Fn26-ronda-financiacion-serie-d-2019"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"aquí","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"¡Hoy es un gran día!\nEstamos encantados de anunciar que hemos cerrado nuestra ronda de financiación de Serie C, con una cantidad de 160 millones de dólares y liderada por Allianz X y Tencent. Todo un récord dentro del sector fintech en Alemania, y una de las financiaciones más altas que se ha visto en Europa. En total, sumando las tres rondas, la financiación asciende a 215 millones de dólares.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Invertimos en el futuro: nuestra ronda Serie C de 160 millones de dólares","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Creemos que tanto Allianz como Tencent son la elección correcta para seguir avanzando hasta convertirnos en líderes del mercado.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Allianz y Tencent se unen a nuestra familia de inversores, y estamos muy orgullosos de esto. Allianz X es la unidad de inversión digital del Grupo Allianz, uno de los grupos aseguradores y proveedores de servicios financieros más importantes del mundo. Tencent ha pasado de ser pionera a ser líder de mercado en redes sociales, juegos, comercio electrónico y pagos móviles en China. Su producto insignia WeChat (conocido como Weixin en China) con mil millones de usuarios activos al mes. Y hace poco que ha sobrepasado a Facebook en capitalización bursátil. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Las buenas noticias no llegan solas. ¡Ya contamos con más de 850.000 clientes! Es un gran salto desde que en agosto de 2017 anunciamos los 500.000. Puedes leer más en la nota de prensa.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Volviendo a la ronda Serie C, estamos muy contentos por lo que esta financiación significa. No es solo por la cantidad de dinero que hemos logrado para nuestro negocio; para nosotros es una confirmación de que nuestra visión y nuestra misión tienen sentido hoy en día. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Para los clientes, esto significa que invertimos directamente en ellos y en nuestro producto. Con esta financiación podremos construir y ofrecer un banco más inteligente y simple. Queremos dar un paso más, y hacer que la experiencia bancaria esté todavía más personalizada para todos los clientes, y para ello recurriremos a la inteligencia artificial.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pero esto no acaba aquí. Seguimos trabajando duramente en nuestra expansión hacia Estados Unidos y Reino Unido, que tendrán lugar este año 2018.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nos morimos de ganas de enseñaros qué viene después. Lo mejor está todavía por llegar.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"10\u002F01\u002F2019 - N26 a levé 300 millions de dollars en Série D. ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Ffr-fr\u002Fblog\u002Fn26-levee-de-fonds-serie-d"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"En savoir plus","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nous sommes très heureux de vous annoncer que nous venons de clore une levée de fonds en Série C d’un montant de 160 millions de dollars. Les principaux investisseurs sont Allianz X et Tencent. Cette levée de fonds (hors introduction en bourse) est un record dans le monde des fintechs en Allemagne, mais aussi l’une des plus importantes en Europe. Depuis sa création, N26 a ainsi levé 215 millions de dollars.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Un investissement dans le futur : notre levée de fonds de 160 millions de dollars en Série C","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nous sommes convaincus que Allianz X et Tencent sont des partenaires de choix pour faire de N26 un leader sur le marché de la banque mobile. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nous sommes très fiers de l’accomplissement que représente l’arrivée d’Allianz X et Tencent parmi nos investisseurs. Allianz est l’une des entreprises les plus importantes dans les domaines de la gestion d’actifs et de l’assurance à travers le monde et est considérée comme l’une des marques les plus fiables dans l’industrie des services financiers. Tencent était un pionnier des réseaux sociaux, des jeux en ligne, du commerce en ligne et des paiements mobiles en Chine et, est désormais devenu le leader de ce marché. Son produit phare, WeChat, compte désormais plus d’un milliard d’utilisateurs actifs chaque mois. Il a récemment dépassé Facebook en termes de valeur de marché. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ce n’est pas la seule bonne nouvelle. Nous avons désormais plus de 850 000 utilisateurs. C’est une grande avancée depuis l’annonce de nos 500 000 utilisateurs en août 2017. Vous trouverez plus d’informations à ce sujet dans notre communiqué de presse ici. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nous sommes très enthousiastes à propos de ce que cet investissement représente pour l’avenir, et ce n’est pas seulement lié au montant de cette levée de fonds. Pour nous, il représente la validation de notre vision et de notre mission : construire la banque que tout le monde aime utiliser. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pour nos utilisateurs, c’est un investissement direct dans notre produit. Grâce à lui, nous allons pouvoir investir pour rendre N26 encore plus simple et intuitive. Nous allons ainsi franchir une étape supplémentaire en rendant la banque plus intelligente et plus personnalisée pour tous nos utilisateurs, grâce au recours à l’intelligence artificielle par exemple. \nNous poursuivons également notre évolution avec notre expansion internationale au Royaume-Uni et aux États-Unis, où nous allons nous lancer cette année. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nous avons hâte de partager avec vous nos nouveaux projets qui arriveront cette année. \nLe meilleur est à venir. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"10\u002F01\u002F2019 - AGGIORNAMENTO: N26 chiude un round di finanziamento di Serie D da 300 milioni di dollari USA. Scopri di più ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fit-it\u002Fblog\u002Fn26-round-finanziamento-serie-d-2019"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"qui","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Oggi è un grande giorno!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Siamo orgogliosi di annunciare che abbiamo appena chiuso la Serie C di finanziamento, con un ulteriore ammontare pari a 160 milioni di dollari USA, guidata da Allianz X e Tencent. Si tratta di un record per questa tipologia di finanziamenti nell’industria Fintech in Germania e uno dei più grandi in Europa, portando l’ammontare totale di finanziamenti raccolti da N26 a 215 milioni di dollari USA. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Investire nel futuro: il nostro round di finanziamenti Serie C da 160 milioni di dollari USA","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Crediamo che Allianz X e Tencent siano la scelta giusta per aiutare N26 a diventare leader del mercato mobile banking. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Allianz e Tencent si uniscono ai nostri investitori già esistenti: questo rappresenta un grande traguardo di cui siamo molto orgogliosi. Allianz è una delle più grandi società di assicurazioni e di gestione patrimoniale al mondo ed una delle più  rispettate e di fiducia nel settore dei servizi finanziari. Tencent è passata dalla posizione di pioniere a quella di leader del mercato, in Cina, nei segmenti social media, giochi, e-commerce e pagamenti tramite dispositivi mobili. Con il suo prodotto di punta, la piattaforma di comunicazione WeChat (conosciuto in Cina come Weixin), che conta un miliardo di utenti attivi mensili, Tencent ha recentemente superato il valore di mercato di Facebook. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Le buone notizie non finiscono qui. Abbiamo ora più di 850.000 clienti!\nUn grande passo avanti da quando abbiamo annunciato i nostri 500.000 clienti ad agosto 2017. Puoi leggere ulteriori dettagli nel nostro comunicato stampa qui. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Guardando al futuro, siamo molto entusiasti riguardo quanto rappresentato da questo nuovo round di finanziamento. Non si tratta soltanto dell’ammontare di denaro raccolto, per noi è una conferma della nostra visione e missione di creare la banca tutto il mondo possa amare, da parte di leader del mercato.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Per i clienti, questo rappresenta un investimento diretto sul nostro prodotto. Con esso, saremo in grado di investire di più con l’obiettivo di rendere l’esperienza bancaria ancora più intelligente e semplice. Una spinta ulteriore nella nostra espansione internazionale in USA e Regno Unito, dove lanceremo ufficialmente entro la fine di questo anno. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Non vediamo l’ora di mostrarti cosa abbiamo in mente e ti assicuriamo che il meglio deve ancora venire!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"pt":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"}},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4Mo0FgNaxioQQKySWmEEG8"}}]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7clAbM3DpKeqcIeWOWow8I"}}}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"3jhPG9bMILr3JqDQpJdFXm","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-10-26T14:11:01.835Z","updatedAt":"2020-10-27T15:55:05.750Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link