lla somma di persone che stanno utilizzando Spaces."},"copy":{"de":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wenn ihr Fans der Tech-Industrie seid  und letzte Woche bei ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Ftechcrunch.com\u002F2018\u002F11\u002F30\u002Fn26-tandem-disrupt-berlin\u002F"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Disrupt Berlin","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" aufgepasst habt, habt ihr vielleicht schon die tollen Neuigkeiten mitbekommen: wir wachsen rasant und haben nun mehr als zwei Millionen Kunden. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Das mag vielleicht nur wie eine Zahl erscheinen, aber wir sind sehr stolz darauf. Die Ankündigung folgt nämlich unserer Ankündigung aus Oktober, dass wir auf 1,5 Millionen Kunden gewachsen sind. Das zeigt, dass wir mit einem ordentlichen Tempo voranschreiten und dementsprechend auch in neue Märkte einsteigen können, wie zum Beispiel die USA. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Seit Oktober hat sich einiges verändert. Wir sind nun auch im Vereinigten Königreich vertreten - das ist unser erster Markt in einer anderen Währung. Das N26 Euro-Konto ist auch in verschiedenen neuen europäischen Ländern verfügbar, wie zum Beispiel Polen, Norwegen, Schweden, Island und Liechtenstein. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Seid ihr neugierig, was das in konkreten Zahlen bedeutet? Wir haben euch eine schöne Infographic zusammengestellt. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"6LKPd1wAFyIMQKsSo6KWkI","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-12-12T15:24:04.194Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:32:58.879Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3},"fields":{"title":{"de":"2 Millionen Kunden in 24 Ländern","en":"2 million customers in 24 markets","es":"2 millones de clientes en 24 países","it":"2 milioni di clienti in 24 paesi"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F6LKPd1wAFyIMQKsSo6KWkI\u002Fe8f0de4bb368e27b087fd4caa7f055b5\u002F1812_2MillionCustomer_PR_Announcement_DE_Body_copy.jpg","details":{"size":464201,"image":{"width":808,"height":1432}},"fileName":"1812_2MillionCustomer_PR Announcement_DE_Body copy.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F6LKPd1wAFyIMQKsSo6KWkI\u002Fb090bb94a5499d12b90db38b37ec4fdf\u002F1812_2MillionCustomer_PR_Announcement_EN_Body.jpg","details":{"size":587017,"image":{"width":808,"height":1432}},"fileName":"1812_2MillionCustomer_PR Announcement_EN_Body.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F6LKPd1wAFyIMQKsSo6KWkI\u002Fd20e3f8875529f4352d8c28ba9c424ab\u002F1812_2MillionCustomer_PR_Announcement_ES_Body.png","details":{"size":307584,"image":{"width":808,"height":1432}},"fileName":"1812_2MillionCustomer_PR Announcement_ES_Body.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F6LKPd1wAFyIMQKsSo6KWkI\u002F4c333d050b3cdeeeacc20d99f6094db7\u002F1812_2MillionCustomer_PR_Announcement_IT_Body_copy.jpg","details":{"size":457524,"image":{"width":808,"height":1432}},"fileName":"1812_2MillionCustomer_PR Announcement_IT_Body copy.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Unterstützt uns dabei die Welt des Bankings zu revolutionieren. Ladet eure Freunde zu N26 ein. \nWir wachsen rasant, aber wir brauchen nach wie vor eure Hilfe. Vor einigen Wochen haben wir den Prozess, um Freunde einzuladen, neu gestaltet. Jetzt ist es noch einfacher und übersichtlicher Freunde einzuladen und so deine Gutschriften zu verwalten. \n","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Ffreunde-einladen"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nMehr Informationen dazu findet ihr auf unserer Website. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Vielen Dank für euer Vertrauen in N26. Wir können es kaum erwarten, euch den nächsten Meilenstein zu verkünden!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"A quick overview over how much our customers are transacting and how many people are using Spaces.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"If you’re a tech fan and tuned into ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Ftechcrunch.com\u002F2018\u002F11\u002F30\u002Fn26-tandem-disrupt-berlin\u002F"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Disrupt Berlin last week","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", you might have already heard the news: we’re growing quickly and just hit 2 million customers.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"That might seem like just another number, but we’re proud to report it because it follows our announcement of 1.5 million in October. It shows that we are expanding at a truly global pace, a pace that will help us launch in more markets, including the US next year.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Since October a few things have changed. We’ve ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fblog\u002Fthe-beta-launch-of-n26-uk-begins"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"launched in the UK","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", which represents our first account in another currency. The N26 euro account is also available in several other European countries including Poland, Norway, Sweden, Iceland, and Liechtenstein.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Curious what that looks like in numbers? We put together a nice infographic to better illustrate just how people are using N26.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"3ff9SQoMgoOiwIEwUmqyim","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-12-05T15:34:38.693Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:32:58.407Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3},"fields":{"title":{"en":"N26 Blogpost 2 Million Customers_3"},"description":{"en":"N26 Blogpost 2 Million Customers_3"},"file":{"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3ff9SQoMgoOiwIEwUmqyim\u002F3853f0599b143191875fcad488c56ace\u002F1812_2MillionCustomer_Blog-Body_transactionvolume_EN.jpg","details":{"size":64427,"image":{"width":1562,"height":348}},"fileName":"1812_2MillionCustomer_Blog-Body_transactionvolume_EN.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"3Uz72bolBYOE