p and on the web. Now you can more clearly see who you’ve invited and how much you’ve earned. Now’s a great time to celebrate and share N26 with your friends.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Send them an invite you’ll also get rewarded depending on your location. You can read more about friend referral ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Finvite-friends"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"here","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Thanks again for your trust in N26. We can’t wait to update you when we reach the next million.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si te gusta la tecnología y estuviste viendo el evento ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Ftechcrunch.com\u002F2018\u002F11\u002F30\u002Fn26-tandem-disrupt-berlin\u002F"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Disrupt Berlin","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" la semana pasada, probablemente ya estés al tanto de la noticia: hemos alcanzado los 2 millones de clientes.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Puede parecer una cifra más, pero ten en cuenta que en octubre superamos el millón y medio. Creemos que es algo de lo que estar orgullosos porque demuestra cómo nos estamos expandiendo globalmente a un ritmo que nos permite entrar en nuevos mercados, como Estados Unidos el año que viene. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"¿Qué ha pasado desde que anunciamos un millón y medio de clientes? Hemos aterrizado en Reino Unido, nuestro primer mercado con otra divisa. Y en lo