Environment"}},"revision":10,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"blogPost"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"en":"Blog: 2 years banking license (ALL, UK)"},"countryCodes":{"en":["DE","AT","FR","IT","ES","EU","GB","CH"]},"title":{"de":"Gegen alle Widrigkeiten: N26’ Weg zur Banklizenz","en":"Against all odds: the trials of getting our banking license","es":"Contra todo pronóstico: el camino para obtener nuestra licencia bancaria","fr":"Licence bancaire : déjà 2 ans","it":"Contro ogni aspettativa: ecco come abbiamo ottenuto la licenza bancaria"},"slug":{"de":"n26-weg-zur-banklizenz","en":"2-years-banking-license-n26","es":"segundo-aniversario-licencia-bancaria-n26","fr":"licence-bancaire-2-ans","it":"2-anniversario-licenza-bancaria"},"previewImage":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Other"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"26mItihWEIWw2qsUUc8GOe","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-07-17T14:08:37.828Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:33:29.895Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"de":"N26-2yr AnnoucementBlog Header-DE","en":"Getting a banking license","es":"N26-2yr AnnoucementBlog Header-ES","fr":"N26-2yr AnnoucementBlog Header-FR","it":"N26-2yr AnnoucementBlog Header-IT"},"description":{"de":"Frohes 2-Jahres Jubiläum zur Banklizenz - N26 Blog","en":"Happy 2nd anniversary to our banking license - N26 Blog","es":"Nuestra licencia bancaria cumple 2 años. ¡Felicidades! - N26 Blog","fr":"Notre licence bancaire fête ses deux ans ! - N26 Blog","it":"La nostra licenza bancaria compie 2 anni! Tanti auguri! - N26 Blog"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F26mItihWEIWw2qsUUc8GOe\u002F13a4affbabe4ce3641acc6564a429b02\u002FN26-2yr_AnnoucementBlog_Header-DE.jpg","details":{"size":473965,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"N26-2yr AnnoucementBlog Header-DE.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F26mItihWEIWw2qsUUc8GOe\u002F16ed6b962e63e1506cb0124adf0e43f9\u002FN26-2yr_AnnoucementBlog_Header-EN.jpg","details":{"size":476743,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"N26-2yr AnnoucementBlog Header-EN.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F26mItihWEIWw2qsUUc8GOe\u002F771e27be4cc9e5a0c0ade3223b4e7312\u002FN26-2yr_AnnoucementBlog_Header-ES.jpg","details":{"size":470932,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"N26-2yr AnnoucementBlog Header-ES.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F26mItihWEIWw2qsUUc8GOe\u002F0ccfaed945b19b802556dc4a66fb2cc9\u002FN26-2yr_AnnoucementBlog_Header-FR.jpg","details":{"size":471030,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"N26-2yr AnnoucementBlog Header-FR.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F26mItihWEIWw2qsUUc8GOe\u002Fe5340a1addd62643deb13628ec852160\u002FN26-2yr_AnnoucementBlog_Header-IT.jpg","details":{"size":468451,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"N26-2yr AnnoucementBlog Header-IT.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"categoryId":{"en":"company"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"27jlDrE1cQuQWOKooYAwYw"}}},"date":{"en":"2018-07-18"},"excerpt":{"de":"Behind the scenes: wie N26 zur Banklizenz kam. Und wie sie uns dabei half, über eine Million Kunden in ganz Europa zu gewinnen.","en":"The inside story of how we got our banking license in just a few months: from late nights to defying expectations.","es":"La historia de cómo conseguimos nuestra licencia bancaria en unos meses, desmontando expectativas y trabajando a contrarreloj.","fr":"Pour les 2 ans de l’obtention de la licence bancaire, Alex Weber revient sur ce moment marquant. ","it":"Tutti i dettagli su come abbiamo ottenuto la licenza bancaria in pochi mesi: dalle ore piccole a lavoro, fino ad un'entusiasmante novità"},"copy":{"de":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ich werde den 8. April 2015 nie vergessen. An diesem Tag schlossen wir unsere Series A Finanzierungsrunde von über 10 Millionen USD ab. An diesem Tag geschah aber noch etwas anderes, etwas sehr Entscheidendes. Die erfolgreiche Finanzierungsrunde war der Beweis für die Markttauglichkeit unseres Produkts und so trafen unsere beiden Gründer Max und Valentin die Entscheidung, mit N26 eine europäische Banklizenz zu beantragen. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Uns war klar: Wenn wir eine ganze Branche neu denken wollten, ist es unerlässlich, aktiv Einfluss auf einen größeren Teil der Wertschöpfungskette nehmen zu können. Eine Banklizenz würde für uns der Schlüssel sein, um Innovation im Banking weiter voranzutreiben. Als lizensierte Bank können wir modernste Technologien entwickeln und implementieren, neue Produkte für unsere Kunden zügig auf den Markt bringen und schnell international expandieren. Als Max und Valentin mich fragten, ob ich die Leitung des Projekts “Banklizenz” übernehmen würde, habe ich daher nicht lange gezögert. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 bestand aus noch nicht einmal 20 Mitarbeitern aber unser erstes Büro in Berlin Mitte (Unter den Linden) platzte damals schon beinah aus allen Nähten. In den letzten zehn Jahren wurden nur eine Handvoll Banklizenzen in Deutschland erteilt, es war also nicht davon auszugehen, dass jemand in unserem Team jemals an so einem Prozess beteiligt war. Schnell wurde klar, dass wir ein Team aus erfahrenen Experten aufstellen mussten, die die Bank aufbauen und betreiben würden. Markus Gunter, ehemaliger Vorstandsvorsitzender einer der größten Direktbanken Deutschlands, war als Geschäftsführer der (damals noch zukünftigen) Bank der erste Mitarbeiter im N26 Bank-Team. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Gemeinsam mit ihm und einem kleinen Kreis aus Experten erarbeiteten wir den Antrag für die Banklizenz und reichten ihn nach einem ersten Einführungsgespräch mit der BaFin (Bundesanstalt für Finanzdienstleistungsaufsicht) offiziell ein. Der Antrag umfasste drei dicke Ordner. Ich werde den Countdown nie vergessen: Die letzten Tage vor der Abgabe waren bis spät in die Nacht geprägt von sorgfältigem Korrekturlesen, Drucken und Sortieren. Wir bereiteten mehrere Versionen vor, die im Anschluss an verschiedene deutsche Regulierungsbehörden geschickt wurden. Nachdem wir den Antrag eingereicht hatten, kam ein großer Fragenkatalog, den wir schriftlich und in persönlichen Gesprächen beantworteten. Als dann alle deutschen Aufsichtsbehörden ihr GO gaben, waren wir nahe am Ziel,  wir mussten aber noch einen weiteren Schritt meistern: Unser Antrag ging nun zur finalen Prüfung an die Europäische Zentralbank.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Bereits damals zählten wir monatlich 10.000 neue Kunden, das Geschäft wuchs rasant und wir wollten die Lizenz so schnell wie möglich erhalten. Daher war klar, dass wir jede Gelegenheit nutzen würden, um den Prozess so schnell es geht zu finalisieren. Ich erinnere mich noch besonders lebhaft an einen Anruf der EZB an einem späten Freitagnachmittag. Wenn wir bis zum nächsten Montagmorgen einen weiteren Fragenkatalog bearbeiten würden, könnten wir den Prozess beschleunigen. Natürlich hat das Team das ganze Wochenende durchgearbeitet und dann, einige Tage später, war sie da, in einer E-Mail als PDF, unterzeichnet von Mario Draghi, dem Präsidenten der EZB: die Banklizenz für N26. Das war am 18. Juli 2016. Dieser Tag ist immer noch einer der wichtigsten Wendepunkte in der Geschichte von N26.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-07-18T12:11:50.147Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:33:30.037Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Blog2years","en":"Banking license pictures (3 in 1)","es":"Blog2years","fr":"Blog2years","it":"Blog2years"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fd34e2b11b769e4fb6d8e6d87778b54e7\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002F27363c667bfae145b22509babdf5a8e0\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fd43091751573e08ee9bdf72f2e3ca277\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fc107585640346ffe42ffeb420e85eb0a\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002F6c0967287e64d7ab0e85f9399007084b\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Rückblickend ist die Banklizenz einer der wichtigsten Gründe, warum wir heute über eine Million Kunden in ganz Europa haben. Sie ermöglichte es uns, in 17 Märkten zu expandieren, unser Produktangebot schnell auszubauen sowie zu verbessern und insbesondere das Vertrauen unserer Kunden auf die nächste zu Stufe heben. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Das Projekt spiegelt eine Geschichte wider, wie sie von so vielen erfolgreichen Start-ups erzählt wird. Zunächst hörst du von anderen ständig, warum du es nicht schaffen und scheitern wirst. Jeder sagt dir, wie komplex dein Projekt ist und versucht dich aktiv davon abzuhalten deine Ziele zu verfolgen. Während man natürlich für konstruktives Feedback offen sein sollte, ist es genauso wichtig, für manche Dinge eine dicke Haut zu entwickeln: Der Erfolg eines Projekts hängt maßgeblich von dem Mut, der Initiative und dem Engagement des ganzen Teams ab.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"},{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Alex Weber, Head of International Markets","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Weitere Informationen zur N26 Banklizenz gibt es im ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.youtube.com\u002Fwatch?v=2haFrU63xNY&t=20s"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Video-Gespräch","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" mit Alex Weber und Markus Gunter.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"I will never forget the 8th of April, 2015. On that day, we closed our USD 10 million Series A funding round at N26. But there was something else, something crucial, that happened on that day. Based on the proven product-market fit, our founders Max and Valentin decided to apply for a full European banking license. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"We knew that in order to rethink and sustainably change an industry, it would be essential to have control over a larger part of the value chain. It was clear that the license would be key to keep fuelling innovation—it would enable us to develop and implement state-of-the-art technologies, launch new products for our customers quickly, and be more flexible towards internationalization. So, when Max and Valentin asked me if I wanted to take over leading the project to obtain this license, I could not have been more excited and quickly agreed to embark on this challenge to help build a bank.  ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"We weren’t even 20 employees, working from our first office in Berlin Mitte (Unter den Linden), which by then had become too small for us already. Only a handful of banking licenses were granted in Germany in the last ten years—so, as you could imagine, nobody in our team had been involved in applying for one. After getting a first overview of what was required to successfully master the project, it was clear that we had to establish a team of experienced experts, who would build and run the bank. Markus Gunter, the former CEO of one of the largest direct banks in Germany, was the first to join the team as Managing Director of the (to-be) bank. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Together with him and a small team of experts and consultants, we drafted the licensing application and handed it in after a first introductory meeting with the German regulator BaFin. The application was around three folders thick and I will never forget the countdown before handing it in. Those last days were characterized by painstaking proofreading, lasting until late in the night. Each document had to be printed, sorted and organized very carefully. We prepared multiple versions to be sent to different German regulators. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"After handing in the application, we received multiple in-depth questions, which had to be clarified in written form and in-person meetings. We were very happy to satisfy all German regulators and excited about the next step in the process: our application was forwarded to the European Central Bank for a final check. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Back then, we were already signing up 10.000 new clients a month, the business was growing rapidly, and we were eager to get the license as fast as possible. We were ready to take every opportunity that was presented to us to fast-track the process. Most notably, I remember a call we got from the ECB on a late Friday afternoon. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"If we wanted to speed things up, we’d have to hand in written answers to several questions by the following Monday morning. Together with a couple of colleagues, we worked through the whole weekend and, astonishingly, a few days later we received the banking license. It arrived first in an e-mail as a PDF, signed by Mario Draghi, the president of the ECB. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"This was on July 18th, 2016. That day still represents one of our key turning points in N26’s history.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-07-18T12:11:50.147Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:33:30.037Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Blog2years","en":"Banking license pictures (3 in 1)","es":"Blog2years","fr":"Blog2years","it":"Blog2years"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fd34e2b11b769e4fb6d8e6d87778b54e7\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002F27363c667bfae145b22509babdf5a8e0\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fd43091751573e08ee9bdf72f2e3ca277\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fc107585640346ffe42ffeb420e85eb0a\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002F6c0967287e64d7ab0e85f9399007084b\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Looking back, the project reflects a story told by so many startups who have achieved something big. Initially, all you hear from third parties is that you can’t do it and why you will fail. Everyone tells you how complex it is and actively tries to discourage you from pursuing it. But, while you have to be open to all constructive feedback, some things are better ignored. A project’s success largely depends on its drivers.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"In the last two years, the banking license has helped us grow to 1 million customers across Europe by enabling us to do business in 17 markets and to rapidly iterate and improve our product offering. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"},{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Alex Weber, Head of International Markets","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"You can find more insights on N26’s banking license in ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.youtube.com\u002Fwatch?v=rQJwd0RqBXA"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"a video talk","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" with Markus and Alex.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nunca olvidaré el 8 de abril de 2015. Ese día cerramos nuestra ronda de financiación Serie A por 10 millones de dólares, aquí en N26. Pero hubo algo más, algo crucial, que también ocurrió ese día: los fundadores de N26, Max y Valentin, vieron que el producto encaja muy bien en los mercados en los que estaba presente, y decidieron solicitar la licencia bancaria europea.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Sabíamos que para repensar y cambiar de forma sostenible una industria sería imprescindible tener el control sobre una mayor parte de la cadena de valor. Estaba claro que la licencia sería clave para seguir empujando la innovación, y que nos permitiría desarrollar e implementar las tecnologías más vanguardistas, lanzar nuevos productos de forma ágil y ser mucho más flexibles de cara a la internacionalización. Así que cuando Max y Valentin me preguntaron si quería encargarme de liderar el proyecto para obtener la licencia, recuerdo que no me pudo hacer más ilusión y rápidamente acepté para embarcarme en este reto de construir un banco.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"No éramos ni 20 empleados, y estábamos todavía en la primera oficina en el barrio de Mitte de Berlín, en la avenida Unter den Linden (y esta oficina ya se había quedado pequeña para nosotros). En Alemania en los últimos años se habían aprobado solo un puñado de licencias bancarias, así que para nosotros, como os podéis imaginar, este proceso era algo completamente nuevo. En cuanto tuvimos una visión global sobre lo que necesitábamos para llevar a cabo el proyecto, estuvo claro que era imprescindible contar con un equipo de expertos que construyesen y dirigiesen el banco. Markus Gunter, el antiguo CEO de uno de los bancos más grandes de Alemania, fue el primero en unirse a nuestro equipo como Managing Director de lo que después sería N26 Bank.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Markus y un pequeño grupo de expertos y consultores nos ayudaron con la solicitud de la licencia y se encargaron de liderar la primera reunión introductoria con el regulador aleman BaFin. La solicitud tenía unas tres carpetas de grosor, y nunca olvidaré la contrarreloj antes de entregarla. Esos últimos días se caracterizaron por una minuciosa corrección constante, que duró hasta altas horas de la noche. Cada documento debía ser impreso, ordenado y organizado con cuidado, y preparamos varias versiones para enviar a diferentes reguladores alemanes.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nada más entregar la solicitud recibimos preguntas que requerían mucha profundidad para responder, y que debíamos clarificar por escrito y en reuniones presenciales. Estábamos muy contentos de satisfacer cualquier duda de los reguladores alemanes, y muy felices de estar a punto de dar el siguiente paso: nuestra solicitud había sido enviada al Banco Central Europeo para las comprobaciones finales.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Por aquel entonces crecíamos cada mes a un ritmo de 10.000 nuevos clientes, y queríamos lograr la licencia cuanto antes. Estábamos preparados para aprovechar cualquier oportunidad que se nos presentase para acelerar el proceso. \nRecuerdo la llamada del Banco Central Europeo un viernes por la tarde. Si queríamos avanzar en el proceso de forma rápida debíamos responder por escrito a una gran cantidad de preguntas antes del lunes por la mañana. Un grupo de compañeros trabajamos todo el fin de semana y, sorprendentemente, unos días después recibimos la licencia bancaria. Llegó primero un PDF por correo electrónico, firmado por Mario Draghi, el presidente del BCE.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Esto fue el día 18 de julio de 2016. Y ese día fue un punto de inflexión en la historia de N26.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-07-18T12:11:50.147Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:33:30.037Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Blog2years","en":"Banking license pictures (3 in 1)","es":"Blog2years","fr":"Blog2years","it":"Blog2years"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fd34e2b11b769e4fb6d8e6d87778b54e7\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002F27363c667bfae145b22509babdf5a8e0\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fd43091751573e08ee9bdf72f2e3ca277\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fc107585640346ffe42ffeb420e85eb0a\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002F6c0967287e64d7ab0e85f9399007084b\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Echando la vista atrás, el proyecto refleja la historia de muchas pequeñas empresas y start-ups que han logrado algo grande. Lo primero que escuchas son mensajes de “nunca lo conseguiréis” y “no es posible”. Todo el mundo te explica lo difícil que es e intentan desanimarte de forma activa. Pero, aunque siempre debamos estar abiertos a críticas constructivas, hay opiniones que a veces deben ser ignoradas. El éxito de un proyecto depende en gran medida de quien lo pilote.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"En los últimos dos años la licencia bancaria nos ha ayudado a crecer hasta superar el millón de clientes en Europa, y nos ha permitido estar presentes en 17 mercados, siempre mejorando y ampliando nuestra oferta de producto.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"},{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Alex Weber, Head of International Markets","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Je n’oublierai jamais le 8 avril 2015. Ce jour là, nous avons finalisé notre levée de fonds de 10 millions de dollars en Serie A. Mais ce n’était pas tout… Un autre événement majeur s’est produit dans la même journée : Max et Valentin (les deux co-fondateurs), motivés par les premiers succès, ont décidé que N26 devait obtenir sa propre licence bancaire européenne. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nous savions que pour repenser et changer durablement une industrie, il était indispensable de contrôler davantage la chaîne de valeur. Il ne faisait aucun doute que la licence nous permettrait de continuer à innover, afin de développer et implémenter ce qu'il se fait de mieux d’un point de vue technologique, de lancer rapidement de nouveaux produits et d’être plus flexible pour nous développer à l’international. Quand Max et Valentin m’ont demandé de prendre la main sur ce projet, je ne pouvais pas cacher mon enthousiasme. Cela représentait un challenge immense mais nécessaire pour atteindre notre objectif de construire une vraie banque. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"A l’époque, nous n’étions même pas 20 employés, basés dans nos premiers bureaux, à Mitte (Berlin), qui étaient déjà trop petits. Seule une poignée de licences bancaires avaient été accordées en Allemagne ces dernières années. Comme vous pouvez l’imaginer, aucun employé n’avait d’expérience en la matière. Après avoir obtenu un premier aperçu des prérogatives nécessaires pour en faire la demande, il est devenu évident que nous avions besoin d’experts qui pourraient construire et gérer une banque. Markus Gunter, ancien CEO de l’une des plus grandes banques en ligne en Allemagne, a été le premier à rejoindre l’équipe en qualité de Directeur Général de l’entreprise qui allait devenir une banque. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Avec lui et une petite équipe d’experts et de consultants, nous avons rédigé les documents nécessaires à l’obtention d’une licence bancaire et avons déposé notre candidature après un premier rendez-vous avec la BaFin, l’autorité de supervision financière allemande. Notre candidature avait l’épaisseur de 3 dossiers. Je n’oublierai jamais les jours qui ont précédé la remise de notre dossier : des relectures méticuleuses pendant de longues heures, jusqu’à tard dans la nuit. Chaque document devait être imprimé, relu et organisé. Nous avons préparé plusieurs versions des documents pour différents organismes. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Une fois la candidature déposée, nous avons reçu plusieurs questions pour lesquelles nous avons dû fournir de nouveaux documents écrits et organiser de nouvelles réunions. Nous avons su répondre à toutes les questions des organismes allemands et nous avons été heureux d’apprendre que notre application passait à l’étape suivante : la validation de notre candidature par la Banque Centrale Européenne. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"A ce moment là, nous avions déjà plus de 10 000 nouveaux clients chaque mois. N26 grandissait rapidement et le besoin d’obtenir la licence bancaire se faisait de plus en plus pressant. Nous étions prêts à saisir toutes les opportunités qui se présenteraient à nous pour accélérer le processus. Je me souviens d’une réunion téléphonique avec la Banque Centrale Européenne un vendredi après-midi : si vous nous voulions passer à la vitesse supérieure, nous devions soumettre le lundi matin suivant des réponses écrites à plusieurs questions qui avaient été soulevées lors de l’examen de notre demande. Avec quelques personnes, nous avons travaillé tout le week-end pour y répondre. Quelques jours plus tard, nous recevions notre licence bancaire. Signée par Mario Draghi, président de la Banque Centrale Européenne, elle nous est tout d’abord parvenue par email, au format PDF.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"C’était le 18 juillet 2016. Encore aujourd’hui, cette date représente l’un des tournants de l’histoire de N26. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-07-18T12:11:50.147Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:33:30.037Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Blog2years","en":"Banking license pictures (3 in 1)","es":"Blog2years","fr":"Blog2years","it":"Blog2years"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fd34e2b11b769e4fb6d8e6d87778b54e7\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002F27363c667bfae145b22509babdf5a8e0\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fd43091751573e08ee9bdf72f2e3ca277\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fc107585640346ffe42ffeb420e85eb0a\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002F6c0967287e64d7ab0e85f9399007084b\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Avec un peu de recul, ce projet est représentatif de ce qu’ont vécu de nombreuses start-ups qui ont rencontré un succès conséquent. Au début, vous entendez les gens extérieurs dire que ce n’est pas possible, que vous allez échouer. Tout le monde vous dit à quel point c’est complexe et, nombreux sont ceux qui cherchent à vous décourager. Finalement, même s'il faut être ouvert aux critiques constructives, il y a certaines choses qu’il vaut mieux ignorer. Le succès d’un projet dépend largement de ceux qui le mènent. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Depuis l’obtention de notre licence bancaire, 2 années se sont écoulées. Elle nous a aidé à dépasser la barre du million de clients, en nous permettant de proposer N26 dans 17 pays et de rapidement développer notre produit. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"},{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Alex Weber, Head of International Markets","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Non dimenticherò mai l’8 Aprile del 2015. Quel giorno abbiamo chiuso un round di finanziamenti di serie A da 10 milioni di Dollari, ma non è tutto, è successo qualcosa di più importante. I fondatori di N26, Max e Valentin, capendo che il prodotto era idoneo al mercato, hanno deciso di chiedere la licenza bancaria europea. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Sapevamo che per poter ammodernare e cambiare in modo sostanziale questo settore, dovevamo avere controllo su una parte più ampia della catena del valore. Era chiaro che la licenza bancaria europea sarebbe stata la chiave per continuare ad alimentare l’innovazione: ci avrebbe permesso di sviluppare e implementare tecnologie all’avanguardia, lanciare nuovi prodotti e essere più propensi all’internazionalizzazione. Quindi, quando Max e Valentin mi hanno chiesto di seguire il progetto per ottenere la licenza, non avrei potuto essere più felice e ho accettato subito questa sfida. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Non eravamo neanche 20 impiegati e lavoravamo dal nostro primo ufficio, in centro a Berlino (Unter den Linden), ormai troppo piccolo. Negli ultimi 10 anni erano state concesse pochissime licenze bancarie in Germania, quindi, come si può immaginare, nessuno del nostro team era stato coinvolto, in passato, nella richiesta di una licenza. Dopo una prima valutazione dei requisiti necessari al successo del progetto, era chiaro che dovevamo creare un team di esperti che ci avrebbe aiutato a creare e a sviluppare la nostra banca. Markus Gunter, l’ex amministratore delegato di una delle più grandi banche tedesche, è stato il primo ad unirsi al team come amministratore delegato della (futura) banca.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Insieme a lui e un piccolo team di esperti e consulenti, dopo un primo incontro con il regolatore tedesco BaFin, abbiamo scritto e consegnato la prima versione della richiesta per la licenza bancaria. Era spessa all’incirca tre cartelle e non dimenticherò mai il conto alla rovescia prima della consegna: gli ultimi giorni sono stati una continua e scrupolosa revisione delle varie bozze, durata fino a tarda notte. Ogni documento doveva essere stampato, classificato e organizzato con molta attenzione. Avevamo preparato diverse versioni da mandare a diversi regolatori tedeschi. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Dopo aver inoltrato la richiesta, abbiamo ricevuto domande sempre più approfondite, alle quali dovevamo rispondere in maniera scritta o presenziando di persona. Siamo stati molto felici di soddisfare tutti i regolatori tedeschi e ancora più eccitati per il passo successivo: la nostra richiesta era stata inoltrata alla Banca Centrale Europea per il controllo finale. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Da quel momento abbiamo ricevuto 10.000 nuove iscrizioni al mese, il business stava crescendo rapidamente ed eravamo ansiosi di ottenere la licenza bancaria il più velocemente possibile. Eravamo pronti ad accettare ogni singola opportunità che ci avesse permesso di accelerare il processo. In particolare, mi ricordo di una chiamata della BCE che abbiamo ricevuto un tardo pomeriggio di venerdì.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Se volevamo velocizzare le cose, avremmo dovuto rispondere in forma scritta ad alcune domande entro il lunedì seguente. Abbiamo lavorato per tutto il weekend, con un paio di colleghi, e, sorprendentemente, pochi giorni dopo abbiamo ricevuto la licenza bancaria: è arrivata via email, in PDF, firmata da Mario Draghi, il presidente della BCE.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Questo è successo il 18 Luglio 2016. Questa data, rappresenta ancora oggi uno dei punti di svolta nella storia di N26.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-07-18T12:11:50.147Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:33:30.037Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Blog2years","en":"Banking license pictures (3 in 1)","es":"Blog2years","fr":"Blog2years","it":"Blog2years"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fd34e2b11b769e4fb6d8e6d87778b54e7\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002F27363c667bfae145b22509babdf5a8e0\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fd43091751573e08ee9bdf72f2e3ca277\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002Fc107585640346ffe42ffeb420e85eb0a\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F1Qf1oPmbaASOyiUg8S6WqU\u002F6c0967287e64d7ab0e85f9399007084b\u002FBlog2years.png","details":{"size":2432032,"image":{"width":2142,"height":694}},"fileName":"Blog2years.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Guardando il passato, il progetto rappresenta la storia di molte start-up che sono riuscite a creare qualcosa di grande. All’inizio, l’unica cosa che ti senti dire è che non ce la farai mai perchè sicuramente fallirai, tutti ti dicono quanto sia difficile e cercano di scoraggiarti, ma anche se è sempre bene essere aperti a tutti i consigli, certe cose è meglio ignorarle. Il successo di un progetto dipende in gran parte dai suoi creatori.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Negli ultimi due anni, la licenza bancaria ci ha aiutato ad ottenere 1 milione di clienti in tutta Europa, consentendoci di fare affari in 17 paesi e di migliorare rapidamente la nostra offerta di prodotti.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"},{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Alex Weber, Head of International Markets","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"pt":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"}},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"1zqiLK9gqgASY2GCgWQCy8"}}]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2pbUemvILuIEqYCQycga8e"}}}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"77Args76P17EM0Sx6EbnZi","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-10-26T14:16:43.277Z","updatedAt":"2020-10-27T15:54:37.824Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","lin