ond de lecture","it":"Un testo \"ATM\" su sfondo letto"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3nWfjXcIgbd3nGfXM16MFU\u002Fc4e1d180d3c817436acf447f9773b064\u002FN26_ATM_1920x1080.jpg","details":{"size":933346,"image":{"width":1920,"height":1080}},"fileName":"N26_ATM_1920x1080.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3nWfjXcIgbd3nGfXM16MFU\u002F2e2b417fe39ff377bc0fbac6af355f88\u002FN26_ATM_1920x1080.jpg","details":{"size":933346,"image":{"width":1920,"height":1080}},"fileName":"N26_ATM_1920x1080.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3nWfjXcIgbd3nGfXM16MFU\u002Fa8407fc660a7e9481da70488634be9c0\u002FN26_ATM_1920x1080.jpg","details":{"size":933346,"image":{"width":1920,"height":1080}},"fileName":"N26_ATM_1920x1080.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3nWfjXcIgbd3nGfXM16MFU\u002F79186d27a91bbd2b54fcc5db05143f3a\u002FN26_ATM_1920x1080.jpg","details":{"size":933346,"image":{"width":1920,"height":1080}},"fileName":"N26_ATM_1920x1080.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3nWfjXcIgbd3nGfXM16MFU\u002F4a2b2fc72e8735fc093fa7dd3349d6ea\u002FN26_ATM_1920x1080.jpg","details":{"size":933346,"image":{"width":1920,"height":1080}},"fileName":"N26_ATM_1920x1080.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"categoryId":{"en":"basics"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5NeRRgvXxb3DvIoPFhx67p"}}},"date":{"en":"2019-02-26"},"excerpt":{"de":"Das Prinzip von Geldautomaten ist simpel: PIN eingeben, Geld entnehmen.  Für alle, die sich schon mal gefragt haben was genau dahintersteckt, haben wir hier alle Antworten.","en":"ATMs have a solid concept: type PIN, get money. But if you’ve ever wondered what comes next, this guide holds the answers.","es":"El concepto de cajero automático es muy sencillo: tecleas el PIN y te da dinero. Si alguna vez te has preguntado qué ocurre después, en esta guía encontrarás la respuesta.","fr":"Tout le monde sait comment fonctionne un distributeur automatique : on tape son code secret et on obtient de l’argent. Aujourd’hui, nous vous proposons d’en savoir plus sur ces machines.","it":"La logica degli ATM è semplice: digiti il PIN, prelevi i contanti. Ma sai che cos’altro possono offrirti questi strumenti? Ecco le risposte.\n"},"copy":{"de":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Auch wenn wir in einer digitalisierten Welt leben, kommen wir alle irgendwann an den Punkt, an dem wir Bargeld brauchen. Und genau dafür sind Geldautomaten da. Seit Jahrzehnten benutzen wir Geldautomaten ganz selbstverständlich, um möglichst schnell und unkompliziert an Bargeld zu gelangen – ohne zur Bank gehen zu müssen.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Aber die Frage ist: Wie kannst du den Gang zum Geldautomaten möglichst effektiv gestalten? Wie findest du, zum Beispiel, den nächstgelegenen Geldautomaten wenn du es eilig hast? ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fsupport.n26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Ferste-schritte\u002Fbargeld\u002Fwie-oft-kann-ich-kostenlos-bargeld-abheben"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Weißt du welche Gebühren anfallen?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fcash26"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ist ein Geldautomat überhaupt die beste Wahl?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" Dieser Artikel beschäftigt sich mit den Basics, die du über unsere täglichen Begleiter auf der Straße wissen solltest.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Was ist ein Geldautomat?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ein Geldautomat ist ein Automat, der nach Einführung der Debit- oder Kreditkarte sowie Abfragen der Karten-PIN Bargeld von deinem Konto abhebt. Im Grunde sind diese Automaten Maschinen, die sich oft in einer Bankfiliale oder in der Außenwand des Gebäudes befinden. Häufig bieten Geldautomaten auch andere alltägliche Banking-Dienstleistungen an.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wie finde ich einen Geldautomaten in der Nähe?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Diese Frage hast du dir sicher schon oft gestellt, wenn du auf dem Weg zu einer Verabredung festgestellt hast, dass du kein Bargeld mehr hast. In Großstädten findet man Geldautomaten wie Sand am Meer. Der nächste Automat ist nie weit entfernt.\nNaturgemäß befinden sich die Automaten oft in Banken oder in deren Außenwänden, aber auch in Shoppingzentren, neben Geschäften oder auch in U-Bahnhöfen.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Geldautomatensuche","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wenn du keine Zeit hast selbst nach dem nächstgelegenen Geldautomaten zu suchen, können Websites oder Apps weiterhelfen. Sie zeigen dir eine Karte deiner Umgebung an, in der alle Bankautomaten eingetragen sind.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"In der N26 App musst dazu einfach nur auf das Kartensymbol in der Ecke oben rechts klicken, um dich ganz unkompliziert zum nächsten Geldautomaten navigieren zu lassen.\n","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"7928Jdry4mzvHHUJJhtghz","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ist die Nutzung von Geldautomaten kostenpflichtig?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Es kommt darauf an. In manchen Ländern, wie Großbritannien, ist die Nutzung der meisten Geldautomaten kostenlos. Aber in den anderen Ländern können Gebühren anfallen – insbesondere wenn du Geld bei einer Bank abhebst, bei der du selbst nicht Kunde bist.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Das ist in Deutschland oft der Fall. Deshalb heben viele nur bei der eigenen Bank Geld ab. So verliert man nicht den Überblick. Zusätzliche Gebühren bei der Abhebung müssen während der Transaktion ausgewiesen werden. Trotz der Ankündigung der Gebühren bleibt der Schock über deren Höhe meist nicht aus. Vielen heben dann trotzdem ab – aus reiner Bequemlichkeit.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Geldautomat ist nicht gleich Geldautomat","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Es gibt zwei Arten von Geldautomaten:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Von Banken betriebene Geldautomaten befinden sich oft in der Bankfiliale selbst oder in deren Außenwand, aber auch in Bahnhöfen und Shoppingzentren. Wenn du ein Konto bei dieser Bank hast, kannst du hier nicht nur Geld abheben, sondern auch andere Services nutzen (zum Beispiel Geld einzahlen).","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Unabhängige Bankautomaten findest du eher in kleinen Lebensmittelgeschäften, an Kiosken, Tankstellen oder Bars und Restaurants. Dort, wo häufig schnell Bargeld gebraucht wird. Wenn du einen solchen Geldautomaten nutzt, solltest du vorsichtig sein und prüfen, welche Gebühren anfallen, da diese vom Betreiber des Automaten selbst und nicht von einer Bank festgelegt werden.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"}],"nodeType":"unordered-list"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wie viel Geld kann man am Automaten abheben?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Das kann dir deine Bank sagen, denn häufig legt sie die Grenze fest und nicht der Automat. Die Limits können von Bank zu Bank sehr unterschiedlich sein.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Für N26 Kunden beträgt das Limit an Geldautomaten in den meisten Ländern 2.500 € pro Kalendertag. Du kannst dieses Limit nach Bedarf in der App heruntersetzen.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Wie komme ich sonst noch an Bargeld?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Geldautomaten sind nicht die einzige Bargeld-Quelle. Kunden traditioneller Banken können natürlich am Schalter Geld abholen. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Mit ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fcash26"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"CASH26","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" kannst du als N26 Kunde deutschlandweit in mehr als 11.500 Geschäften und in Österreich bei 1.900 Partnergeschäften so oft du willst Geld abheben. Dazu brauchst du nicht einmal ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fgirokonto"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"deine N26 Mastercard","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" – einfach die N26 App öffnen und den QR-Code scannen.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fcash26"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"CASH26","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" ist bei Rossmann, REWE, Penny, Real, dm, BUDNI, Ludwig, Eckert, ON Express, Adam’s, Barbarino und mobilcom-debitel verfügbar. Du wählst den Betrag den du abheben oder einzahlen willst direkt in der N26 App aus und die App erstellt einen Barcode, den wiederum der Kassierer scannt. Auf diese Weise kannst du so oft du willst Bargeld abheben und auch einzahlen. Monatliche Einzahlungen von bis zu 100 € sind kostenfrei möglich.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fde-de\u002Fblog-archiv\u002Fkategorie\u002Fbasics"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Wir wollen Banking für jeden vereinfachen","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":". Freue dich auf mehr Artikel, die die Basics im Bereich Geld sowie Finanzen und zu allem, was mit Banking zu tun hat, leicht verständlich erklären – denn häufig ist es viel einfacher, als du auf den ersten Blick denkst.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"3ofgvQOMPfcEX3zadQ3ItR","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Even though we live in an increasingly digital world, everyone finds themselves needing cash-in-hand at some point. That’s where the cash machine come in handy. For decades, they’ve been the most convenient way to get instant access to the money in your account, without physically having to go into the bank.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The question is, are you sure you’re getting the most out of your cash machine experience? For instance, how do you find the closest one when you’re in a rush? Do you know what it charges? And is an ATM even the best option? This article goes back to basics, to take a closer look at one of the handiest machines we encounter on the street everyday.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"What is an ATM?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"ATM stands for “Automated Teller Machine”, also commonly known as a “cash machine”, “cash dispenser”, “cashpoint” or “hole-in-the-wall”. In essence, it’s a machine that’s often situated either inside a bank branch or around the wall outside it, where you can enter your card, type in a PIN and withdraw money from your account. Often, ATMs offer several features to let you take care of other everyday banking tasks, too.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"How can I find an ATM near me?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"If you’ve ever gone to dinner and realised you forgot to get cash out beforehand, you’ve probably asked yourself this question. In big towns and cities, there’s normally plenty of ATMs to be found. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"As you’d expect, they’re often located in or outside bank branches, but you can also find them elsewhere, for instance, in shopping malls, at stores or near public transport stations. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"ATM locators","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"If you haven’t got time to wander around town looking for the nearest ATM, an online or app-based ATM locator can help. It provides a map of the local area with ATM cash points marked on it.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"In the N26 app, just touch the map symbol in the top right corner to see the Cash Map, and easily navigate to the nearest ATM.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"7928Jdry4mzvHHUJJhtghz","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"ATM charges","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Do ATMs cost money to use? It depends. In some countries, like the UK, most ATMs are free to use. But in others, you might have to pay – especially if you withdraw money from an ATM owned by a bank that you don’t bank with.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Germany is one example of this system. It’s standard practice for people to only take cash out from ATM machines run by their own bank. Customers are able to keep an eye out for any fees, because legally these have to be stated during the transaction. But even knowing the fees upfront doesn’t make them any easier to swallow, and people can feel pressured to pay just for the convenience of being at the closest ATM.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"But remember that whichever country you’re in, there will probably be a few ATMs – typically ones which are not operated by a bank – that will always charge a fee, so look out for these. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Types of ATM","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"There are two basic types of ATM:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Bank-owned ATMs, which as the name suggests, are run by a bank. Many of them will actually be in or just outside of a branch of that bank – but you could also find bank-owned ATMs in other locations, like train stations or shopping malls. As well as withdrawing cash, you can do a variety of other things via bank-owned ATMs, such as depositing money if you have an account at the same branch.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Independent ATMs. You’re more likely to find the independent ones in convenience stores or convenient spending locations like gas stations, bars and restaurants. If you’re using an ATM that’s not owned by a bank, ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fmag.n26.com\u002Fwe-did-everything-an-atm-asked-us-to-do-abroad-and-it-emptied-our-bank-account-3a4cdd0a862a"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"be careful to check for extra fees","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" because in these cases, you’re being charged by the ATM operator itself, rather than your bank.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"}],"nodeType":"unordered-list"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"How much can I withdraw from an ATM?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"You should check directly with your bank to find out what their ATM withdrawal limit is – they can vary quite widely and often this actually depends on your bank rather than the ATM itself. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"For N26 customers, the maximum withdrawal limit from an ATM is €2.500 in most countries. If you want to set a lower withdrawal limit, you can change this in the app.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Your money at N26","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fbank-account"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The N26 free bank account","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" lets you withdraw cash from any ATM for free, ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fsupport.n26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fgetting-started\u002Fcash\u002Fhow-often-can-i-withdraw-cash-for-free"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"up to 5 times a month","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":". And there’s also another way to get cash that doesn’t involve ATMs at all.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"With ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-de\u002Fcash26"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"CASH26","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", N26 customers can make unlimited free cash withdrawals at more than 11.500 retail locations around Germany and a growing number of stores in Austria just by opening the N26 app and letting the cashier scan a barcode on their phone – you don’t even need your bank card. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"CASH26 is a bit like asking for cashback when you buy something in a supermarket, except you don’t need to make a purchase. Simply head to one of our many retail partner locations, including Rossmann, REWE, Penny, Real, dm, BUDNI, Ludwig, Eckert, ON Express, Adam’s, Barbarino or mobilcom-debitel. Then use the N26 app to generate a barcode for the cashier to scan. You can withdraw cash for free as often as you want. You can even deposit cash this way, too – up to €100 per month for free. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"We want to simplify banking for everyone. We’re bringing you a series of articles that shine a light on ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fblog\u002Fbanking-basics-getting-started"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"the basics of money","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":", finance and all things banking related – it’s often a lot simpler than you might think.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"3ofgvQOMPfcEX3zadQ3ItR","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Aunque estemos en la era digital y utilicemos el móvil para pagar, el efectivo sigue siendo necesario. Por eso los cajeros son tan prácticos. Durante décadas, nos han permitido acceder al dinero de nuestras cuentas bancarias, ahorrándonos el trámite de tener que pasar por la sucursal.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Los usamos muy a menudo pero, ¿aprovechamos al máximo todas las opciones que ofrecen los cajeros? Por ejemplo, ¿sabes cómo encontrar el cajero automático más cercano cuando vas con prisa? ¿Sabes cuánto te cobran? ¿Son los cajeros automáticos la mejor opción? En este artículo nos remontamos a sus orígenes para conocer más de cerca cómo funcionan.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"¿Qué es un cajero automático?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Un cajero automático es básicamente una máquina expendedora de billetes (más o menos). Estas suelen encontrarse dentro o cerca de las sucursales de los bancos y nos permiten ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fes-es\u002Fsacar-dinero"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"sacar dinero","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" con solo introducir la tarjeta, elegir el importe y teclear el PIN. Desde algunos cajeros también se pueden hacer otras transacciones como consultar el saldo de tu cuenta o hacer depósitos.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"¿Cómo encuentro cajeros automáticos cerca de mi ubicación?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Es posible que te hayas hecho esta pregunta si alguna vez has salido a cenar y te has se te ha olvidado llevar efectivo. En las ciudades suele ser fácil encontrar cajeros automáticos.\nComo comentábamos antes, normalmente están al lado de las sucursales de los bancos, aunque a veces también se encuentran en los centros comerciales, las zonas de tiendas o cerca de las estaciones de transporte público.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Buscadores de cajeros automáticos","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si no tienes tiempo de callejear para encontrar el más cercano, contar con la ayuda de un buscador de cajeros automáticos puede resultarte muy útil. Ya sea online o una app, el buscador te muestra un mapa de la zona en el que aparecen marcadas las ubicaciones de los cajeros.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"En la app de N26 hay un mapa de cajeros que te permite encontrar el más cercano a ti basándose en tu ubicación actual.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"7aArMtSGBPfeNHsGKBl9j7","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Comisiones por usar el cajero","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"¿Cuesta dinero utilizar un cajero automático? Depende. En algunos países, como el Reino Unido, utilizar un cajero no te cuesta nada. Aunque hay otros países en los que sí tienes que pagar una comisión por sacar dinero de cajeros que no sean de tu banco.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"España es un ejemplo de ello. Por eso, lo normal es que la gente saque dinero de cajeros que sean del banco del que son clientes. A partir de aquí, ya sabes si vas a pagar comisiones o no, ya que los bancos tienen la obligación legal de informarte antes de que finalice la transacción. Saber cuánto pagas por sacar dinero se agradece, pero no quita el hecho de que estás pagando por retirar tu propio dinero. A veces nos vemos en la situación de tener que pagar por sacar efectivo, simplemente porque es la única opción y es el cajero más cercano.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Por suerte, N26 tiene una alternativa para los clientes españoles. Incluso desde la cuenta estándar gratuita de N26, se puede sacar efectivo en euros en cualquier cajero automático, hasta 5 veces al mes gratis.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pero recuerda: es posible que des con algún que otro cajero que cobre comisiones (suelen ser los que no pertenecen a un banco), así que no bajes la guardia.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Tipos de cajero automático","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Los dos tipos principales de cajero son los siguientes:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":" Los cajeros de los bancos","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":": como su propio nombre indica, son el tipo de cajero que gestionan los bancos. De hecho, muchos de ellos se encuentran dentro o justo al lado del propio banco, aunque a veces también están en otros sitios, como en estaciones de tren o centros comerciales. Además de sacar dinero, los cajeros de los bancos te permiten hacer otros trámites, como ingresar dinero en tu cuenta.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Los cajeros independientes","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":": los cajeros independientes suelen estar más presentes en supermercados grandes, zonas turísticas, gasolineras y algunas estaciones. Si utilizas un cajero ajeno a un banco, ten en cuenta que puede que el operador del cajero te cobre alguna comisión adicional.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"}],"nodeType":"unordered-list"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"¿Cuánto dinero puedo sacar del cajero?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Para conocer el límite de efectivo del que puedes disponer en el cajero consúltalo directamente en tu oficina, ya que varía de una entidad a otra y, en muchos casos, depende del banco y no del cajero.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Los clientes de N26 pueden retirar hasta 2.500 euros al día en cajeros en la mayoría de países. Desde la app puedes modificar el límite diario de retiradas de efectivo, a tu gusto. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"¿Qué otras opciones tengo para sacar dinero?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Los cajeros automáticos no son la única forma que tienes de acceder a tu dinero. Sabes que si operas con un banco tradicional, también puedes disponer de efectivo pidiéndolo en caja de la sucursal. Aunque existe una manera que no te obliga a ir a la sucursal en persona.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Con ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-de\u002Fcash26"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"CASH26","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", los clientes de N26 podrán sacar dinero del cajero todas las veces que quieran y de forma totalmente gratuita en más de 11.500 establecimientos repartidos por toda Alemania y Austria. Solo hay que abrir la app de N26 y presentar el código QR en el teléfono móvil, todo ello sin necesidad de usar la tarjeta. Con este método puedes sacar dinero de forma gratuita todas las veces que quieras y también te permite ingresar hasta 100 euros al mes sin comisiones.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Retirar efectivo con CASH26 es como pagar una cantidad con tarjeta en un comercio para recibirla a cambio en efectivo. No obstante, aunque sea una forma común de retirar efectivo en países como Alemania, es una práctica que aún no ha llegado a España.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Sabemos que la era de los cajeros automáticos aún no ha terminado. Cada vez usamos menos efectivo y por eso puede que ya no sean tan importantes como solían serlo hace unos años. Aun así, nunca está de más saber algo más sobre cómo funcionan y conocer otros sistemas alternativos, como CASH26.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Queremos que todo el mundo entienda a la perfección cómo operar con los bancos. Iremos publicando más artículos sobre dinero, finanzas y otros aspectos relacionados con las operaciones bancarias, para que de lo único que tengas que preocuparte es de cómo quieres gastar tu dinero.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"3ofgvQOMPfcEX3zadQ3ItR","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" Même si nous vivons dans un monde de plus en plus dématérialisé, nous avons tous, à un moment ou un autre, besoin d’espèces (cela varie souvent en fonction des pays). C’est là qu’interviennent les distributeurs automatiques. Depuis des décennies, ils constituent le moyen le plus pratique d’obtenir de l’argent en espèces sans devoir entrer dans une banque.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Mais, êtes-vous sûr de tout savoir sur les distributeurs ? Par exemple, comment faire pour trouver le distributeur le plus proche de vous ? Savez-vous si son utilisation engendre des frais ? Cet article vous explique plus en détail comment fonctionnent et comment utiliser au mieux les distributeurs automatiques.  ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Qu’est-ce qu’un distributeur automatique de billets ?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Le distributeur automatique de billets est également appelé DAB, distributeur de billets, distributeur automatique ou parfois, tout simplement distributeur. Il s’agit d’une machine généralement située dans une agence bancaire ou à l’extérieur, qui vous permet de retirer de l’argent de votre compte en insérant votre carte et en tapant votre code PIN. \nAttention à ne pas confondre le DAB avec le GAB, le guichet automatique de banque. Ce dernier, en plus de vous permettre de retirer de l’argent en libre-service, vous permet également de réaliser certaines opérations bancaires simples, comme la consultation de votre compte ou l’impression d’un relevé, par exemple.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Le saviez-vous ?","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" Le premier distributeur de billets disponible 24\u002F24 et 7\u002F7 a été installé en juin 1967, au nord de Londres, en Grande-Bretagne. A l’époque, cette invention de John Shepherd-Barron distribuait seulement des billets de 10 Livres et ne fonctionnait pas avec une carte bancaire mais un bon en papier. Une fois le bon inséré, le client devait entrer son code à 4 chiffres. En France, le premier DAB est installé en 1968, rue Auber dans le 9ème arrondissement de Paris.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Comment trouver le distributeur automatique de billets le plus proche ?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Vous vous êtes sûrement déjà posé cette question alors que vous étiez en route pour retrouver des amis par exemple et que vous aviez oublié de prendre de l’argent liquide. Les distributeurs automatiques de billets sont très nombreux dans les grandes villes françaises et vous devriez en trouver un à proximité, sans grande difficulté.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Les DAB se trouvent à l’intérieur ou à l’extérieur des banques, mais aussi dans les centres commerciaux ou souvent, à proximité des stations de transports publics.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Géolocaliser les distributeurs automatiques de billets","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si vous n’avez pas le temps de chercher un distributeur au hasard des rues, pensez aux applications qui géolocalisent les distributeurs de billets qui se trouvent autour de vous. Ils permettent de visualiser facilement sur une carte leur emplacement et parfois de faire apparaître l’itinéraire le plus court pour s’y rendre.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Si vous détenez un compte N26, il vous suffit de vous connecter à votre application N26 et d’appuyer sur l’icône carte dans le coin supérieur droit de votre écran pour afficher le plan des distributeurs automatiques les plus proches de vous.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"7928Jdry4mzvHHUJJhtghz","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Les types de distributeurs automatiques de billets","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Il existe deux sortes de distributeurs automatiques standards :\n·     Le distributeur automatique dépendant d’une banque, qui, comme l’intitulé l’indique, est géré par une banque. Ce type de distributeur automatique est, en général, situé à l’intérieur ou à l’extérieur des filiales de cette banque, mais on peut également le retrouver dans les gares ou les centres commerciaux. \nSi vous vous rendez dans votre banque, vous pouvez également utiliser les guichets automatiques de banque qui vous permettront d’effectuer aussi des opérations bancaires simples.\n·     Les distributeurs indépendants. Les distributeurs indépendants sont souvent situés dans les supérettes ou autres endroits pratiques comme les stations-service, les bars et les restaurants. Si vous utilisez un distributeur automatique qui ne dépend pas d’une banque, pensez à vérifier si des frais supplémentaires sont prélevés, car dans ce cas de figure, c’est l’opérateur du distributeur de billets qui vous facture et non pas votre banque. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pour en savoir plus sur la façon dont les distributeurs peuvent vous facturer lorsque vous êtes à l’étranger ou même vous faire dépenser plus que prévu, consultez cet article. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Le coût des distributeurs automatiques de billets","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Faut-il payer pour utiliser un distributeur automatique ? Cela dépend des pays et des distributeurs. Dans certains pays comme la France, les distributeurs automatiques de grandes banques vous permettent de retirer sans frais. En revanche, votre banque peut facturer vos retraits, notamment si vous retirez fréquemment de l’argent dans les distributeurs d’une autre banque. Ces frais de retraits sont bien évidemment indiqués dans votre contrat, consultez-le si vous n’êtes pas sûr. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Avec un compte N26 standard gratuit, vous pouvez retirer dans les distributeurs de votre choix sans frais, jusqu’à cinq fois par mois. Mais attention aux distributeurs indépendants qui peuvent facturer vos retraits. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Quelles sont mes limites de retrait ?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pour connaître votre limite de retrait à un distributeur automatique, il faut vous renseigner auprès de votre banque. La limite est très variable et doit être inscrite dans votre contrat.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Pour les clients N26, la limite de retrait à un distributeur est de 2 500 € par jour. Pour vous aider à gérer votre argent mais aussi pour la sécurité de votre compte, vous pouvez cependant fixer des limites de retraits et de paiement inférieures, directement depuis l’application N26 et en temps réel.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"N26 souhaite rendre le secteur bancaire plus accessible afin de vous redonner le contrôle de vos finances. Gardez un oeil sur les articles de notre blog pour découvrir tout ce que vous devriez savoir sur le monde de la banque. Vous verrez, c’est souvent beaucoup plus simple qu’il n’y paraît.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"3ofgvQOMPfcEX3zadQ3ItR","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Viviamo in un mondo sempre più digitale, eppure arriva sempre quel momento in cui ci ritroviamo ad avere bisogno di contanti. Ecco perché i bancomat sono così utili: da decenni, ormai, sono il modo più pratico e veloce di prelevare denaro senza dover mettere piede in banca.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ma la domanda è: sei sicuro di sfruttare al meglio tutte le funzionalità che offrono? Come puoi trovare lo sportello ATM più vicino a te quando sei di fretta? Sapresti dire quali commissioni ti vengono addebitate? Con questo articolo ripartiamo dalle nozioni di base per scoprire qualcosa di più su questo strumento così utile nella nostra vita di tutti i giorni.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Cos’è un bancomat?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Gli sportelli ATM (dall’inglese ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Automated Teller Machine","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":") sono conosciuti comunemente come sportelli automatici, sportelli bancomat o semplicemente bancomat. A dire il vero quest’ultimo appellativo, anche se molto diffuso in Italia, è utilizzato impropriamente: ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"bancomat","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", infatti, è in realtà il nome di uno dei più importanti circuiti per il prelievo di contante utilizzati negli sportelli automatici. Con il tempo, però, questo marchio è diventato talmente conosciuto e diffuso da essere utilizzato per fare riferimento agli sportelli stessi. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Gli sportelli ATM non sono altro che dispositivi installati all’esterno delle filiali bancarie o situati al loro interno. Questi strumenti ti consentono di prelevare denaro dal tuo conto semplicemente inserendo la tua carta e digitando il tuo PIN… ma non solo! Spesso gli ATM offrono funzionalità aggiuntive, utili per eseguire le operazioni bancarie di tutti i giorni.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Come posso trovare il bancomat più vicino a me?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"È la domanda che ti fai ogni volta che arrivi in un ristorante o in un bar e ti ricordi improvvisamente di non aver prelevato. Nelle grandi città, fortunatamente, puoi trovare un ATM praticamente a ogni angolo: non solo dentro e fuori qualsiasi filiale bancaria, ma anche all’interno dei centri commerciali, nei supermercati o nei pressi delle stazioni dei trasporti pubblici.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Cercare un bancomat nelle vicinanze","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Se non hai tempo di gironzolare per trovare lo sportello ATM più vicino a te, puoi affidarti a uno dei tanti servizi di ricerca ATM disponibili online o tramite app. Questi ti mostreranno una mappa della zona in cui ti trovi, segnalando tutti gli sportelli intorno a te.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Con l’app N26, ti basta toccare il simbolo della mappa nell’angolo in alto a destra per visualizzare la Cash Map ed essere guidato allo sportello più vicino a te.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"7928Jdry4mzvHHUJJhtghz","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Commissioni sui prelievi: quanto costa usare un ATM?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Dipende. In alcuni paesi, come ad esempio Inghilterra, la maggior parte degli sportelli ATM può essere utilizzata gratuitamente. In altri, però, questo servizio può essere a pagamento, specialmente quando prelevi contanti da uno sportello che non appartiene alla tua banca.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"In Italia si cerca tendenzialmente di evitare di usare un bancomat appartenente a una banca diversa dalla propria, proprio per evitare eventuali commissioni. Quando questo accade, comunque, lo sportello ATM deve avvertire il cliente nel caso in cui venga applicata una commissione. Il fatto di sapere che dovremo pagare un extra, però, non rende la cosa più facile da digerire… e non tutti sono disposti a farlo per la sola comodità di usare lo sportello più vicino.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fit-it\u002Fconto-corrente"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" offre ai propri clienti italiani una soluzione alternativa. Tutti i conti N26, infatti, garantiscono la possibilità di effettuare prelievi in euro illimitati presso qualsiasi ATM, gratuitamente.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Indipendentemente dal paese in cui ti trovi, però, fai attenzione: ricorda che potresti incappare in sportelli ATM che addebitano sempre una commissione sulle tue operazioni. Di norma, si tratta di quelli che non sono gestiti da un istituto bancario.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"I diversi tipi di ATM","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Esistono due tipi principali di sportello automatico:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"ATM di proprietà di una banca","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":": come suggerisce il nome, sono gestiti da un istituto bancario. Generalmente sono installati all’esterno delle filiali o al loro interno, ma puoi trovarli anche altrove, ad esempio nelle stazioni dei treni o nei centri commerciali. Oltre a prelevare contanti, questi ATM ti consentono normalmente di eseguire altre operazioni. Se si tratta di uno sportello della tua banca, per esempio, hai spesso anche la possibilità di depositare denaro sul tuo conto corrente.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"ATM indipendenti","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":": puoi trovarli nei supermercati e anche nelle stazioni di servizio, nei bar o nei ristoranti. Quando usi questo tipo di sportelli ATM, fai attenzione ai costi extra: in questi casi, infatti, è il gestore dello sportello ad applicare le commissioni, non la tua banca.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"}],"nodeType":"unordered-list"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Quanto si può prelevare al giorno?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"I limiti di prelievo possono variare notevolmente e dipendono il più delle volte dalla banca piuttosto che dallo sportello ATM. Se vuoi conoscere l’importo massimo che puoi prelevare in un giorno, quindi, rivolgiti direttamente alla tua banca.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"I clienti N26 possono prelevare fino a 2500 € al giorno nella maggior parte dei paesi e, se lo desiderano, possono ridurre il proprio limite di prelievo direttamente dall’app.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"hr"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Vogliamo rendere l’esperienza bancaria semplice e accessibile per tutti. Continua a seguirci: ti proporremo presto nuovi articoli in cui faremo chiarezza su tanti altri aspetti del mondo bancario. Scoprirai che può essere molto più semplice di quanto non sembri.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Scopri di più: ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fit-it\u002Fblog\u002Fguida-al-conto-bancario"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Banking basics: conosci il tuo conto bancario","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"3ofgvQOMPfcEX3zadQ3ItR","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"pt":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"6KHnAHOFTTO1wDyMD12fvc","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"}},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"4vJCycc2KoafnAjjIDGe3a"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6KHnAHOFTTO1wDyMD12fvc"}}]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"31Q9DBRDczx2gb1yAtMjEk"}}}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"3h23IM91oy8XcvdDOKiOt6","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-10-23T09:54:07.575Z","updatedAt":"2020-10-23T09:54:07.575Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"redirect"}}},"fields":{"from":{"en":"crm-performance-business-metal-promo-incentive"},"toCountry":{"en":[{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space