rlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":". ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Yet the future of N26 is global. Our US launch is a major milestone in our journey to become a truly global bank. We aim to reach over 50 million customers around the world in the coming years. We know that millions of people worldwide, particularly in the US, still pay hidden fees, suffer from poor customer experience, and cannot easily integrate their personal banking into their everyday lives. We will radically change the way Americans bank, ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fblog\u002Fn26-you-bank-account-with-travel-insurance-announcement"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"like we did for our customers throughout Europe","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":". ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-us\u002Fblog\u002Fn26-launch-in-the-us"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Check out our US product blog post","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" and learn about a few things you can expect from banking with N26 in the US.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"As the first European challenger bank launching in the US, we are excited that 100,000 customers on the US waitlist now have access to our product. We’re looking forward to our full public launch later this summer. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"We would like to say thank you to our fantastic team and ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-us\u002Fblog\u002Four-us-journey-begins-today"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"our US CEO Nic","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", as well as our incredibly loyal customers, who have all made this US launch possible. We wouldn’t be celebrating this success without their support. Their trust and confidence in N26 has helped us create this remarkable company, which today is one of the most successful startups in Europe. We are looking forward to continuing this success story – in Europe, the US and other markets around the world.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"With sincere thanks,","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Valentin Stalf, Maximilian Tayenthal","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Founders","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2019-07-11T09:20:15.636Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:23:17.606Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":7},"fields":{"title":{"de":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","en":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","es":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","fr":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","it":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)"},"description":{"de":"N26 Launch USA","en":"N26 US Launch Infographic ","es":"N26 Aterriza en EE UU - Infográfico"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F4239596f41f41baf51d30e01493ae928\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-DE__1_.jpg","details":{"size":918866,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-DE (1).jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F8388a7a85084e7e2f22388863fe485e5\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-EN-UK__1_.jpg","details":{"size":885869,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-EN-UK (1).jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F07f29c13f1cfc7592f31ac3973983a46\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-ES.jpg","details":{"size":970109,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-ES.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002Fe085154ec80c1c740f4bc4da39dc35b3\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-FR.jpg","details":{"size":967037,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-FR.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002Fb405f4cec3a025d9ff35ecd0834c4fb9\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-IT.jpg","details":{"size":935050,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-IT.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Anunciamos el lanzamiento de N26 en EE UU, nuestro gran salto para convertirnos en el banco móvil global.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nuestro objetivo es ofrecer a todo el mundo la oportunidad de tener su propia experiencia bancaria, a su manera. Queremos que nuestros clientes tengan el control y decidan qué oportunidades quieren aprovechar, y que se sientan inspirados día a día.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Desde nuestro lanzamiento en enero de 2015, hemos vivido muy buenos momentos que por aquel entonces ni nos imaginamos que viviríamos. Hoy, ofrecemos una experiencia bancaria móvil a más de 3 millones y medio de clientes por todo el mundo, con una actividad de más de 16 millones de transacciones al mes. Cada día más de 10.000 clientes se crean una cuenta nueva dentro de nuestros 24 mercados europeos.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Sí, el futuro de N26 es global.","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":" El lanzamiento en EE UU es nuestro mayor logro hasta la fecha y el primer paso para crear el banco móvil global del que todo el mundo se enamora","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":". Sabemos que hay millones de personas en todo el mundo, especialmente en EE UU, que siguen pagando comisiones ocultas, y se enfrentan cada día a todas las trabas que les supone manejar sus finanzas. N26 quiere cambiar radicalmente la experiencia bancaria de los estadounidenses, como ya hemos hecho con todos nuestros clientes en Europa.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Somos el primer challenger bank europeo que lanza su producto en EE UU, y lo hacemos con 100.000 clientes en lista de espera que ya tienen acceso al producto desde ahora. Tenemos muchas ganas de lanzar N26 públicamente para el resto del mercado a finales de verano.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nos gustaría dar las gracias a nuestro equipo y a todos nuestros clientes. Nuestro éxito no hubiera sido posible sin estos apoyos. La confianza que habéis depositado en nosotros nos hace llegar lejos y hoy podemos decir con orgullo que somos una de las ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"startups","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" mejor valoradas de Europa. Miramos al futuro con la ilusión de saber que seguís a nuestro lado y con la certeza de que habrá muchos más éxitos que celebrar juntos.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"},{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Valentin Stalf y Maximilian Tayenthal","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"value":"Fundadores","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2019-07-11T09:20:15.636Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:23:17.606Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":7},"fields":{"title":{"de":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","en":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","es":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","fr":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","it":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)"},"description":{"de":"N26 Launch USA","en":"N26 US Launch Infographic ","es":"N26 Aterriza en EE UU - Infográfico"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F4239596f41f41baf51d30e01493ae928\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-DE__1_.jpg","details":{"size":918866,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-DE (1).jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F8388a7a85084e7e2f22388863fe485e5\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-EN-UK__1_.jpg","details":{"size":885869,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-EN-UK (1).jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F07f29c13f1cfc7592f31ac3973983a46\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-ES.jpg","details":{"size":970109,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-ES.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002Fe085154ec80c1c740f4bc4da39dc35b3\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-FR.jpg","details":{"size":967037,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-FR.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002Fb405f4cec3a025d9ff35ecd0834c4fb9\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-IT.jpg","details":{"size":935050,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-IT.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Aujourd’hui, N26 se lance aux Etats-Unis. Cet événement marque une nouvelle étape de notre croissance en tant que véritable banque globale.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Notre objectif est de simplifier l’expérience bancaire pour permettre à chacun de gérer ses finances comme il le souhaite et de façon agréable. Nous redonnons à nos clients le contrôle sur leurs finances et leur offrons tous les outils et services nécessaires pour gérer leur budget du mieux possible. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Depuis notre lancement en janvier 2015, N26 a connu un grand succès. Aujourd’hui, nous comptons plus de 3,5 millions d’utilisateurs, qui effectuent plus de 16 millions de transactions par mois, pour un volume mensuel de transactions de plus de 2 milliards d’euros. Chaque jour, plus de 10 000 utilisateurs ouvrent un compte dans l’un de nos 24 marchés européens, principalement grâce au bouche-à-oreille. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Le futur de N26 est à l’international. Notre lancement aux Etats-Unis est un événement majeur pour La Banque Mobile. Nous avons pour objectifs de devenir la banque que des millions de clients dans le monde aiment utiliser et de franchir le cap des 50 millions de clients dans les années à venir. Nous savons que des millions de personnes dans le monde payent encore des frais bancaires élevés, que leur expérience bancaire est opaque et ne leur permet pas de gérer facilement leurs comptes au quotidien. Nous allons donc radicalement modifier la façon dont les américains perçoivent et interagissent avec leur banque, comme nous l’avons déjà fait pour tous nos clients en Europe. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"En tant que première néo-banque européenne à se lancer aux Etats-Unis, nous sommes très heureux d’annoncer que les 100 000 utilisateurs inscrits sur notre liste d’attente aux Etats-Unis, peuvent désormais ouvrir leur compte et découvrir N26. Le lancement public aura lieu plus tard cet été. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Enfin, nous voudrions remercier l’ensemble de nos équipes, le ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-us\u002Fblog\u002Four-us-journey-begins-today"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"CEO pour les Etats-Unis, Nicolas Kopp","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":",  ainsi que tous les clients qui nous accordent leur confiance. Notre succès n’aurait pas été possible sans leur soutien et c’est grâce à eux que N26 a pu évoluer pour devenir l’entreprise qu’elle est aujourd’hui. Nous sommes impatients de poursuivre notre croissance - en Europe, aux États-Unis et sur d'autres marchés à travers le monde.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Avec nos remerciements les plus sincères,","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Valentin Stalf, Maximilian Tayenthal","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Fondateurs","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2019-07-11T09:20:15.636Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:23:17.606Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":7},"fields":{"title":{"de":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","en":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","es":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","fr":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","it":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)"},"description":{"de":"N26 Launch USA","en":"N26 US Launch Infographic ","es":"N26 Aterriza en EE UU - Infográfico"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F4239596f41f41baf51d30e01493ae928\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-DE__1_.jpg","details":{"size":918866,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-DE (1).jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F8388a7a85084e7e2f22388863fe485e5\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-EN-UK__1_.jpg","details":{"size":885869,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-EN-UK (1).jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F07f29c13f1cfc7592f31ac3973983a46\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-ES.jpg","details":{"size":970109,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-ES.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002Fe085154ec80c1c740f4bc4da39dc35b3\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-FR.jpg","details":{"size":967037,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-FR.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002Fb405f4cec3a025d9ff35ecd0834c4fb9\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-IT.jpg","details":{"size":935050,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-IT.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Oggi N26 sbarca ufficialmente negli Stati Uniti. Con questo traguardo fondamentale, siamo sempre più vicini a realizzare la nostra missione: diventare la banca che tutto il mondo ama usare.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Puntiamo a semplificare l’esperienza bancaria per permettere a tutti di gestire il proprio denaro e la propria vita a modo loro. Vogliamo offrire ai nostri clienti tutti gli strumenti e i servizi necessari per riprendere il controllo delle proprie finanze, in modo che possano prendere decisioni consapevoli e cogliere le migliori opportunità.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Fin dal nostro lancio nel gennaio 2015, N26 è stata e continua a essere una straordinaria storia di successo. Ad oggi sono 3,5 milioni le persone che si sono affidate a noi, 16 milioni le transazioni effettuate ogni mese e il volume delle transazioni mensili ammonta a 2 miliardi di euro. Ogni giorno, oltre 10.000 nuovi clienti nei nostri 24 mercati europei aprono un conto N26, principalmente grazie al passaparola di altri utenti entusiasti dei nostri servizi.   ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Il futuro di N26, però, è globale. E l’arrivo negli Stati Uniti è un passo fondamentale nel nostro percorso per diventare una banca globale a tutti gli effetti. Il nostro obiettivo per i prossimi anni è superare i 50 milioni di clienti in tutto il mondo. Sappiamo che, a livello mondiale e specialmente negli Stati Uniti, milioni di persone continuano a pagare commissioni nascoste e a incontrare ostacoli e difficoltà nella gestione quotidiana delle loro finanze. Noi cambieremo radicalmente il modo in cui gli americani utilizzano i servizi bancari, proprio come abbiamo fatto per i nostri clienti in Europa.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"In quanto prima challenger bank europea ad arrivare negli Stati Uniti, non potremmo essere più entusiasti all’idea che i nostri 100.000 clienti sulla lista d’attesa negli USA possano finalmente iniziare a utilizzare il nostro prodotto. Non vediamo l’ora che arrivi il nostro lancio pubblico completo, previsto più avanti quest’estate. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Vogliamo ringraziare il nostro fantastico team, il nostro ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-us\u002Fblog\u002Four-us-journey-begins-today"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"CEO USA Nic","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" e tutti i clienti che si sono affidati a noi, che hanno reso possibile il nostro arrivo negli Stati Uniti. Senza il loro sostegno, non potremmo celebrare questo nuovo successo. La fiducia che hanno riposto in N26 ci ha sostenuto nella creazione di questa incredibile azienda, che è attualmente una delle start up di maggior successo in Europa. Non vediamo l’ora di continuare a scrivere questa storia di successo, in Europa, negli Stati Uniti e in tanti altri mercati in tutto il mondo.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Con un ringraziamento sincero,","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Valentin Stalf e Maximilian Tayenthal","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Fondatori","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Corporate"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2019-07-11T09:20:15.636Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:23:17.606Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":7},"fields":{"title":{"de":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","en":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","es":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","fr":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)","it":"N26 US Launch Infographic (ALL)"},"description":{"de":"N26 Launch USA","en":"N26 US Launch Infographic ","es":"N26 Aterriza en EE UU - Infográfico"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F4239596f41f41baf51d30e01493ae928\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-DE__1_.jpg","details":{"size":918866,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-DE (1).jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F8388a7a85084e7e2f22388863fe485e5\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-EN-UK__1_.jpg","details":{"size":885869,"image":{"width":1634,"height":2900}},"fileName":"N26-US-Launch-Infographic-EN-UK (1).jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F34f78Ge4jDrOiTanCPkXnk\u002F07f29c13f1cfc7592f31ac3973983a46\u002FN26-US-Launch-Infographic-ES.jpg","details":{"size":