k also comes with the signature N26 Black features meaning you don’t get charged percentage fees on foreign currency ATM withdrawals. You get what your money is worth, without it being eaten up by extra fees.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"You also get a handy 0,1% cashback on all purchases you make with your Mastercard. You’ll get your money right back in your account every quarter. That’s a sound investment for the future of your business.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"More space for your projects","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"As a premium account, Business Black lets you have up to 10 simultaneous spaces (sub-accounts). Spaces is one of our newest products which lets you break up your money into different sub-accounts so you can save towards a goal, or just better organize your money.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"For freelancers this can be very useful; it’s handy to break up your expenses by category. So maybe you have a travel expenses space, a business trip food space, or a space for an online course in UX design. It’s all up to you; we just want to help you get to where you want to go.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1AppFull"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1Card"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2CardYou"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Spaces"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"15hHsaU9FSeyYa6agGum00","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-08-24T15:22:10.372Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:23:54.583Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision"