ses right back into your business. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Other"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"5lz3XFBmI8AYYgcSUCI66E","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-08-24T15:19:43.692Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:21:00.589Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2},"fields":{"title":{"en":"Business Black Blog body 2"},"file":{"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F5lz3XFBmI8AYYgcSUCI66E\u002Fad450bee2bcb166ec6d2a7ab2140efe1\u002FBusiness_Black_Blog_body_2.png","details":{"size":623565,"image":{"width":777,"height":437}},"fileName":"Business Black_Blog_body_2.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-asset-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Make business trips more secure","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 Business Black comes complete with comprehensive trip insurance from Allianz. With it, you can travel worry-free with foreign medical cover based on the Insurance General Terms and Conditions. That can help keep costs low in an emergency. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"At home or abroad, N26 Business Black also protects your work devices. With an extended warranty up to 1 year and purchase protection on eligible purchases, you don’t have to worry about if the new work laptop breaks down on you.\nYou can see everything Business Black covers ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fyou-bank-account-with-travel-insurance"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"here","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":".","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Make your money go further","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Business Black also comes with the signature N26 Black features meaning you don’t get charged percentage fees on foreign currency ATM withdrawals. You get what your money is worth, without it being eaten up by extra fees.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"You also get a handy 0,1% cashback on all purchases you make with your Mastercard. You’ll get your money right back in your account every quarter. That’s a sound investment for the future of your business.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"More space for your projects","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"As a premium account, Business Black lets you have up to 10 simultaneous spaces (sub-accounts). Spaces is one of our newest products which lets you break up your money into different sub-accounts so you can save towards a goal, or just better organize your money.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"For freelancers this can be very useful; it’s handy to break up your expenses by category. So maybe you have a travel expenses space, a business trip food space, or a space for an online course in UX design. It’s all up to you; we just want to help you get to where you want to go.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1AppFull"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1Card"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2CardYou"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Spaces"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space