pp N26 con Apple Pay aperto"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F27Ik8o2lGcSMs4sqcwK8s0\u002Ff83885b0c2c81ef5a2420bda85311c48\u002F1811-Apple_Pay_Launch_DE-Blog.jpg","details":{"size":139621,"image":{"width":2400,"height":1254}},"fileName":"1811-Apple Pay Launch DE-Blog.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F27Ik8o2lGcSMs4sqcwK8s0\u002F1a51e61a8794ab69c4f7b9b804c6049b\u002F1811-Apple_Pay_Launch_DE-Blog.jpg","details":{"size":139621,"image":{"width":2400,"height":1254}},"fileName":"1811-Apple Pay Launch DE-Blog.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F27Ik8o2lGcSMs4sqcwK8s0\u002Fd42b21e28f4acd202489b3bc4ef521db\u002F1811-Apple_Pay_Launch_DE-Blog.jpg","details":{"size":139621,"image":{"width":2400,"height":1254}},"fileName":"1811-Apple_Pay_Launch_DE-Blog.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F27Ik8o2lGcSMs4sqcwK8s0\u002F5a7f6c617b1b06d0c68abec2466cd29d\u002F1811-Apple_Pay_Launch_DE-Blog.jpg","details":{"size":139621,"image":{"width":2400,"height":1254}},"fileName":"1811-Apple_Pay_Launch_DE-Blog.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F27Ik8o2lGcSMs4sqcwK8s0\u002F3380f51ab3a5e17b7c6d03275d2a9889\u002F1811-Apple_Pay_Launch_DE-Blog.jpg","details":{"size":139621,"image":{"width":2400,"height":1254}},"fileName":"1811-Apple_Pay_Launch_DE-Blog.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"categoryId":{"en":"product"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5KiVGM6QjC6aOuyciK8cGy"}}},"date":{"en":"2017-11-09"},"excerpt":{"en":"Starting today, Apple Pay is available for N26 customers in Spain, Italy, and Finland. ","es":"Desde hoy, Apple Pay está disponible para clientes de N26 en España, Italia y Finlandia.","it":"A partire da oggi, Apple Pay è disponibile per i clienti N26 in Italia, Spagna e Finlandia."},"copy":{"de":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"6KHnAHOFTTO1wDyMD12fvc","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"What if there was a way to pay without your card that is accepted in stores, online and in apps? Well, say hello to Apple Pay. Starting today, Apple Pay is available for N26 customers in Spain, Italy, and Finland. Apple Pay is one step closer to seamless payments with your N26 account and makes it easier and more secure to pay, opening up a whole new world of possibilities.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"What is Apple Pay?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Apple Pay is a mobile payment system that makes it easy to use your Apple devices to pay in stores, apps, and on the web. It integrates directly with your N26 bank account, meaning you can quickly add your Mastercard to Apple Pay right in the N26 App. After quick card verification, customers can already start making payments. Since it’s fully integrated with your Mastercard, you’ll see your transactions in real-time and receive push notifications.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Using Apple Pay","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Apple Pay is exciting because of its almost endless possibilities. You can make payments in stores, secure payments online, and pay in apps. It uses the NFC technology in your Apple device for easy contactless payments. Hold your Apple device next to the reader, confirm with your fingerprint and go. In apps, you can also use Apple Pay to order things like food or a taxi.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Since Apple Pay doesn’t store your card information on your device or share it when you pay, it is more secure than normal card payments. It’s the perfect marriage of security and convenience.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"With Apple Pay, you have another way to manage their money and make mobile payments with the devices you love. We’re excited to see what you all think of it. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"6KHnAHOFTTO1wDyMD12fvc","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"¿Y si hubiera una manera de pagar sin tu tarjeta, aceptada tanto en tiendas, como online y en apps? Bueno, saluda a Apple Pay. Desde hoy, Apple Pay está disponible para clientes de N26 en España, Italia y Finlandia. Apple Pay significa un paso más hacia pagos más eficientes con tu cuenta N26 y hace que pagar sea más sencillo y seguro, abriendo un mundo entero de nuevas posibilidades.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"¿Qué es Apple Pay?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Apple Pay es un sistema de pagos móviles que facilita el uso de tus dispositivos Apple para pagar en tiendas, aplicaciones y en la web. Apple Pay se integra directamente en tu cuenta bancaria N26, lo que te permite fácilmente añadir tu Mastercard a Apple Pay dentro de tu aplicación N26. Tras una rápida verificación de tarjeta, nuestros clientes pueden comenzar a realizar pagos. Como está totalmente integrado con tu Mastercard, verás tus transacciones en tiempo real y recibirás notificaciones push.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Utilizando Apple Pay","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Apple Pay es emocionante debido a sus casi infinitas posibilidades. Puedes realizar pagos en tiendas, compras online de manera segura y pagos en aplicaciones. Utiliza la tecnología NFC de tu dispositivo Apple para pagos contactless. Mantén tu dispositivo Apple cerca del lector, confirma con tu huella dactilar, y listo. En aplicaciones también puedes utilizar Apple Pay para pedir cosas como comida o un taxi.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ya que Apple Pay ni guarda la información de tu tarjeta en tu dispositivo ni la comparte a la hora del pago, es más seguro que los tradicionales pagos con tarjeta. Es el matrimonio perfecto entre la seguridad y la comodidad.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Con Apple Pay tienes una nueva manera de gestionar tu dinero y realizar pagos móviles en los dispositivos que te encantan. Queremos saber qué pensáis acerca de Apple Pay. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"6KHnAHOFTTO1wDyMD12fvc","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"6KHnAHOFTTO1wDyMD12fvc","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"E se ci fosse un modo per pagare senza utilizzare la carta, che sia accettato nei negozi, online e su app? Bene, dai il benvenuto a Apple Pay. A partire da oggi, Apple Pay è disponibile per i clienti N26 in Italia, Spagna e Finlandia. Apple Pay rende i tuoi pagamenti con la carta N26 ancora più semplici e sicuri, aprendoti un mondo di nuove possibilità.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Che cos’è Apple Pay?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Apple Pay è un sistema di pagamento mobile che ti permette di utilizzare il tuo dispositivo Apple per i pagamenti in negozio, online e su app. Il sistema si integra direttamente al tuo conto corrente N26, quindi non dovrai far altro che aggiungere la tua Mastercard ad Apple Pay, direttamente dall’app N26. Dopo una veloce verifica della tua carta, potrai già effettuare tutti i pagamenti. Data la completa integrazione con la tua Mastercard, vedrai tutte le transazioni del tuo conto in tempo reale e riceverai subito notifiche push.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Come si usa Apple Pay?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Apple Pay è sorprendente perché ricco di infinite possibilità. Puoi effettuare pagamenti in negozio, acquisti online in tutta sicurezza e paghi direttamente su app. Nel tuo dispositivo Apple è integrata una tecnologia NFC, che ti consente di effettuare pagamenti contactless. Avvicina il tuo dispositivo Apple al lettore della carta, conferma la transazione con la tua impronta ed il gioco è fatto! Puoi anche utilizzare Apple Pay su app, per ordinare ad esempio il tuo taxi o la tua cena.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Apple Pay è ancora più sicuro dei normali pagamenti con carta, in quanto i dettagli della tua carta non vengono salvati sul tuo dispositivo né condivisi al momento del pagamento. Il connubio perfetto tra sicurezza e convenienza. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Con Apple Pay, hai un altro modo per gestire il tuo denaro ed effettuare pagamenti mobile con il tuo amato dispositivo. Siamo curiosi di sapere cosa ne pensi. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"6KHnAHOFTTO1wDyMD12fvc","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"pt":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"6KHnAHOFTTO1wDyMD12fvc","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"}},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"rN5QKPAxrwYCy8WiqQ8um"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6KHnAHOFTTO1wDyMD12fvc"}}]}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"2mIbFaOrxU2xZmGFdDDCy","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-03-10T14:55:32.019Z","updatedAt":"2020-03-10T14:55:32.019Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"redirect"}}},"fields":{"from":{"en":"de-at\u002Fblog\u002Fgreat-news-english-speaking-number26-users"},"to":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"31WmoehcBiwwuAsaOeOmuI","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-04-27T10:36:42.982Z","updatedAt":"2020-05-12T15:11:15.390Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":21,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"page"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"en":"Page: Blog Archive (ALL)"},"countryCodes":{"en":["DE","AT","FR","IT","ES","EU","CH"]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"35OZ1wU4XmseoW0i4Ugawe"}}},"trackingName":{"en":"blogArchive"},"seaPage":{"en":false},"isIndexed":{"en":false},"title":{"de":"Blog Archiv","en":"Blog Archive","es":"Archivo Blog","fr":"Archives du blog","it":"Archivio del blog"},"slug":{"de":"blog-archiv","en":"blog-archive","es":"blog-archivo","fr":"blog-archive","it":"blog-archivio"},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3X6uhG6KfS66ooUUuOCucs"}}]}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"5hJyb6uVyx6fjxEXv1cRUt","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-03-10T14:52:24.038Z","updatedAt":"2020-03-10T14:52:24.038Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"redirect"}}},"fields":{"from":{"en":"\u002Fen-de\u002Fblog\u002F1-year-old-100-000-customers-strong"},"to":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"blog1NoEvergreenNoSeasonal"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"blog2Company"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"blog3Global"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"blog4NoConversionCard"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"rsWqXHeAGyK0m0MQwOI6C","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-04-26T14:01:17.391Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-25T10:01:53.043Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":5,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"blogPost"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"de":"Unser Kunde 100.000","en":"Our Customer 100000"},"countryCodes":{"en":["EU"]},"title":{"de":"Unser Kunde 100.000","en":"Our Customer 100000"},"slug":{"de":"kunde-100000","en":"our-customer-100000"},"categoryId":{"en":"company"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"27jlDrE1cQuQWOKooYAwYw"}}},"date":{"en":"2016-01-26"},"copy":{"de":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"100.000 Kunden – der perfekte Anlass, sich die Kunden einmal genauer anzuschauen (das haben wir ja auch schon in der Infografik getan). Und hier ist er: Nummer 100.000 Michael Jäger, 33, aus Marbach am Neckar. Der glücklich verheiratete Sales Manager ist stolzer Vater einer Tochter (Geburtstag 26. Januar!) und Fotografie-Liebhaber. Außer der NUMBER26 App liebt er den eSign Manager, PhotoshopMix und Apple Music. Wir haben ihm ein paar Fragen gestellt:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Wie kamst du auf NUMBER26","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"- Meine Wahl fiel auf NUMBER26, da die Kontoeröffnung zum einen extrem schnell (weniger als 10 Minuten) und unkompliziert ging. Außerdem haben die Leistungen voll überzeugt, angefangen bei der ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fkreditkarte"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"kostenlosen Kreditkarte","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", die ich für meine vielen Reisen durch Deutschland gut gebrauchen kann.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Außerdem hat mir allein die Möglichkeit gefallen, dass sämtliche Transaktionen in Echtzeit auf der App nachweislich waren. Nach den ersten Erfahrungen mit NUMBER26 wird es wohl auf kurz oder lang mein Hauptkonto werden.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Was ist dein Lieblings-Feature?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Unschlagbar ist auf jeden Fall die App, über die wirklich alles geregelt werden kann.\nDas Sahnestück ist, dass ich mein Transaktionslimit in Echtzeit und sofort selber bestimmen kann. Ich erinnere mich da an meinen Fahrzeugkauf zurück, den ich mit EC-Karte bezahlen wollte und die Zahlung nicht durchführen konnte, da es leider das Zahlungslimit trotz vorhandenem Kapital an diesem Tag überschritten hätte. (Mal ehrlich, warum soll ich erst einen Temin beim Bankberater vereinbaren, damit er das Auszahlungslimit für einen bestimmten Zeitraum höher setzt!)\nWas unterscheidet NUMBER26 von anderen Banken?\nGute Frage! Zum einen eine wirklich super funktionierende App, über die wirklich alles geregelt werden kann. Zum anderen, dass für den Endverbraucher keinerlei Gebühren anfallen. Weder für die Karte noch Kontoführungsgebühren. Man kann mit den Karten von NUMBER26 (abgesehen von einigen Sparkassenautomaten) überall kostenlos Bargeld beziehen.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Was wünschst du NUMBER26 zum ersten Geburtstag?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Macht auf jeden Fall weiter so. Haltet eure Standards weiter so schön hoch und entwickelt euch immer weiter bis an die Spitze, denn nur so sieht ein wirklich kundenorientiertes Bankenmodell der Zukunft aus.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Wo siehst du NUMBER26 im Jahr 2026?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Hoffentlich als eine international verzweigte Bank auch außerhalb Europas! \nIhr seid auch leidenschaftliche NUMBER26 Liebhaber? Schreibt uns eure Gründe für NUMBER26 in die Kommentare!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Our 100,000th customer - it’s quite the milestone. To ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fblog\u002Four-customer-100000"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"honour this landmark","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":", we wanted to introduce you to Michael Jäger, who hails from Marbach am Neckar. The sales manager, a happily married father of one (whose daughter shares a birthday with us on January 26th!), enjoys photography in his spare time. In addition to the NUMBER26 app, Michael is a fan of eSign Manager, Photoshop Mix and Apple Music.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"He took some time out of his busy schedule to answer a few questions for us.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"How did you discover NUMBER26?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"I chose NUMBER26 because of how ridiculously easy and quick it is (less than 10 minutes) to open an account. The features were also quite convincing, starting with a ","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{"uri":"https:\u002F\u002Fn26.com\u002Fen-eu\u002Fmastercard"},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"free credit card","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"hyperlink"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":" (which I’ve already put to good use in my travels throughout Germany). I really like the way I can receive data in real time on the app. It didn’t take long to convince me, and sooner or later it’s bound to become my regular bank account.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"What’s your favourite feature?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"To me, the app is unbeatable because you can manage everything right there. The kicker is that I can set a limit on transactions in real time, and I have control over those functions. I think back to when I bought a car and I wanted to pay with an EC-Card but the payment wouldn’t process -- despite the fact that I had the funds available -- because I had already overspent my limit for the day. (And let’s be honest: why should I have to make an appointment with a bank manager so that he can increase my limit for a certain amount of time?!)","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"How does NUMBER26 differentiate from other banks?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Good question! First, the app itself is just super, given how much control you have over everything. Secondly, the user isn’t dinged with nickel-and-dime fees, either for the card or on the account. So you’re able to use the NUMBER26 card just about everywhere (except for a few Sparkasse ATMs) to take out cash.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Any birthday wishes for NUMBER26?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Keep doing what you’re doing. Keep your standards high and keep developing your account till you reach the top, because this is how a customer-driven, bank-of-the-future looks like.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"How do you envision NUMBER26 in 2026?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Hopefully as an international bank outside of Europe!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"},"pt":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"}},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2A8Xd4TrRKmrVWb45l4UYz"}}]}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"3NEHHjFqhS1mYeLnplv61f","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-03-03T13:56:49.046Z","updatedAt":"2020-03-03T13:56:49.046Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"redi