"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"595OGhB7HiqTz5s97YwcR3","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2019-11-12T13:07:29.721Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:28:30.617Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3},"fields":{"title":{"de":"Blog Header Extra Cards Launch","en":"Blog Header Extra Cards Launch","es":"Blog Header Extra Cards Launch","fr":"Blog Header Extra Cards Launch","it":"Blog Header Extra Cards Launch"},"description":{"de":"Schwarz und Grün N26 Sie Karte","en":"Black and green N26 You card","es":"Tarjeta N26 You negra y verde","fr":"Carte N26 You noire et verte","it":"Nero e verde N26 Tu carta"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F595OGhB7HiqTz5s97YwcR3\u002F0458c47e0b7a325e396c4574f95c1ddc\u002Fn26-extra-card-blog-1360-765.png","details":{"size":49031,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"n26-extra-card-blog-1360-765.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F595OGhB7HiqTz5s97YwcR3\u002F1fcf255bd95260ac4d240e2e0892007f\u002Fn26-extra-card-blog-1360-765.png","details":{"size":49031,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"n26-extra-card-blog-1360-765.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F595OGhB7HiqTz5s97YwcR3\u002F13a5a2e95e332becf414fd9bf80feb96\u002Fn26-extra-card-blog-1360-765.png","details":{"size":49031,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"n26-extra-card-blog-1360-765.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F595OGhB7HiqTz5s97YwcR3\u002F8ac9018dd924fa407e204ceaadf61b02\u002Fn26-extra-card-blog-1360-765.png","details":{"size":49031,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"n26-extra-card-blog-1360-765.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F595OGhB7HiqTz5s97YwcR3\u002Fb2f5f72c4d72cf7fd5a4c987ba4e7051\u002Fn26-extra-card-blog-1360-765.png","details":{"size":49031,"image":{"width":1360,"height":765}},"fileName":"n26-extra-card-blog-1360-765.png","contentType":"image\u002Fpng"}}}}},"categoryId":{"en":"product"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5KiVGM6QjC6aOuyciK8cGy"}}},"date":{"en":"2019-11-13"},"excerpt":{"de":"Doppelt hält besser und mit N26 kannst du ab sofort in Österreich auch eine Zusatzkarte bestellen. ","en":"Good news for people who lose things – now you can order a second bank card for your N26 account. Find out how.","it":"Sei tra quelli che puntualmente non trovano la carta proprio quando ne hanno bisogno? Buone notizie: ora puoi richiedere una seconda carta per il tuo conto N26. Scopri come!\n"},"copy":{"de":{"nodeType":"document","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Ab sofort kannst du als N26 Premiumkunde (You, Business You oder Metal) eine zusätzliche Mastercard für dein Girokonto anfordern. Damit du jederzeit Ersatz bereit hast, wenn du ihn brauchen solltest.","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Sicher ist Sicher","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Eine Bankkarte gehört meistens zu jenen Dingen, ohne die du niemals das Haus verlassen würdest (außer natürlich, du verwendest Apple Pay!). Dabei kann es aber vorkommen, dass eine Zusatzkarte ganz schön sinnvoll wäre. Ob du im Urlaub lieber auf Nummer Sicher gehen willst oder gerne einfach zuhause einen Back-Up hättest, mit N26 Premium kannst du das jetzt veranlassen. ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Denn als N26 You, Business You oder Metalkunde in Österreich, kannst du ab sofort eine Zusatzkarte bestellen. Für 10 € (einmalig), kannst du sowohl eine Karte jederzeit bei dir haben, als auch eine sicher als Back-Up verstauen, damit du in jeder Situation flexibel bleiben kannst. ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Dein Konto, deine Karten","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Als You oder Business You Kunde, kannst du deine Zusatzkarte in einer der fünf verfügbaren You-Farben wählen: Aqua, Rhabarber, Sand, Schiefer und Ozean. Und als Metalkunde kannst du dich nun ebenfalls an farbenfrohen Kombinationen erfreuen, denn zusätzlich zu deiner Metallkarte kannst auch du deine Zusatzkarte aus den You-Modellen aussuchen. ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block","content":[],"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"7928Jdry4mzvHHUJJhtghz","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Jetzt bestellen","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Deine Zusatzkarte anzufordern ist ganz einfach:","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"ordered-list","content":[{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Öffne deine N26 App und gehe auf “Entdecken”","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Klicke unter der Kategorie “Upgrades” auf “Zusatzkarte hinzufügen” ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Wähle aus den Farben Aqua, Rhabarber, Sand, Schiefer und Ozean deine neue Kartenfarbe aus ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"list-item","content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Bestätige deine Adresse, die Bestellung deiner Zusatzkarte für 10 € und stimme den AGB zu. Gib anschließend deine PIN ein. Deine Zusatzkarte wird an die hinterlegte Adresse versandt. ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"heading-2","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Teilen macht Freude, aber...","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Bitte beachte, dass deine Zusatzkarte an dich und dein Konto gebunden ist. Daher darfst du auch deine Zweitkarte niemals einer anderen Person zu Verfügung stellen. Wenn du einer Zweitperson die Nutzung deines Kontos gestattest, verstößt du gegen die AGB von N26. Das kann zur Schließung deines N26 Kontos führen. Wenn du im Alltag Geld mit deiner Familie und Freunden teilen möchtest, kannst du schon bald einen Shared Space einrichten und bis zu 10 Personen dazu einladen. ","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block","content":[],"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"5geGqLZkq4vjozMlEKplOM","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}}},{"nodeType":"paragraph","content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"","marks":[],"data":{}}],"data":{}}]},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"If you find yourself constantly hunting for missing belongings, we’ve got great news for you. Starting today, N26 You, Business You and Metal customers can now order a second Mastercard for use with their account, so you’ll always have a spare to hand.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Extra peace of mind","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Whether it’s grabbing coffee-to-go or the down-payment on a vacation, debit cards are still one of the most common ways to pay for most of us. If you ever lose you card, even a few days waiting for the new card to arrive can feel like a lifetime. That’s why it’s better to have a backup. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"We’re offering customers with N26 You, Business You and Metal account memberships the chance to order a second card to be linked to their account for just €10, that can be used interchangeably with the original, so that you can keep one in your pocket and one at home – or any other safe place where you need a spare.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Your card, your way","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 You and Business You customers can order another card in whichever of the 5 colors available – Sand, Rhubarb, Teal, Ocean and Slate – that they prefer. N26 Metal customers can also benefit from this and choose one of the N26 You design cards, which will have the exact same functionality as their original Metal card.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Order yours","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ordering an extra card for your account is easy. Just open the Explore tab in your N26 app and follow these steps:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Under Upgrades, click ‘Add extra card’","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Choose your favorite card color in either Sand, Rhubarb, Teal, Ocean or Slate. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Once you confirm the shipping address, the additional card cost of €10 and agree to the Terms & Conditions, just click and enter your PIN to purchase. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Your new card will be shipped to your registered address! ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"list-item"}],"nodeType":"ordered-list"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Sharing is caring, but...","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Please note that for legal reasons, it won’t be possible to order a spare card and give it to someone else to use, since both cards would be registered under your name and attached to your N26 account. Allowing more than one person to use the same account would breach the T&C’s of your N26 user agreement, which could result in your account being closed. If you’re interested in managing everyday money together in one place with friends and family, you’ll soon be able to set up a Shared Spaces sub-account and invite up to 10 people to join instead.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"5geGqLZkq4vjozMlEKplOM","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"5geGqLZkq4vjozMlEKplOM","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"5geGqLZkq4vjozMlEKplOM","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"5geGqLZkq4vjozMlEKplOM","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"},"pt":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{"target":{"sys":{"id":"5geGqLZkq4vjozMlEKplOM","type":"Link","linkType":"Entry"}}},"content":[],"nodeType":"embedded-entry-block"}],"nodeType":"document"}},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"qJ5oiYoB3R565jwlz80vs"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5geGqLZkq4vjozMlEKplOM"}}]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6bz8T80r8gOX8ph8VcmOqa"}}}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"1MDvvREFlrqg9H9e1FQjsW","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-01-15T13:08:29.329Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-15T16:49:31.786Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"redirect"}}},"fields":{"from":{"en":"de-de\u002Fblog\u002Fupdate-zu-cash26-gebuehren-fuer-bargeldeinzahlungen"},"to":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"5C8xJno5l6S0UYaY4Eiy8Q","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2017-08-03T16:04:49.196Z","updatedAt":"2020-06-10T09:14:33.680Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":9,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"page"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"en":"Cash26 Page (DE)"},"countryCodes":{"en":["DE"]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6hzWsLmWju6QUQsyGkgico"}}},"trackingName":{"en":"cash26Page"},"productPreference":{"en":"n26Cash26"},"title":{"de":"Cash26: Geld abheben und einzahlen im Supermarkt","en":"Cash26: withdraw or deposit cash in supermarkets"},"slug":{"de":"cash26","en":"cash26"},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7bH5aHLIfXHESSofFu1TqM"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"2jTdyeUizI8QhcRaqQKKbE"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"7M50Ahel36dFdpA6QI6G9B"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"p0sDzIrut7iVzvbLFZr9w"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6rRmxhRx4L85SKWAyYOjQJ"}}]}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"1J7DVdWZ4Rp8TZPzT34Y4D","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-01-15T13:05:12.365Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-15T16:48:59.463Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"redirect"}}},"fields":{"from":{"en":"de-de\u002Fblog\u002Fanfang-vom-ende-des-geldautomaten"},"to":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"31WmoehcBiwwuAsaOeOmuI","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-04-27T10:36:42.982Z","updatedAt":"2020-05-12T15:11:15.390Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":21,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"page"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"en":"Page: Blog Archive (ALL)"},"countryCodes":{"en":["DE","AT","FR","IT","ES","EU","CH"]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"35OZ1wU4XmseoW0i4Ugawe"}}},"trackingName":{"en":"blogArchive"},"seaPage":{"en":false},"isIndexed":{"en":false},"title":{"de":"Blog Archiv","en":"Blog Archive","es":"Archivo Blog","fr":"Archives du blog","it":"Archivio del blog"},"slug":{"de":"blog-archiv","en":"blog-archive","es":"blog-archivo","fr":"blog-archive","it":"blog-archivio"},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"3X6uhG6KfS66ooUUuOCucs"}}]}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"6ix6UGFuQQ5OOR2kvuw04J","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-01-15T13:46:07.175Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-15T16:48:36.320Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":3,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"redirect"}}},"fields":{"from":{"en":"de-de\u002Fblog\u002Fmobile-first-trifft-safety-first"},"to":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"3CRxl7myw0i6aAkMWeKyqo","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-12-13T14:35:19.287Z","updatedAt":"2021-05-11T17:02:09.846Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":5,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"blogPost"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"en":"Blog post: Security during registration process (DE, AT, IT, ES)"},"countryCodes":{"en":["DE","AT","IT","ES","EU"]},"title":{"de":"Sicherheit bei der Kontoeröffnung","en":"Security when opening an N26 account: how we make sure your data stays safe","es":"La seguridad cuando abres una cuenta N26: cómo protegemos tus datos","it":"La sicurezza quando si apre un conto N26: come ci assicuriamo che i tuoi dati siano protetti"},"slug":{"de":"sicherheit-bei-der-kontoeroeffnung","en":"security-when-opening-an-n26-account","es":"seguridad-cuando-abres-una-cuenta-n26","it":"sicurezza-quando-apri-un-conto-n26"},"previewImage":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset1NoApp"}},{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Tag","id":"asset2Other"}}]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"3Xr0uyijeMyMywmSQ4QAKE","type":"Asset","createdAt":"2018-07-26T10:59:40.237Z","updatedAt":"2021-06-05T09:26:57.560Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":5},"fields":{"title":{"de":"N26 final AnnaCor-57","en":"N26 final AnnaCor-57","es":"N26 final AnnaCor-57","fr":"N26 final AnnaCor-57","it":"N26 final AnnaCor-57"},"description":{"de":"Mann hält einen Pass in der Hand","en":"Man holding a passport in his hand","es":"Hombre con un pasaporte en la mano","fr":"Homme, tenue, passeport, sien, main","it":"Uomo che tiene un passaporto in mano","pt":"Homem com um passaporte na mão"},"file":{"de":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3Xr0uyijeMyMywmSQ4QAKE\u002F709c924b128604cf59c6fd1f7c8bd151\u002FN26_final_AnnaCor-57.jpg","details":{"size":135593,"image":{"width":1200,"height":675}},"fileName":"N26_final_AnnaCor-57.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"en":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3Xr0uyijeMyMywmSQ4QAKE\u002F44ca98de68ce95b7b0787873dfa162dd\u002FN26_final_AnnaCor-57.jpg","details":{"size":135593,"image":{"width":1200,"height":675}},"fileName":"N26_final_AnnaCor-57.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"es":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3Xr0uyijeMyMywmSQ4QAKE\u002Fab377eef09edf03f3ca8a3ab56303b70\u002FN26_final_AnnaCor-57.jpg","details":{"size":135593,"image":{"width":1200,"height":675}},"fileName":"N26_final_AnnaCor-57.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"fr":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3Xr0uyijeMyMywmSQ4QAKE\u002Fb4b3c6f645c1d27a751c08d760b20ced\u002FN26_final_AnnaCor-57.jpg","details":{"size":135593,"image":{"width":1200,"height":675}},"fileName":"N26_final_AnnaCor-57.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"},"it":{"url":"\u002F\u002Fimages.ctfassets.net\u002Fq33z48p65a6w\u002F3Xr0uyijeMyMywmSQ4QAKE\u002F60f46cd1321354ec47fbb1192599c8a3\u002FN26_final_AnnaCor-57.jpg","details":{"size":135593,"image":{"width":1200,"height":675}},"fileName":"N26_final_AnnaCor-57.jpg","contentType":"image\u002Fjpeg"}}}}},"categoryId":{"en":"technology"},"category":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"kaFaEXjWLYmWEIi4wGi2I"}}},"date":{"en":"2018-12-14"},"excerpt":{"de":"Wir ermöglichen es euch, in nur wenigen Minuten ein Konto zu eröffnen. Doch hinter dieser Schnelligkeit liegen natürlich mehrere Sicherheitsstufen. Das fängt bei der Kundenverifizierung bereits an. ","en":"When opening N26 accounts, we use advanced security methods to protect our customers’ identities.","es":"Estos son los métodos de seguridad que utilizamos para verificar la identidad de nuestros clientes.","it":"Quando apri un conto N26, seguiamo metodi di sicurezza molto avanzati per proteggere l’identità dei nostri clienti. \n"},"copy":{"de":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Bereits bei der Kundenverifizierung während der Anmeldung spielt Sicherheit  für uns eine wichtige Rolle. Wir ermöglichen es euch, in nur wenigen Minuten ein Konto zu eröffnen. Doch hinter dieser Schnelligkeit liegen natürlich mehrere Sicherheitsstufen. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Generell arbeiten wir bei der Kontoeröffnung mit drei verschiedenen Identifizierungsverfahren: Foto, Video oder Postident. Welches das geeignete Verfahren ist, hängt von eurer Nationalität und eurem Wohnsitz ab. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Unser internes Kompetenzzentrum für Kundenverifizierung, in dem wir Informationen und Expertise zum Thema Identifizierung sammeln, hilft uns dabei, unsere Verifizierungsmethoden weiter zu entwickeln und dabei immer sicherer zu machen.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Bei der Auswahl unserer Verfahren beachten wir die geltenden rechtlichen lokalen und europäischen Vorgaben; daneben spielt auch eine gute Nutzererfahrung für uns als mobile Bank eine zentrale Rolle. Als voll lizenzierte Bank arbeiten wir ausschließlich mit etablierten Partnern zusammen, die auch für andere renommierte Banken in Deutschland und weltweit tätig sind. Sowohl unsere Mitarbeiter als auch die unserer Partner werden regelmäßig  entsprechend der neuesten Standards geschult und verfügen über Expertise mit der Überprüfung von Ausweisdokumenten. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Was passiert bei der Verifizierung?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Bei jeder Kontoeröffnung führen wir und unsere Partner insbesondere die folgenden Maßnahmen durch: \n(a) Überprüfung auf Manipulation und Fälschung von Ausweisen, beispielsweise durch die Kontrolle dokumentenspezifischer Sicherheitsmerkmale; \n(b) Überprüfung der Übereinstimmung von Dokumenten-Inhaber und der sich verifizierenden Person;\n(c) Datenbankabgleiche gegen internationale Sperrlisten und bekannte Betrugsversuche.   ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Der erste Schritt bleibt bei allen Verifizierungsverfahren gleich. Ihr entschließt euch, bei N26 ein Konto zu eröffnen und gebt dafür direkt in der App eure Daten ein. Im nächsten Schritt erfolgt die  Verifizierung eurer Identität über eine der folgenden Verfahren:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"1.) Video-Identifizierung","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Beim Video-Identifizierungsverfahren werdet ihr an einen ausgebildeten Spezialisten weitergeleitet, der per Videochat mit euch kommuniziert und alle Daten sowie die Echtheit des Ausweises überprüft. Diese Mitarbeiter sind speziell geschult, betrügerisches Verhalten sofort zu entdecken – zum Beispiel Manipulation oder gefälschte Ausweise. Bei Korrektheit aller Angaben gibt uns der Spezialist grünes Licht, um euer Konto zu eröffnen. Für das Video-Identifizierungsverfahren gibt es umfangreiche Vorgaben der BaFin (Bundesanstalt für Finanzdienstleistungsaufsicht), die wir umgesetzt haben. Außerdem entwickeln wir das Video-Identifizierungsverfahren auch intern immer weiter: Gerade testen wir ein qualitativ noch hochwertigeres Video-Verifizierungstool, dass das Identifizierungsverfahren bald noch sicherer machen wird. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"2.) Foto-Identifizierung","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Der Großteil unserer Kunden außerhalb Deutschlands verwendet das Foto-Identifizierungsverfahren. Bei diesem Prozess arbeiten wir mit SafeNed zusammen, einem Zahlungsdienstleister, der durch die Finanzdienstleistungsaufsicht des Vereinigten Königreichs lizenziert ist. Nach der Dateneingabe in der App, ladet ihr dort Fotos eures Ausweises sowie ein Selfie hoch. Die geschulten Mitarbeiter von Safened prüfen eure eingegebenen Daten und Dokumente anhand der Bilder auf Gültigkeit und Echtheit.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Sobald eure Dokumente anhand der gesammelten Informationen überprüft und akzeptiert sind, erhalten wir von Safened die Zusage und können euer Konto eröffnen ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"3.) Postident-Identifizierung","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 Kunden in Deutschland mit einem nicht-deutschen Ausweis bieten wir teilweise Postident-Identifizierungsverfahren an. Das ist ein Verifizierungsverfahren unseres Partners Deutsche Post. Nach der Anmeldung in der App können Kunden (abhängig von der Nationalität sowie Art des Ausweises) sich in einer Postfiliale in Deutschland verifizieren lassen. Details zu den Dokumenten findet ihr hier.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Sobald eure Dokumente überprüft und akzeptiert sind, erhalten wir über die Postfiliale die Zusage und können euer Konto eröffnen. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Bei der Auswahl unserer Verfahren steht natürlich die Einhaltung der Gesetze und regulatorischen Vorgaben an erster Stelle, aber auch eine gute Nutzererfahrung spielt für uns als mobile Bank eine zentrale Rolle. Das Vertrauen unserer Kunden ist für uns von größtem Wert und deshalb prüfen und verbessern wir unsere Identifizierungverfahren auch immer weiter. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"en":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"When it comes to customer verification during registration, security plays a vital role for us. We allow you to open an account in just a few minutes. But, behind this speed, we employ several levels of security to protect you.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"When you open an account at N26, you'll use one of three different identification methods: photo, video or Postident. The appropriate procedure depends on your nationality and your place of residence.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Our in-house customer verification team, which specializes in identity verification knowledge and research, helps us to develop our verification methods further and make them increasingly secure.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"When we design and select a procedure, we make sure it complies with local and European requirements. Yet we try our best to never compromise our emphasis on good user experience. As a fully licensed bank, we work exclusively with established partners who also work for other renowned banks in Germany and around the world. Both our employees and those of our partners are regularly trained to meet the latest standards and are equipped with the expertise to verify ID documents.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"What happens during the verification?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-3"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Each time we open an account, we employ the three following techniques to help prevent identity fraud:\n(a) we check for any possible ID card or passport tampering and counterfeiting by, for example, testing document-specific security features;\n(b) we confirm that the document holder and verifier are the same person;\n(c) we run the signup information through databases of international blacklists and known fraud attempts.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"The first step is always the same when you begin signup. Once you decide to open an account, you'll enter your personal data directly into the app.  Then we verify your identity using one of the following methods:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"1.) Video Identification","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nOnce you begin verification, you'll be forwarded to a trained specialist who will communicate with you via video chat and check all your data and the authenticity of your ID card. \nThese employees are specially trained to detect fraudulent behavior immediately—like tampering or fake ID cards. If all your information is correct, the specialist gives us the green light to open your account. For the video identification procedure, there must meet the extensive requirements of BaFin (Federal Financial Supervisory Authority). \nTo ensure we keep with and improve current standards, we continuously improve the process internally, too. At the moment, we are testing a higher-quality video verification tool that will soon make the identification process even more secure.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"2.) Photo identification","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nMost of our customers outside Germany will confirm their identification using a photo verification process. For this method, we work with SafeNed, a payment service provider licensed by the UK Financial Services Authority. After entering the data in the app, upload photos of your passport and a selfie. The trained staff of Safened check your entered data and documents based on the images on validity and authenticity.\nOnce your documents have been reviewed and accepted, SafeNed will send us a confirmation and you can open your account","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"3.) Postident identification","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nIf you're living in Germany and you want to open an N26 account, you can use Deutsche Post's postident method. After registering, you (depending on your nationality and the chosen type of ID) can verify your identity at a post office. Details about which documents they accept are here. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Once they review and accept your documents, we receive a confirmation from Deutsche Post and you can open your account.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"It goes without saying that when we chose a verification method, complying with the law and regulatory requirements comes first. But, as a mobile bank, we still put a premium on good user experience. Your trust is of the utmost importance to us. You should feel secure when you open a bank account. That's why we are working constantly to review and improve our identification methods.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Cuando verificamos tu identidad durante el registro, la seguridad es nuestra mayor prioridad. El hecho de que puedas abrir una cuenta en cuestión de minutos no compromete tu seguridad: utilizamos varios controles para protegerte.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Cuando abres un cuenta en N26 tienes que pasar por uno de los tres métodos de identificación: por foto, con una videollamada o mediante Postident (identificación en oficina postal, disponible en Alemania). El procedimiento elegido en cada caso depende de tu nacionalidad y tu país de residencia. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nuestro equipo de verificación del cliente está especializado en métodos de verificación de identidad, y nos ayuda a investigar y desarrollar nuevos y más complejos sistemas para hacer el proceso todavía más seguro.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Durante el desarrollo de nuevos métodos de verificación, siempre seguimos rigurosamente los requisitos locales y europeos. Centramos nuestros esfuerzos en combinar la seguridad y la experiencia de usuario. Como banco con licencia bancaria europea, trabajamos exclusivamente con partners de confianza que también colaboran con otros bancos tanto alemanes como internacionales. Para estar al día de las novedades, tanto nuestros empleados como los partners participan activamente en cursos de formación sobre los últimos estándares de verificación de documentos de identidad. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"¿Qué sucede durante la verificación?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Cada vez que abrimos una cuenta empleamos tres técnicas distintas para prevenir fraude:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"(a) Comprobamos cualquier posible falsificación del documento de identidad, por ejemplo revisando los diferentes elementos de seguridad específicos de cada país;","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"(b) Confirmamos que el documento corresponde a la persona que quiere abrir la cuenta;","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"(c) Introducimos la información en bases de datos internacionales para detectar si la persona es sospechosa de haber cometido fraude anteriormente.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"El primer paso al abrir una cuenta en N26 es introducir los datos personales en la app. Después verificamos la identidad utilizando unos de los siguientes métodos:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"1) Identificación por vídeo","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nUna vez que se inicia la verificación, el cliente se pone en contacto por videollamada con un especialista que le guiará por todo el proceso para comprobar la autenticidad de su documento de identidad.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Los agentes están especialmente entrenados para detectar actitudes fraudulentas, tales como documentos manipulados o falsificados. Si toda la información es correcta, el especialista dará luz verde para abrir la cuenta. En el caso de la verificación por vídeo debemos seguir una lista de requisitos impuestos por la Autoridad Federal de Supervisión Financiera alemana (BaFin, por sus siglas en alemán).","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Para asegurarnos de que cumplimos con los estándares actualizados, estamos continuamente mejorando los procesos internos. Actualmente estamos probando una herramienta de verificación por vídeo que utiliza un sistema de mayor calidad de imagen, para hacer el proceso aún más seguro.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"2) Identificación por foto","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nLa mayoría de nuestros clientes confirman su identidad a través de un proceso que requiere varias fotografías. Para utilizar este método, trabajamos con SafeNed, un servicio proveedor pagos con licencia de la Autoridad de Servicios Financieros de Reino Unido (FSA, por sus siglas en inglés). Después de introducir los datos en la app, el cliente tiene que subir dos fotos de su documento de identidad y una de sí mismo. El equipo de SafeNed comprueba que los datos introducidos y los documentos coinciden, así como su validez y autenticidad.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Una vez que los documentos son revisados y aceptados, SafeNed nos envía la confirmación y procedemos a abrir la cuenta.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"3) Identificación Postident","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nEn Alemania, uno de nuestros mercados principales, es posible abrir una cuenta N26, realizando la verificación de identidad con el método Postident a través de Deutsche Post. En cuanto el futuro cliente se registra, dependiendo de su nacionalidad y del documento de identidad que utilice, puede verificar su identidad en una oficina postal. Aquí puedes encontrar los detalles de los documentos que aceptan.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"En cuanto los documentos son revisados y aceptados recibimos una confirmación de Deutsche Post y el cliente puede seguir abriendo su cuenta.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Cuando elegimos un método de verificación es siempre cumpliendo con la regulación y los requisitos legales pertinentes. Eso sí, como banco móvil, una de nuestras prioridades es ofrecer la mejor experiencia de usuario. La confianza de nuestros clientes es lo más importante para nosotros. Y por eso trabajamos día a día para mejorar, entre otros temas, nuestros métodos de identificación.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"Quando si parla della verifica dell’identità dei nostri clienti in fase di registrazione, la sicurezza gioca un ruolo cruciale per noi. Ti permettiamo di aprire un conto corrente in pochi minuti, ma dietro questa velocità ci sono diversi livelli di sicurezza che vengono messi in atto per proteggerti.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Nel momento in cui apri un conto N26, userai uno di questi tre metodi di verifica dell’identità: foto, video o PostIdent. La procedura seguita dipende dalla tua nazionalità e dal tuo paese di residenza.\nIl nostro team interno, altamente specializzato in quanto a conoscenza e ricerca sulla tematica di verifica dell’identità, ci aiuta a migliorare costantemente i nostri metodi di verifica per renderli sempre più sicuri.\nQuando definiamo e selezioniamo le procedure da seguire, ci assicuriamo che queste soddisfino i requisiti locali ed Europei. Al tempo stesso, non scendiamo mai a compromessi quando si tratta di offrire ai nostri clienti la migliore esperienza possibile. Essendo una banca con licenza bancaria europea, lavoriamo esclusivamente con partner consolidati, che al tempo stesso lavorano con altre affermate banche in Germania e in tutto il mondo. Sia i nostri dipendenti che quelli dei nostri partner vengono formati costantemente per adeguarsi agli standard più aggiornati e vengono forniti di tutti gli strumenti e della conoscenza necessaria per verificare i documenti d’identità.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Cosa accade durante la verifica?","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ogni volta che apriamo un conto corrente, mettiamo in atto tre diverse tecniche per prevenire truffe d’identità: a) controlliamo eventuali manomissioni e contraffazioni di carte d'identità o passaporti, ad esempio testando funzionalità di sicurezza specifiche del documento; b) confermiamo che il possessore del documento e chi effettua la verifica siano la stessa persona; c) confrontiamo le informazioni di registrazione con database di blacklist internazionali e noti tentativi di frode.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Quando inizi la registrazione, il primo passaggio è sempre lo stesso. Una volta deciso di aprire un conto, inserirai i tuoi dati personali direttamente nell'app. Quindi, noi verificheremo la tua identità utilizzando uno dei seguenti metodi:","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"1) Identificazione video","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nUna volta iniziata la verifica, sarai inoltrato a uno specialista esperto che comunicherà con te tramite video chat e verificherà tutti i tuoi dati e l'autenticità della tua carta d'identità.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Questi dipendenti sono appositamente addestrati per rilevare comportamenti fraudolenti, ad esempio manomissioni o carte d'identità false. Se tutte le tue informazioni sono corrette, lo specialista ci dà il via libera per aprire il tuo conto. Per la procedura di identificazione con video, è necessario soddisfare i numerosi requisiti di BaFin (l'Autorità Federale di Vigilanza Finanziaria).","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Per assicurarci di mantenere e migliorare gli standard attuali, miglioriamo continuamente il processo anche a livello interno. Al momento stiamo testando uno strumento di verifica video di qualità superiore, che renderà presto il processo di identificazione ancora più sicuro.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"2) Identificazione fotografica","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nLa maggior parte dei nostri clienti fuori dalla Germania confermerà la propria identità utilizzando un processo di verifica tramite foto. Per questo metodo lavoriamo con SafeNed, un fornitore di servizi di pagamento autorizzato dalla UK Financial Services Authority. Dopo aver inserito i dati nell'app, caricherai diverse foto del tuo passaporto e un selfie. Lo staff qualificato di SafeNed controllerà i tuoi dati e documenti in base alle immagini, alla validità e all'autenticità.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Una volta che i tuoi documenti saranno stati esaminati e accettati, SafeNed ci invierà una conferma e tu potrai aprire il tuo conto.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"value":"3) Identificazione PostIdent","nodeType":"text"},{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"\nSe vivi in Germania e vuoi aprire un conto N26, puoi utilizzare il metodo PostIdent di Deutsche Post. Dopo esserti registrato, tu (a seconda della tua nazionalità e del tipo di documento d'identità che hai selezionato) puoi verificare la tua identità presso un ufficio postale. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Una volta esaminati e accettati i tuoi documenti, noi riceviamo una conferma da Deutsche Post e tu potrai aprire il tuo conto.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Inutile dire che, quando scegliamo un metodo di verifica, il rispetto della legge e dei requisiti normativi viene prima di tutto. In quanto banca mobile, però, riteniamo anche che una buona esperienza cliente sia fondamentale. Per noi, la tua fiducia ha la massima importanza. Dovresti sentirti sicuro quando apri un conto bancario. Ecco perché lavoriamo costantemente per aggiornare e migliorare continuamente i nostri metodi di identificazione.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"pt":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"}},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"312teg7bF6mwSqUOGoKseM"}}]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"6y03uErB5YCkGaMuQ4kImm"}}}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"cy5hMahWeY0E668jr44aC","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2020-01-15T16:26:57.613Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-15T16:46:20.563Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":2,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"redirect"}}},"fields":{"from":{"en":"en-eu\u002Fblog\u002F6124"},"to":{"en":{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"31WmoehcBiwwuAsaOeOmuI","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2018-04-27T10:36:42.982Z","updatedAt":"2020-05-12T15:11:15.390Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":21,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"page"}}},"fields":{"internalTitle":{"en":"Page: Blog Archive (ALL)"},"countryCodes":{"en":["DE","AT","FR","IT","ES","EU","CH"]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"35OZ1wU4XmseoW0i4Ugawe"}}},"trackingName":{"en":"blogArchive"},"seaPage":{"en":false},"isIndexed":{"en":false},"title":{"de":"Blog Archiv","en":"Blog Archive","es":"Archivo Blog","fr":"Archives du blog","it":"Archivio del blog"},"slug":{"de":"blog-archiv","en":"blog-archive","es":"blog-archivo