":[],"value":"This is why we’ve taken our N26 Black packaged bank account and customised it even further to fit in with you.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 You—your lifestyle, your card","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"We’re delighted to introduce you to N26 You—a bank account that puts you at the core of everything, while building on an existing seamless, borderless banking experience.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"N26 You expands on all the extended benefits of the N26 Black membership that you know and love. With free ATM withdrawals in any currency around the globe, zero fees on foreign transactions or markup costs when paying with your card abroad, N26 You gives you the freedom to roam without restrictions. ","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"In July, we’re also unveiling something extra special. To align your banking experience to you and give you full control over what your N26 You Mastercard looks like, you’ll be able to pick from 5 colours—Aqua, Rhubarb, Sand, Ocean and Slate—to truly reflect your aesthetic and personality. If you’d like to choose a shade that best represents you, as well as reap all the benefits, upgrade to N26 You or open an account. As an existing N26 Black customer, you can also re-order your Mastercard in a new colour directly in the N26 app under “Card Settings.” Of course, if you want to keep your card in black, you can.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"And that’s not all. If you’d like to keep a spare card handy at home or at the office, we’ll soon be giving you the option of ordering an additional card to use with your account—more details to follow!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Exclusive partner benefits – coming soon!","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"heading-2"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Ultimately, N26 You continues to be a premium account for all situations, whether you’re island hopping in the Mediterranean, or using your Mastercard to pay for a meal down the road. But when it comes to catering to your individual lifestyle, it goes further.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"Alongside the flexibility of having a bank account with no foreign transaction fees and a card colour that matches your needs, your membership will soon also come with a series of carefully hand-picked discounts from partners such as WeWork and GetYourGuide, and many more. Keep an eye out for these exclusive partner benefits, launching in the near future.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"},{"data":{},"content":[{"data":{},"marks":[],"value":"It’s just another way we want to make your life easier, and deliver a premium and personal banking experience that works for you.","nodeType":"text"}],"nodeType":"paragraph"}],"nodeType":"document"},"es":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"},"fr":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"},"it":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"},"pt":{"data":{},"content":[],"nodeType":"document"}},"content":{"en":[{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"Yp91lokjmX4QgaGXYm06T"}}]},"seoData":{"en":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Entry","id":"5Rxx7hAb3u56ojr0AIHxyW"}}}}}}}},{"metadata":{"tags":[]},"sys":{"space":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"Space","id":"q33z48p65a6w"}},"id":"2oQNg3gtinQbL7T1xFPQ1a","type":"Entry","createdAt":"2019-07-16T06:17:37.667Z","updatedAt":"2019-07-16T06:17:37.667Z","environment":{"sys":{"id":"master","type":"Link","linkType":"Environment"}},"revision":1,"contentType":{"sys":{"type":"Link","linkType":"ContentType","id":"redirect"}}},"fields":{"fro